(408, 406, 75, 54, 2, 'Privacy Policy', 1, 'privacy-policy', 1, '', '{\"title_2\":\"Privacy Policy Statement for 112Life\",\"content_2\":\"<div class=\\\"container\\\">\\r\\n   <div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n      <div class=\\\"col-md-12 my-class\\\">\\r\\n         <p>\\r\\n         <\\/p><div class=\\\"ltn__page-details-area ltn__blog-details-area mb-120\\\">\\r\\n            <div class=\\\"container\\\">\\r\\n               <div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n                  <div class=\\\"col-lg-12\\\">\\r\\n                     <div class=\\\"ltn__blog-details-wrap\\\">\\r\\n                        <div class=\\\"ltn__page-details-inner ltn__blog-details-inner\\\">\\r\\n                           <h2 class=\\\"ltn__blog-title\\\">\\r\\n                              Privacy Policy\\r\\n                           <\\/h2>\\r\\n                           <div class=\\\"content\\\">\\r\\n                              <p>This privacy policy discloses information about the personal data collected and used through the 112Life website.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Collected Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>112Life may collect the following personal data provided by users on the website:<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <ul>\\r\\n                                 <li>Name and Surname<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Phone Number<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Email Address<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Address<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Gender<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Marital Status<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Educational Information<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Work Experiences<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Desired Position to Apply For<\\/li>\\r\\n                              <\\/ul>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Use of Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>Collected personal data may be used for the following purposes:<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <ul>\\r\\n                                 <li>Responding to customer inquiries and providing services<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Evaluating job applications<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Communicating and providing updates<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Conducting statistical analysis and improving the website<\\/li>\\r\\n                                 <li>Complying with legal requirements<\\/li>\\r\\n                              <\\/ul>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Sharing Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>112Life uses collected personal data only for the specified purposes and does not share, sell, or rent them to third parties unless requested by legal requirements or authorized authorities.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Security of Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>112Life takes appropriate technical and administrative measures to ensure the security of collected personal data. However, no full security guarantee can be provided for communication over the internet, and no responsibility is accepted for the security of data provided by users.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Protection of Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>112Life processes and stores collected personal data in accordance with relevant legislation. Personal data is deleted or anonymized within reasonable periods after collection, except when required by legal obligations or business needs.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Updating the Privacy Policy<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. The updated policies will come into effect when published on the website. Please regularly check our privacy policy for updates.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p><strong>Contact<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n                              <p>If you have any questions regarding the privacy policy, please contact us at <a href=\\\"mailto:info@112life.com\\\">info@112life.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n                              <br>\\r\\n                              <br>\\r\\n                              <br>\\r\\n                           <\\/div>\\r\\n                        <\\/div>\\r\\n                     <\\/div>\\r\\n                  <\\/div>\\r\\n               <\\/div>\\r\\n            <\\/div>\\r\\n         <\\/div>\\r\\n         <p><\\/p>\\r\\n      <\\/div>\\r\\n   <\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\"}', '2023-11-13 10:53:20', '2023-11-25 17:12:34');
