(478, 478, 86, 79, 1, 'Nöroloji', 15, 'noroloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"N\\u00f6roloji\",\"content_1\":\"        <p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri b\\u00fcnyesinde serebrovask\\u00fcler olay \\u00fcnitesi, ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">beyin damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span>, demiyelinizan hastal\\u0131klar (<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">multipl skleroz<\\/span>),\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">epilepsi<\\/span>, n\\u00f6rodejeneratif hastal\\u0131klar (<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Alzheimer<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Parkinson hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span>), n\\u00f6romusk\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar, periferik sinir sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 konusunda ayaktan ve yatarak tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti verilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"N\\u00f6roloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 ve Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">migren<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve di\\u011fer ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131lar\\u0131, bel ve boyun a\\u011fr\\u0131lar\\u0131,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, beyin damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">inme<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">),\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">multipl skleroz<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve di\\u011fer demiyelinizan hastal\\u0131klar, Alzheimer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve di\\u011fer\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">demansiyel sendromlar<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, Parkinson hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">distoniler,<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0diskineziler,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">esansiyel tremor<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">huzursuz bacak sendromu<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0gibi hareket bozukluklar\\u0131 ve n\\u00f6rodejeneratif hastal\\u0131klar,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">epilepsi,<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">myastenia gravis<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve di\\u011fer n\\u00f6romusk\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">uyku bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, tuzak n\\u00f6ropatileri, periferik n\\u00f6ropatiler ve benzeri hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavi s\\u00fcre\\u00e7leri konusunda hizmet verilmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Elektrofizyoloji laboratuvarlar\\u0131m\\u0131zda EEG, EMG, VEP, SEP, BAEP, Tek lif EMG incelemelerinin yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra beyin ve omurilik cerrahileri s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda intraoperatif monitorizasyon uygulamas\\u0131 yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0N\\u00f6roloji<\\/span>\\u00a0bran\\u015f\\u0131m\\u0131z\\u0131n<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0n\\u00f6rooftalmoloji<\\/span>\\u00a0adl\\u0131 bir alt birimi de mevcuttur.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Intraoperatif N\\u00f6romonit\\u00f6rizasyon \\u00dcnitesi\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130ntraoperatif n\\u00f6romonit\\u00f6rizasyonun amac\\u0131 ameliyat esnas\\u0131nda hastan\\u0131n beyin, beyin sap\\u0131, kraniyal sinir ve periferik sinirlerden olu\\u015fan sinir dokusu fonksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131 korumakt\\u0131r.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Beyin ya da omurilik\\u00a0<\\/span>hasar g\\u00f6rd\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde etkilenen b\\u00f6lgeye ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak ki\\u015fi hareket etme, hissetme, duyma ya da konu\\u015fma kabiliyetlerini kaybedebilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunu \\u00f6nlemek amac\\u0131 ile son y\\u0131llarda beyin ve omurilik ameliyatlar\\u0131nda<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0intraoperatif n\\u00f6romonit\\u00f6rizasyon<\\/span>\\u00a0yayg\\u0131n olarak kullan\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130ntraoperatif n\\u00f6romonit\\u00f6rizasyon ekibi uygun hastada, ameliyat esnas\\u0131nda sinir dokular\\u0131n\\u0131n fonksiyonunu de\\u011ferlendirebilmekte ve cerrahi giri\\u015fim nedeniyle geli\\u015febilecek olas\\u0131 bir hasar\\u0131 giri\\u015fim s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda erken d\\u00f6nemde tan\\u0131mlayarak, cerraha bilgi verebilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu verilen bilgi do\\u011frultusunda cerrah, \\u00e7o\\u011fu zaman, hastan\\u0131n sinir dokular\\u0131n\\u0131n zarar g\\u00f6rmemesi i\\u00e7in ameliyat stratejisini de\\u011fi\\u015ftirebilmektedir. B\\u00f6ylelikle hastan\\u0131n ameliyat sonras\\u0131nda saptanabilecek konu\\u015fma, hareket, i\\u015fitme ya da duyu fonksiyonlar\\u0131ndaki hasar\\u0131n \\u00f6n\\u00fcne ge\\u00e7mek m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn olabilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"N\\u00f6rooftalmoloji\",\"mcontent3_1\":\" <p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00f6z ile beyin aras\\u0131ndaki ba\\u011flant\\u0131y\\u0131 sa\\u011flayan g\\u00f6rme sinirleri ve yollar\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyen hastal\\u0131klarla ilgilenen birimdir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"N\\u00f6roloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Hangi Hastal\\u0131klara Bakar?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\" <p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0v\\u00fccut sisteminin n\\u00f6rolojik olarak \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyen, kendi ba\\u015f\\u0131na veya herhangi bir sebebe ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olu\\u015fan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tedavisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilir.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6rolojik<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0a\\u00e7\\u0131dan problemleri olan hastalar\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 konulmadan \\u00f6nce doktor taraf\\u0131ndan hastan\\u0131n ge\\u00e7mi\\u015f bulgular\\u0131 incelenir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastan\\u0131n ge\\u00e7mi\\u015finde daha \\u00f6nce var olan hastal\\u0131klar ve genetik bir hastal\\u0131k olup olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 anlamak i\\u00e7in aile \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc al\\u0131n\\u0131r. Hastan\\u0131n detayl\\u0131 ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fi al\\u0131nd\\u0131ktan sonra klinik olarak kapsaml\\u0131 bir de\\u011ferlendirme ile kan testleri, BT taramalar\\u0131 ve periferik sinir ve kas fonksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc testler yap\\u0131l\\u0131r.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Beyinsel hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n en s\\u0131k belirtileri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0aras\\u0131nda\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi, v\\u00fccutta g\\u00fc\\u00e7 kayb\\u0131, hareketlere engel olamama gibi koordinasyon sorunlar\\u0131, bilin\\u00e7 bulan\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, uyu\\u015fma<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0veya\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">gibi semptomlar g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00d6zellikle ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015fen \\u015fiddetli bulant\\u0131, kusma, g\\u00f6rme kayb\\u0131, el - ayaklarda uyu\\u015fuklar ve ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi gibi ek semptomlar varsa ve bu semptomlar g\\u00fcn\\u00fcn belirli saatlerinde kendini tekrar ediyorsa, ki\\u015finin g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck hayat\\u0131n\\u0131 b\\u00fcy\\u00fck \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcde etkiliyorsa en k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcrede mutlaka bir\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">n\\u00f6roloji uzman\\u0131na<\\/span>\\u00a0g\\u00f6z\\u00fckmesi gerekir.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El ayak uyu\\u015fmalar\\u0131 da farkl\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klara ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olabilece\\u011fi gibi\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">n\\u00f6rolojik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131nda<\\/span>\\u00a0ba\\u015flang\\u0131c\\u0131 olarak kabul edilebilir. S\\u00fcrekli olarak kendini tekrarlayan el ve ayakta uyu\\u015fmalar veya hareket kayb\\u0131 gibi durumlarda da mutlaka \\u00f6ncelikle bir n\\u00f6roloji uzman\\u0131na dan\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gerekir. Bu rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar ya\\u015fl\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011fa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015febilece\\u011fi gibi ayn\\u0131 zamanda hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n habercisi de olabilir.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0sinir sistemindeki beyin, beyin sap\\u0131, omurilik ve sinirlerle ilgilenir.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0bir\\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. N\\u00f6roloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc; beyin damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 gibi, beyin fonksiyonlar\\u0131ndan kaynaklanan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi ile ilgilenir.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">N\\u00f6rolojik hastal\\u0131klardan<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 ise;\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Parkinson, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Migren, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Alzheimer, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Epilepsi, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u0130nme, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Menenjit, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Demans,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">N\\u00f6rom\\u00fcsk\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Omurilik bozukluklar\\u0131, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Diskineziler,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Uyku bozukluklar\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Uyku apnesi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Beyin t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, \\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Distoni,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Meninjiyom,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Huzursuz bacak sendromu,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Titreme Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 (Esansiyel Tremor),<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Torasik Outlet (\\u00c7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f) Sendromu,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kas distrofisi gibi kas hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Beyin anevrizmalar\\u0131,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: 