(510, 510, 86, 79, 1, 'Gastroenteroloji', 8, 'gastroenteroloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Gastroenteroloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastroenteroloji;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0sindirim sistemi a\\u011f\\u0131zdan ba\\u015flayarak, yemek borusu, mide, ince ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak, kal\\u0131n ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak, karaci\\u011fer, safra yollar\\u0131 ve pankreas hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilenen bir bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Gastroenteroloji birimi \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sindirim sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisiyle ilgilenir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Gastroenteroloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn \\u00c7al\\u0131\\u015fma Alanlar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fma alan\\u0131 olduk\\u00e7a geni\\u015ftir.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Yemek borusu<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">mide hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131ndan, ba\\u011f\\u0131rsa\\u011fa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015fen hastal\\u0131klara, karaci\\u011fer, safra kesesi<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">pankreasa<\\/span>\\u00a0kadar birbirinden farkl\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnen fakat birbiriyle ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131 olabilecek hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi bu alanda ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilir.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde hastalara te\\u015fhis ve tedavi hizmetleri verilmektedir. Te\\u015fhiste kullan\\u0131lan y\\u00f6ntemler genellikle\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">endoskopik<\\/span>\\u00a0y\\u00f6ntemlerdir. Bu y\\u00f6ntemlerden mide i\\u00e7in olan\\u0131 gastroskopi, kal\\u0131n ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak i\\u00e7in olan\\u0131 da kolonoskopi olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. Bu te\\u015fhis y\\u00f6ntemleri g\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde kamera sistemiyle yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. Hastan\\u0131n v\\u00fccuduna ince bir borunun ucunda yer alan kameralar g\\u00f6nderilir ve b\\u00f6lge incelemesi yap\\u0131l\\u0131r.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Endoskopi<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">kolonoskopi<\\/span>\\u00a0i\\u015flemleri esnas\\u0131nda hastan\\u0131n herhangi bir rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k hissetmemesi i\\u00e7in sedasyon i\\u015flemi uygulan\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Gastroenteroloji Hangi Hastal\\u0131klarla \\u0130lgilenir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bir\\u00e7ok sindirim sistemi hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n benzer semptomlar\\u0131 vard\\u0131r.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0Gastroenteroloji<\\/span>\\u00a0alan\\u0131n\\u0131n ilgilendi\\u011fi hastal\\u0131klar genelde yayg\\u0131n g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen hastal\\u0131klar aras\\u0131ndad\\u0131r. Sindirim a\\u011f\\u0131z yolundan ba\\u015flayarak, an\\u00fcse kadar devam etmektedir. Bu s\\u00fcre\\u00e7 yutak, yemek borusu,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">mide, ba\\u011f\\u0131rsaklar, karaci\\u011fer, safra kesesi, pankreas, rektum<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">an\\u00fcs\\u00fc<\\/span>\\u00a0i\\u00e7ermektedir. Bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi, gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde uzman doktorlar taraf\\u0131ndan yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n \\u00e7o\\u011fu genellikle ya\\u015fam tarz\\u0131 de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikleriyle en aza indirilebilir. Bunun d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak al\\u0131\\u015fkanl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n de\\u011fi\\u015ftirilmesi, ba\\u011f\\u0131rsaklar\\u0131n \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyen sorunlar\\u0131n ortadan kald\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ve her sene d\\u00fczenli olarak yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131 \\u00f6nerilen kanser tarama testleri sayesinde erken te\\u015fhisle tedavi edilebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Gastrointestinal Kanal Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastrointestinal sistemin ilk k\\u0131sm\\u0131 olan \\u00f6zofagus (yemek borusu) hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, mide yanmas\\u0131, yutma g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc ve a\\u011f\\u0131z kokusu gibi semptomlar\\u0131n\\u0131n sebebi olabilir.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Refl\\u00fc\\u00a0<\\/span>ba\\u015fta olmak \\u00fczere, yemek borusunu ilgilendiren kanama veya yabanc\\u0131 cisim kaynakl\\u0131 \\u00f6zofagus yaralanmalar\\u0131nda, ya\\u011f \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcc\\u00fc ve \\u00e7ama\\u015f\\u0131r suyu gibi tahri\\u015f edici maddelerin yaratt\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 hasarlarda ve<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00f6zofagus kanseri<\\/span>\\u00a0gibi ciddi hastal\\u0131klarda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi gastroenteroloji uzmanlar\\u0131 taraf\\u0131ndan yap\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Karaci\\u011fer, Safra ve Pankreas Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 son derece \\u00f6nemli hastal\\u0131klar aras\\u0131nda yer almaktad\\u0131r. Gastroenteroloji hekimlerinin en s\\u0131k kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015ft\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar aras\\u0131nda karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Bunlar;\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><b>karaci\\u011fer sirozu, portal hipertansiyon, karaci\\u011fer apseleri, karaci\\u011fer kist hidati\\u011fi,\\u00a0<\\/b><font color=\\\"#092c74\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">karaci\\u011fer kanseri<\\/span><\\/font><b>, iyi huylu karaci\\u011fer t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri,\\u00a0<\\/b><font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">hepatit A<\\/span><\\/font>,\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">hepatit B<\\/span><\\/font>,\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">hepatit C<b>\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/span><\\/font><\\/span>ve<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0hepatit D<\\/span>\\u00a0gibi hastal\\u0131klard\\u0131r.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Safra hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/span>da\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">karaci\\u011fer<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">pankreasla\\u00a0<\\/span>ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131 geli\\u015fen hastal\\u0131klar aras\\u0131nda yer al\\u0131r. Safra yollar\\u0131nda geli\\u015fen baz\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar ise;\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><font color=\\\"#092c74\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">safra kesesi ta\\u015f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/font><b>, safra kesesi iltihab\\u0131, safra kesesi polipi<\\/b><\\/span>, safra yolunda meydana gelen yaralanmalar veya darl\\u0131klar ve safra kesesi t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleridir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu gruba dahil olan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n aras\\u0131nda pankreasa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015fen hastal\\u0131klar da yer almaktad\\u0131r. V\\u00fccut i\\u00e7in \\u00f6nemli hormonlar olan\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">ins\\u00fclin<\\/span>\\u00a0ve glukagon hormonlar\\u0131 pankreasta \\u00fcretilir. Herhangi bir sebeple pankreas\\u0131n al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 halinde v\\u00fccut art\\u0131k bu hormonlar\\u0131 \\u00fcretemez. Bu nedenle pankreas\\u0131 al\\u0131nan ki\\u015filerin bu duruma dikkat etmesi gereklidir. Pankreasa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015fen baz\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar ise;\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">akut pankreas<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">kronik pankreas\\u00a0<\\/span>enfeksiyonu ve\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">pankreas kanseridir<\\/span><\\/font>. Gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n seyrine g\\u00f6re tan\\u0131 ve tedavi i\\u015flemi planlan\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn geni\\u015f bir hastal\\u0131k yelpazesi bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n te\\u015fhisinde genel olarak hasta \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc al\\u0131nd\\u0131ktan sonra doktor taraf\\u0131ndan geni\\u015f kapsaml\\u0131 bir muayene yap\\u0131l\\u0131r. Hekimin gerek g\\u00f6rmesi durumunda ise bir\\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 te\\u015fhis y\\u00f6nteminden faydalan\\u0131l\\u0131r. Bunlar; Ultrason, Bilgisayarl\\u0131 Tomografi (CT), Manyetik Rezonans G\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme (MR), Endoskopik Retrogard Kolanjiyo-Pankreatografi (ERCP), Endosonografi olabilir ve ayr\\u0131ca kan ve gaita testi, d\\u0131\\u015fk\\u0131 elastaz \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcm\\u00fc gibi laboratuvar ortam\\u0131nda yap\\u0131lan testler de istenebilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"G\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-eye\"}', '2023-12-11 14:16:27', '2023-12-27 16:08:23'),
