(514, 514, 86, 79, 1, 'Kardiyoloji', 12, 'kardiyoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Kardiyoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kardiyoloji;<\\/span>\\u00a0kalp ve damarlar\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilenen bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Kalp v\\u00fccutta kan\\u0131n pompaland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 organd\\u0131r. Akci\\u011ferlerde oksijenlenen kan, kalbe ta\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131r, kalpten pompalanarak damarlar arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ile t\\u00fcm v\\u00fccudu dola\\u015f\\u0131r. Dokulardaki oksijeni azalm\\u0131\\u015f ve karbondioksit miktar\\u0131 artm\\u0131\\u015f kan, yine damarlar arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ile kalbe d\\u00f6ner ve sonras\\u0131nda akci\\u011ferlere ta\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131r. B\\u00f6ylece farkl\\u0131 yap\\u0131 ve g\\u00f6revdeki damarlarla birlikte\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">dola\\u015f\\u0131m sistemi<\\/span>ni olu\\u015ftururlar. Kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 dendi\\u011finde organ olarak kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, kardiyovask\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131k dendi\\u011finde kalp ve damar sisteminin b\\u00fct\\u00fcn\\u00fc ifade edilir. Kardiyoloji uzman\\u0131na\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kardiyolog<\\/span>\\u00a0ad\\u0131 verilir.<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Kardiyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri kalp sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 korumak ve var olan kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 te\\u015fhis ve tedavi etmek i\\u00e7in \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmaktad\\u0131r. Kardiyak rehabilitasyon, koroner yo\\u011fun bak\\u0131m ve anjiyo laboratuvarlar\\u0131 bu \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalara destek vermektedir<\\/div>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Kardiyoloji Hangi Hastal\\u0131klar \\u0130le \\u0130lgilenir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Dola\\u015f\\u0131m sisteminin amac\\u0131, doku ve organlar\\u0131n \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fabilmesi i\\u00e7in gerekli oksijenin ta\\u015f\\u0131nmas\\u0131d\\u0131r. Kardiyolojik hastal\\u0131klar, yaln\\u0131zca kalbi ve damarlar\\u0131 de\\u011fil t\\u00fcm v\\u00fccudu etkilerler. Kardiyolojik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n baz\\u0131 ortak belirtileri bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Kardiyolojik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n belirtileri \\u015f\\u00f6yle s\\u0131ralanabilir:<\\/div><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcste bask\\u0131 hissi, a\\u011fr\\u0131 veya yanma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kollar, sol omuz, dirsekler, \\u00e7ene ve s\\u0131rtta a\\u011fr\\u0131 veya rahat\\u0131zl\\u0131k<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcste s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fma ve nefes darl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Bay\\u0131lma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Bulant\\u0131 ve yorgunluk<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">So\\u011fuk terleme<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp ritminde d\\u00fczensizlik, \\u00e7arp\\u0131nt\\u0131, d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck ya da y\\u00fcksek nab\\u0131z<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Tansiyonda d\\u00fczensizlik, y\\u00fcksek kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">H\\u0131zl\\u0131 yorulma<\\/li><\\/ul><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu belirtilere ek olarak dola\\u015f\\u0131m bozuklu\\u011funa sebep olan t\\u0131kal\\u0131 bir damar varsa, o damar\\u0131n besledi\\u011fi organ ve dokularda \\u015fikayetler g\\u00f6zlenebilir. Damarla ili\\u015fkili organlarda g\\u00fc\\u00e7s\\u00fczl\\u00fck, uyu\\u015fma, a\\u011fr\\u0131 ve so\\u011fukluk g\\u00f6zlemlenebilir.\\u00a0<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu belirtilerle kendini g\\u00f6steren ve kardiyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn ilgilendi\\u011fi ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca hastal\\u0131klar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/div><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Do\\u011fu\\u015ftan gelen (Konjenital) kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Aritmiler<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Damar sertli\\u011fi (Ateroskleroz)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Y\\u00fcksek kolesterol ve trigliserid<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hipertansiyon<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Angina (G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ani kalp durmas\\u0131.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp yetmezli\\u011fi\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp krizi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kan p\\u0131ht\\u0131lar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Koroner arter hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Perikardit (Kalp zar\\u0131 iltihab\\u0131)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Myokardit (Kalp kas\\u0131 iltihaplanmas\\u0131)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Endokardit (Kalp kapaklar\\u0131 ve kalp i\\u00e7 zar\\u0131 iltihab\\u0131)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp kapak\\u00e7\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 sorunlar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kardiyojenik \\u015fok<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp anomalileri<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kardiyomiyopati<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Aortunuzla ilgili sorunlar (anevrizma, stenoz)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Arterlerinizle ilgili problemler (Periferik Arter Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, Subklavian Arter Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, Renal Arter Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, Koroner Arter Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Fel\\u00e7<\\/li><\\/ul><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kardiyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, ani ya da k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcre i\\u00e7inde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan (akut), daha uzun zaman i\\u00e7inde geli\\u015fen (kronik) ve do\\u011fu\\u015ftan gelen (konjenital) kardiyovask\\u00fcler rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n t\\u00fcm\\u00fcyle ilgilenmektedir.\\u00a0 Kardiyovask\\u00fcler rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n t\\u00fcr\\u00fcne ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olaraktedavi t\\u00fcr ve s\\u00fcreleri farkl\\u0131l\\u0131k g\\u00f6stermektedir.<\\/div>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Giri\\u015fimsel Olmayan \\u0130\\u015flemler\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hastal\\u0131k ve risk taramas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">2-D, doppler ve renkli doppler ekokardiografileri\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Stres ekokardiografisi\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Stres Elektrografisi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">24 saat EKG ve kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131 izlemi\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalp sintigrafisi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Multidedekt\\u00f6r BT ile kalsiyum taramas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">2-D, doppler ve renkli doppler ekokardiografileri\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">BT koroner anjiografi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kardiyak MR<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Giri\\u015fimsel \\u0130\\u015flemler\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kardiyak kateterizasyon\\/Anjiyogram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Koroner stent yerle\\u015ftirme, atrektomi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Perk\\u00fctan koroner giri\\u015fim (PCI)\\/Anjiyoplasti<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Septal ablasyon<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Atriyal septal defekt kapatma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Aort balon valvuloplasti<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Mitral balon valvoplasti<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sol atriyal apendiks kapatma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Patent foramen ovale kapatma<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"K\",\"status_1\":\"1\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-heart-beat-alt\"}', '2023-12-12 07:34:45', '2023-12-27 16:04:56'),
