(522, 522, 86, 79, 1, 'Periodontoloji', 17, 'periodontoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Periodontoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Periodontoloji<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">, di\\u015f eti hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve \\u00e7ene kemi\\u011fi ile ilgili sorunlar\\u0131n te\\u015fhisi, tedavisi ve \\u00f6nlenmesi \\u00fczerine odaklanan di\\u015f hekimli\\u011fi dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Periodontoloji birimi; sa\\u011flam di\\u015flerin sadece iyi di\\u015f yap\\u0131s\\u0131na de\\u011fil, ayn\\u0131 zamanda sa\\u011flam di\\u015f etlerine ve \\u00e7ene kemi\\u011fine de ba\\u011fl\\u0131 oldu\\u011funu g\\u00f6sterir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Periodontal hastal\\u0131klar,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">di\\u015f etlerinin iltihaplanmas\\u0131na neden olur ve tedavi edilmezse di\\u015f kayb\\u0131na yol a\\u00e7abilir. Erken te\\u015fhis ve uygun tedavi, di\\u015f eti hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u00f6nlenmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Periodontoloji uzmanlar\\u0131, hastalar\\u0131n a\\u011fz\\u0131n\\u0131n genel sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 de\\u011ferlendirir, di\\u015f etlerini ve destekleyici dokular\\u0131 inceleyerek sorunlar\\u0131 te\\u015fhis eder ve uygun tedavi planlar\\u0131n\\u0131 olu\\u015fturur. Tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri aras\\u0131nda di\\u015f ta\\u015f\\u0131 temizli\\u011fi, ila\\u00e7 tedavisi veya cerrahi m\\u00fcdahaleler bulunabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Di\\u015f eti sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n, genel v\\u00fccut sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00fczerinde de etkileri oldu\\u011fu bilinmektedir. Bu y\\u00fczden d\\u00fczenli di\\u015f hekimi kontrolleri ve iyi a\\u011f\\u0131z hijyeni, sadece a\\u011fz\\u0131n\\u0131z\\u0131n de\\u011fil, t\\u00fcm v\\u00fccudunuzun sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 korumada \\u00f6nemli bir rol oynar.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Periodontal Hastal\\u0131klar Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Gingivitis:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Ba\\u015flang\\u0131\\u00e7 d\\u00fczeyindeki di\\u015f eti iltihab\\u0131d\\u0131r. Genellikle di\\u015f etlerinde f\\u0131r\\u00e7alarken veya spontane kanama ile kendisini g\\u00f6sterir. Di\\u015f eti \\u015fi\\u015fmesi, k\\u0131zarmas\\u0131 s\\u0131k g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen belirtiler aras\\u0131ndad\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Periodontitis:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Gingivitisin ilerlemesi ile ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kar. Di\\u015fi yerinde tutan kemi\\u011fin di\\u015f eti iltihab\\u0131ndan etkilenmesi ile karakterizedir. \\u0130leri derece periodontitis di\\u015f eti \\u00e7ekilmesi ve di\\u015flerin sallanarak d\\u00fc\\u015fmesi riskini beraberinde getirmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Di\\u015f eti \\u00e7ekilmesi:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Bir\\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 fakt\\u00f6re ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak (\\u0130ltihap, sert f\\u0131r\\u00e7alama, di\\u015f s\\u0131kma vb.) di\\u015f eti \\u00e7ekilmesi meydana gelebilir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Gummy Smile (Di\\u015f eti g\\u00fcl\\u00fcmsemesi):<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Hasta g\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde veya normal konu\\u015fma esnas\\u0131nda di\\u015f etlerinin g\\u00fcl\\u00fc\\u015f esteti\\u011fini bozacak \\u015fekilde fazla g\\u00f6z\\u00fckmesidir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Periodontal Tedaviler Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Subgingival k\\u00fcretaj tedavisi:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Di\\u015f etlerinin alt\\u0131nda yer alan bakteriyel toksinler, plaklar ve iltihabi dokular\\u0131n lokal uyu\\u015fturma alt\\u0131nda temizlenmesidir. Subgingival k\\u00fcretaj tedavisi ile di\\u015flerin \\u00e7evresindeki kemik erimesinin durdurulmas\\u0131 ve di\\u015flerin iltihaba ba\\u011fl\\u0131 kayb\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u00f6nlenmesi hedeflenir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Serbest di\\u015f eti grefti operasyonu:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Di\\u015f etinin koruyucu k\\u0131sm\\u0131 olan \\u2018yap\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131k di\\u015f eti\\u2019 eksikli\\u011finde tercih edilen bir y\\u00f6ntemdir. Periodontal cerrahi prosed\\u00fcrler ile yap\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131k di\\u015f eti tekrar olu\\u015fturularak di\\u015flerin \\u00f6mr\\u00fcn\\u00fcn uzat\\u0131lmas\\u0131 hedeflenir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ba\\u011f dokusu grefti operasyonu:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Di\\u015f eti \\u00e7ekilmesi olan vakalarda kaybedilen di\\u015f etinin yeniden olu\\u015fturulmas\\u0131 amac\\u0131yla uygulanan bir y\\u00f6ntemdir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Flap operasyonu ve kemik grefti uygulamalar\\u0131:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Kemik erimesi olan vakalarda di\\u015f eti alt\\u0131ndaki ve kemik \\u00e7evresindeki iltihabi dokular\\u0131n temizlenmesi ile birlikte yeniden kemik dokusu kazanabilmek amac\\u0131yla greft uygulamas\\u0131 yap\\u0131labilmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Gingivektomi\\/Gingivoplasti i\\u015flemleri:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\">\\u00a0Gummy smile (Di\\u015f eti g\\u00fcl\\u00fcmsemesi) veya d\\u00fczensiz di\\u015f etine sahip bireylerde simetrik ve estetik di\\u015f eti g\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fc olu\\u015fturmak amac\\u0131yla gingivektomi\\/gingivoplasti uygulamalar\\u0131 yap\\u0131labilmektedir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"P\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-12 10:03:05', '2023-12-27 16:02:33'),
