(534, 534, 87, 82, 1, 'Intraoperatif 3 Tesla MR', 5, 'intraoperatif-3-tesla-mr', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Intraoperatif 3 Tesla MR\",\"content_1\":\"<p>\\u0130ntraoperatif 3 Tesla MR, operasyon s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcrl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc y\\u00fcksek ve h\\u0131zl\\u0131 veriler elde edilmesine olanak sa\\u011flayan bir g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme cihaz\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Hangi Hastal\\u0131klarda Kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\u00d6zellikle beyin operasyonlar\\u0131 s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme yaparak, cerraha beynin ula\\u015f\\u0131lmas\\u0131 zor b\\u00f6lgelerindeki t\\u00fcm\\u00f6r\\u00fcn b\\u00fcy\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc ve y\\u00f6n\\u00fc konusunda bilgi verir. B\\u00f6ylece cerrah, operasyonun sonlanmas\\u0131 ya da devam etmesi konusunda karar verir.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Nas\\u0131l uygulan\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p>Cihaz, ameliyathaneye ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131 bir alanda bulunur. Operasyon s\\u00fcrerken ihtiya\\u00e7 duyuldu\\u011fu anda anestezi etkisi alt\\u0131ndaki hastan\\u0131n \\u00e7ekiminin yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flar.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Uygulanan bu y\\u00f6ntem, \\u00f6zellikle beyin operasyonlar\\u0131nda hayati \\u00f6nem ta\\u015f\\u0131r. Cerrah, ihtiya\\u00e7 duydu\\u011fu her noktada hastay\\u0131 uyand\\u0131rmadan ve operasyon b\\u00f6lgesini kapatmadan gerekli tetkikleri yapabilir. Kal\\u0131nt\\u0131lar\\u0131n t\\u00fcm\\u00fcyle temizlenememesi, fonksiyonel alanlarda hasar olu\\u015fmas\\u0131, hatal\\u0131 b\\u00f6lgelere i\\u015flem yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gibi riskler ortadan kalkabildi\\u011fi i\\u00e7in ikinci bir operasyon ihtimalini d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcr\\u00fcr.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\",\"image_1_8546\":[\"intraoperatif-3-tesla-mr_31_.jpg\",\"99\"]}', '2023-12-18 06:36:49', '2023-12-18 06:39:06'),
