(550, 550, 84, 68, 1, 'Acıbadem', 7, 'acibadem', 1, '', '{\"image_1_628076\":[\"acibademm_29_.jpg\",\"99\"],\"name_1\":\"Ac\\u0131badem\",\"address_1\":\" Yukar\\u0131 Dikmen Mahallesi Tevfik K\\u0131\\u015f Caddesi No:6 \\u00c7ankaya\\/Ankara\",\"link_1\":\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/\",\"e-posta_1\":\"albania@acibadem.com\",\"phone_1\":\" +90 312 593 4444\",\"status_1\":\"1\",\"description_1\":\"<p>Ac\\u0131badem, sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sekt\\u00f6r\\u00fcnde \\u00f6nc\\u00fc ve k\\u00f6kl\\u00fc bir kurum olup, hasta memnuniyetini \\u00f6n planda tutan bir sa\\u011fl\\u0131k hizmeti sa\\u011flay\\u0131c\\u0131s\\u0131d\\u0131r. Geli\\u015fmi\\u015f t\\u0131bbi teknolojiyi benimseyerek, alan\\u0131nda uzman hekim kadrosuyla bir araya gelerek hastalar\\u0131na geni\\u015f bir yelpazede kaliteli ve ki\\u015fiye \\u00f6zel sa\\u011fl\\u0131k hizmetleri sunmaktad\\u0131r. Hasta odakl\\u0131 yakla\\u015f\\u0131m\\u0131yla bilinen Ac\\u0131badem, modern t\\u0131bb\\u0131n en son geli\\u015fmelerini takip ederek hastalar\\u0131n\\u0131n ihtiya\\u00e7lar\\u0131na uygun tedavi se\\u00e7enekleri sunmay\\u0131 ama\\u00e7lamaktad\\u0131r. Sa\\u011fl\\u0131k hizmetlerindeki \\u00fcst\\u00fcn kalite ve g\\u00fcvenilirlik anlay\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131yla tan\\u0131nan Ac\\u0131badem, hastalar\\u0131na konforlu bir tedavi ortam\\u0131 sa\\u011flayarak sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir ya\\u015fam i\\u00e7in gerekli olan deste\\u011fi sunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\"}', '2023-12-18 07:52:16', '2023-12-28 13:52:59'),
