(554, 554, 86, 79, 1, 'Genel Cerrahi', 8, 'genel-cerrahi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Genel Cerrahi\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Genel Cerrahi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, mevcut hastane, t\\u0131p merkezi ve polikliniklerde hasta muayene ve tedavisini ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirmek \\u00fczere organize olmu\\u015ftur.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Obezite Cerrahisi\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obezite hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 insan v\\u00fccudunda \\u00e7ok say\\u0131da organ\\u0131 etkilemektedir. Bu y\\u00fczden tedavisinin de multidisipliner yani birden \\u00e7ok bran\\u015f\\u0131n birlikte uyum i\\u00e7erisinde \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 bir ortamda planlan\\u0131p yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gerekir. 112Life olarak obezitenin tedavisinde kulland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131m\\u0131z y\\u00f6ntemlerden biri olan obezite cerrahisinde mide band\\u0131, gastrik sleeve ve gastrik bypass y\\u00f6ntemleri kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Endokrin Cerrahisi\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Endokrin cerrahisi, tiroid, paratiroid, adrenal ve gastrointestinal ile pankreas\\u0131n n\\u00f6roendokrin t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rlerini i\\u00e7eren cerrahi aland\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Gastroentroloji Cerrahisi\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastrointestinal Sistem Cerrahisi\\u2019nde \\u00f6zefagus ve mide-duodenum, ince ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak, kal\\u0131n ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak ve rektuma ait hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n cerrahi tedavileri yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Meme Cerrahisi\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life\'da meme kanserinin tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"G\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-surgeon\"}', '2023-12-18 08:23:31', '2023-12-27 16:07:28'),
