(558, 558, 86, 79, 1, 'Ortopedi ve Travmatoloji', 16, 'ortopedi-ve-travmatoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Ortopedi ve Travmatoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Travma; d\\u00fc\\u015fme, spor yaralanmas\\u0131, i\\u015f kazas\\u0131 veya trafik kazas\\u0131 gibi etkenlerle \\u00e7o\\u011fu zaman bir s\\u00fcrpriz ile kar\\u015f\\u0131m\\u0131za \\u00e7\\u0131kar. Meydana gelen hasar, travman\\u0131n \\u015fiddetine g\\u00f6re, basit bir yumu\\u015fak doku ezilmesinden b\\u00fcy\\u00fck kemiklerde par\\u00e7al\\u0131 k\\u0131r\\u0131klara kadar de\\u011fi\\u015febilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Travma hastas\\u0131n\\u0131n kar\\u015f\\u0131lanmas\\u0131 ve ilk m\\u00fcdahalelerinin ilgili uzman taraf\\u0131ndan yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131 hayati \\u00f6nem ta\\u015f\\u0131maktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131n tedavisinde yakla\\u015f\\u0131m ve ameliyat y\\u00f6ntemleri s\\u00fcrekli yenilenmektedir. Ama\\u00e7 hastay\\u0131 en k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcrede ve sorunsuz olarak g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ya\\u015fam\\u0131na d\\u00f6nd\\u00fcrmektir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Ortopedi ve Travmatoloji Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Artroskopi ve Spor Yaralanmalar\\u0131 (Diz-omuz)<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Artroskopik diz ameliyatlar\\u0131 kapsam\\u0131nda; menisektomi veya meniskus tamiri, artroskopik \\u00f6n \\u00e7apraz ba\\u011f, arka \\u00e7apraz ba\\u011f, i\\u00e7-d\\u0131\\u015f yan ba\\u011f ve kombine ba\\u011f yaralanmalar\\u0131nda rekonst\\u00fcr\\u00fcksiyon ameliyatlar\\u0131, k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak yaralanmalar\\u0131nda, artroskopik mikrofrakt\\u00fcr veya osteochondral k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak nakli, omuz \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda; artroskopik bankart tamiri, subakromiyal s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fma sendromu, omuz eklem osteoartriti, labral y\\u0131rt\\u0131k eksizyonu-tamiri, k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak ameliyatlar\\u0131 ve rotator cuff tamiri yer almaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Omurga Cerrahisi (Spinal cerrahi)<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Omurgada do\\u011fu\\u015ftan veya sonradan olu\\u015fan; skolyoz, kifoz (kamburluk)\\u00a0 Schuermann Kifozu, spondilolistezis, spinal stenoz, omurga ya\\u015flanmas\\u0131 sorunlar\\u0131, ankilozan spondilit, osteoporoza(kemik erimesi), k\\u0131r\\u0131klar, \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131klar omurga yaralanmalar\\u0131 ve omurga enfeksiyonlar\\u0131 Omurga Cerrahisi\\u2019nin ilgilendi\\u011fi alanlardan baz\\u0131lard\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Ortopedisi ve Travmatolojisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">16 ya\\u015f alt\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n do\\u011fumsal kal\\u00e7a \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, \\u00e7arp\\u0131k ayak, serebral paralizi, myelomeningosel, do\\u011fumsal deformiteler, d\\u00fcz tabanl\\u0131k, t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rler, geli\\u015fimsel bozukluklar ve k\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n takip ve tedavisi ile ilgilenmektedir.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ayak ve Ayak Bile\\u011fi Cerrahisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ayak ve ayak bile\\u011finin dejeneratif hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, spor yaralanmalar\\u0131, k\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131, ba\\u011f y\\u0131rt\\u0131lmalar\\u0131, k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak yaralanmalar\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavisi ile u\\u011fra\\u015fmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ortopedik Onkoloji<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">T\\u00fcm kemik, kas ve yumu\\u015fak dokular ba\\u015fta olmak \\u00fczere; ekstremitelerin her t\\u00fcrl\\u00fc t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rlerinin medikal ve cerrahi tedavisi\\u00a0 ile ilgilenmektedir.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Omuz ve Dirsek Cerrahisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Omuz ve dirse\\u011fin artrozlar\\u0131, rotator k\\u0131l\\u0131f hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 tekrarlayan \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131klar, a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 kullan\\u0131ma veya travmaya ba\\u011fl\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n artroskopik ve a\\u00e7\\u0131k cerrahi y\\u00f6ntemlerle tedavisini sa\\u011flamaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Artroz-kire\\u00e7lenmeler<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gonartroz ve koxartroz tedavisi, kal\\u00e7a-diz protezleri, protez enfeksiyonu ve gev\\u015femelerde revizyon ameliyatlar\\u0131, periacetabular ve y\\u00fcksek tibial rekonst\\u00fcr\\u00fcktif kemik ameliyatlar\\u0131 bu b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn ilgilendi\\u011fi alanlard\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ekstremite Cerrahisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kol-bacak kemik uzatma ameliyatlar\\u0131 ba\\u015fta olmak \\u00fczere; kemik deformiteleri, k\\u0131r\\u0131k kaynamamas\\u0131, kemik enfeksiyonlar\\u0131 ve external fixator uygulamalar\\u0131 ile ilgilenmektedir.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kal\\u00e7a K\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00d6zellikle ya\\u015fl\\u0131 hasta grubunun maruz kalaca\\u011f\\u0131 travmalar sonras\\u0131 tedavi gerektiren durumlard\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">El ve \\u00dcst Ekstremite Cerrahisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El, el bile\\u011fi, dirsek ve kol ile ilgili sorunlar\\u0131 bulunan hastalar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavilerinin planlanmas\\u0131 ve uygulanmas\\u0131 ile ilgilenir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00dcst Ekstremite Cerrahisi Servisinin klinik aktiviteleri aras\\u0131nda \\u00fcst ekstremiteyi ilgilendiren akut yumu\\u015fak doku travmalar\\u0131n\\u0131n ( tendon kesileri, periferik sinir kesileri, ezilme ve s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fma sonucu olu\\u015fan cilt ve kas dokusu kay\\u0131plar\\u0131 vb), amputasyonlar\\u0131n ( mikrocerrahi y\\u00f6ntemler kullanarak replantasyonlar, revask\\u00fclarizasyonlar vb), el, elbile\\u011fi, \\u00f6nkol, dirsek ve kolda meydana gelen k\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131n de\\u011ferlendirilmesi, koordinasyonu, tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi yer al\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00dcst Ekstremite Cerrahisi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El cerrahisinin ge\\u00e7 rekonstr\\u00fcksiyonuna y\\u00f6nelik; travma ve kire\\u00e7lenmeler sonras\\u0131 do\\u011fumsal n\\u00f6romusk\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n ve t\\u00fcm\\u00f6ral durumlar\\u0131n \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fclmesinde el bile\\u011fi-dirsek artroskopisi, k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck eklem protezi uygulamalar\\u0131, tendon transferleri, mikrocerrahi doku transferleri bu b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Boyun F\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Boyun f\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, boyun omurlar\\u0131 aras\\u0131ndaki hareketi sa\\u011flayan diskin bozulup, i\\u00e7indeki k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak maddenin ta\\u015farak omurilik veya sinirlere bask\\u0131 yapmas\\u0131yla meydana gelir.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Skolyoz\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Skolyoz omurgan\\u0131n yana e\\u011frili\\u011fi ya da kendi etraf\\u0131na d\\u00f6nmesine denir. Skolyoz bir\\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011fa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilir. Skolyoz genellikle ergenlik d\\u00f6neminde kendini g\\u00f6stermektedir. Omurgan\\u0131n do\\u011fumsal anomalililerine veya kas ve sinir hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak da geli\\u015febilir.\\u00a0<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kifoz\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kifoz, \\u00f6zellikle s\\u0131rttaki kamburlu\\u011fun normal de\\u011ferler d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 derecede ilerlemesi ile meydana gelir. Kifoz, ki\\u015finin duru\\u015f bozuklu\\u011funa veya omurga hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak geli\\u015febilir.\\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Diz A\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Diz a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131 \\u00e7ok s\\u0131k kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan a\\u011fr\\u0131 \\u00e7e\\u015fitlerinden biridir. Bunlar spor yaralanmalar\\u0131na, ya\\u015flanmaya, k\\u0131k\\u0131rdak a\\u015f\\u0131nmas\\u0131na, romatizmal hastal\\u0131klara ya da enfeksiyonlara ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015febilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"O\",\"status_1\":\"1\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-bone\"}', '2023-12-18 08:27:12', '2023-12-27 16:03:04'),
