(566, 566, 89, 79, 1, 'A Vitamini', 0, 'a-vitamini', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"A Vitamini\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">A vitamini, karaci\\u011ferde depolanan ve ya\\u011fda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnen bir vitamin t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Besinlerde 2 tip A vitamini bulunur.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Bunlardan ilki \\u00f6nceden olu\\u015fturulmu\\u015f (premade) A vitaminidir.<\\/span>\\u00a0Ayn\\u0131 zamanda\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">retinol<\\/span>\\u00a0ad\\u0131yla da bilinir ve aktif bir A vitamini tipidir. Et, bal\\u0131k, k\\u00fcmes hayvanlar\\u0131, tam ya\\u011fl\\u0131 s\\u00fct ve s\\u00fct \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri gibi hayvansal g\\u0131dalarda bulunur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130kinci A vitamini tipi ise provitamin A olarak bilinir<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve meyveyle sebze gibi bitki bazl\\u0131 g\\u0131dalarda bulunur. \\u0130kinci tipin di\\u011fer ad\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">karotenoidlerdir<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve bunlar yiyeceklere koyu rengini verirler, yani pigmentlerdir. Bu tip aktif A vitamini formuna d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015febilir. 500\'den fazla bilinen karotenoid vard\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">En yayg\\u0131n provitamin A tipinin ad\\u0131 beta-karotendir. Vitaminler genel olarak ya v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan hi\\u00e7 \\u00fcretilmeyen ya da olumsuz sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131n\\u0131 veya hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 \\u00f6nlemek i\\u00e7in yetersiz miktarda \\u00fcretilebilen temel besinlerdir. Bu sebeple uygun beslenmeyle ve sadece t\\u0131bbi a\\u00e7\\u0131dan gerekli oldu\\u011fu durumlarda vitamin takviyeleriyle v\\u00fccuda vitamin sa\\u011flamak gereklidir. A vitamini kaps\\u00fcl olarak ve diyet takviyesi olarak sat\\u0131lan \\u00fcr\\u00fcnler halinde de mevcuttur. \\u00c7o\\u011fu zaman retinil asetat veya retinil palmitat (\\u00f6nceden olu\\u015fturulmu\\u015f A vitamini) halinde, beta-karoten (provitamin A) halinde veya ikisinin bir kombinasyonu \\u015feklinde takviyelere eklenir.<\\/p><div><br><\\/div>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"A Vitaminin Faydalar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">A vitamini di\\u015f, kemik, yumu\\u015fak doku, mukus zarlar\\u0131 ve cilt yap\\u0131lar\\u0131n\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir \\u015fekilde olu\\u015fturulmas\\u0131na ve korunmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur. G\\u00f6z retinas\\u0131nda renk veren pigmentleri \\u00fcretir.<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">A vitamini, \\u00f6zellikle d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kta iyi g\\u00f6r\\u00fc\\u015f elde etmeyi sa\\u011flar. Ayn\\u0131 zamanda sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 hamilelik ve hamilelik sonras\\u0131 anne s\\u00fct\\u00fc ile emzirmede b\\u00fcy\\u00fck rol oynar.<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Beta-karoten tipi A vitaminleri antioksidand\\u0131r. Antioksidanlar h\\u00fccreleri serbest radikal ad\\u0131 verilen maddelerin neden oldu\\u011fu hasarlardan korur.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Serbest radikallerin baz\\u0131 kronik ve uzun s\\u00fcrede seyreden hastal\\u0131klara katk\\u0131da bulundu\\u011fu ve ya\\u015flanmada rol oynad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 bilinmektedir. Beta-karoten i\\u00e7eren g\\u0131da kaynaklar\\u0131n\\u0131n t\\u00fcketilmesi kanser riskini azaltabilir. Ancak Beta-karoten i\\u00e7eren takviyelerin kanser riskini azaltmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"A Vitamini Eksikli\\u011fi\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccutta A vitamininin eksik olmas\\u0131 durumunda \\u00e7e\\u015fitli g\\u00f6z ve g\\u00f6rme sorunlar\\u0131 ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilir. Bu sorunlar aras\\u0131nda d\\u00fczelebilir gece k\\u00f6rl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc ve geri d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fc olmayan kornea hasar\\u0131 olan kseroftalmi bulunur. A vitamini eksikli\\u011fi ayn\\u0131 zamanda hiperkeratoza veya kuru, pullu cilde yol a\\u00e7abilir.<\\/p><div><br><\\/div>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"A Vitamini Fazlas\\u0131\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">A Vitamininin fazlas\\u0131 da hastalanmaya neden olabilir. Y\\u00fcksek dozlarda A vitamini do\\u011fum kusurlar\\u0131na neden olabilir. Akut A vitamini zehirlenmesi genellikle bir birey taraf\\u0131ndan birka\\u00e7 y\\u00fcz bin IU, yani uluslararas\\u0131 \\u00fcnite A vitamini al\\u0131nd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kar. Kronik vitamin A zehirlenmesi ise d\\u00fczenli olarak g\\u00fcnde 25.000 IU\\u2019dan fazla alan yeti\\u015fkinlerde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bebekler ve \\u00e7ocuklar A vitaminine kar\\u015f\\u0131 daha duyarl\\u0131d\\u0131rlar. Daha k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck dozlarda A vitamini veya retinol gibi A vitamini i\\u00e7eren \\u00fcr\\u00fcnler ald\\u0131ktan sonra da hasta olabilirler.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ok miktarda al\\u0131nan beta-karoten bireyleri genelde hasta etmez. Ancak, y\\u00fcksek miktarda beta-karoten cilt rengini sar\\u0131 veya turuncuya d\\u00f6nd\\u00fcrebilir. Beta-karoten t\\u00fcketimi azal\\u0131nca cilt rengi normale d\\u00f6ner.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"A Vitamini \\u0130\\u00e7eren Besinler Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">2 tip A vitamini bulndu\\u011fundan, A vitamini kaynaklar\\u0131 2 kategoriye ayr\\u0131labilir.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00d6nceden olu\\u015fturulmu\\u015f A Vitamini<\\/span>\\u00a0alabal\\u0131k, beyaz peynir, ci\\u011fer, kral uskumru, morina ci\\u011feri ya\\u011f\\u0131, somon, tavuk ci\\u011feri, tereya\\u011f\\u0131, yumurta sar\\u0131s\\u0131, ya\\u011fl\\u0131 s\\u00fct, peynir, krema, b\\u00f6brek, pisi bal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve bal\\u0131k ya\\u011f\\u0131 gibi\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">hayvansal g\\u0131dalardan elde edilir.<\\/span>\\u00a0<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Provitamin A<\\/span>\\u00a0ise balkaba\\u011f\\u0131, brokoli, havu\\u00e7, \\u0131spanak, kara lahana, karahindiba ye\\u015fillikleri, k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 biber, lahana, maydanoz, paz\\u0131, br\\u00fcksel lahanas\\u0131, tatl\\u0131 patates, portakal gibi sar\\u0131 meyveler ve koyu ye\\u015fil yaprakl\\u0131\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">sebzelerde bol miktarda bulunur.<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sebze ya da meyvenin rengi ne kadar koyuysa, o kadar \\u00e7ok beta-karoten i\\u00e7erir. Bitkisel beta-karoten kaynaklar\\u0131 ya\\u011f ve kolesterol i\\u00e7ermez. Bu kaynaklar ya\\u011fla birlikte yenilirse, onlardan elde edilen A vitamininin emilimi artar. V\\u00fccudun A vitamini de dahil olmak \\u00fczere di\\u011fer \\u00f6nemli vitaminler i\\u00e7in de g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ihtiyac\\u0131n\\u0131 elde etmenin en iyi yolu \\u00e7ok \\u00e7e\\u015fitli meyve, sebze, takviye edilmi\\u015f s\\u00fct \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri, kuru fasulye gibi baklagiller, mercimek ve kepekli tah\\u0131llar ile beslenmektir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"A\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 15:19:26', '2023-12-20 15:43:46'),
