(570, 570, 89, 79, 1, 'B12 Vitamini Eksikliği', 2, 'b12-vitamini-eksikligi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"B12 Vitamini Eksikli\\u011fi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccut i\\u00e7erisinde\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini seviyesi<\\/span>\\u00a0\\u00e7ok azald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan duruma\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 eksikli\\u011fi<\\/span>\\u00a0denilir. Bu durum geri d\\u00f6nd\\u00fcr\\u00fclemez n\\u00f6rolojik sorunlara yol a\\u00e7abilir. \\u0130nsan v\\u00fccudu d\\u00f6rt y\\u0131l yeterli olacak kadar\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitaminini<\\/span>\\u00a0depolayabilir ve fazla, istenmeyen k\\u0131sm\\u0131n\\u0131 idrar ile d\\u0131\\u015far\\u0131 atar.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0hayvan etinde do\\u011fal olarak bulunur ve sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir diyetle\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 eksikli\\u011fi belirtilerinden<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0kolayca ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmak m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr. Ancak \\u00e7e\\u015fitli nedenlerle et t\\u00fcketmeyen insanlar ek\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 vitamini takviyesi\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">alabilirler. Bu vitamin end\\u00fcstriyel olarak sadece bakteriyel fermantasyon sentezi ile \\u00fcretilebilir.\\u00a0<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"B12 Vitamini Nedir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0suda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnebilen, DNA sentezinde, ya\\u011f asitleri ve amino asitlerin v\\u00fccut i\\u00e7inde kullan\\u0131m\\u0131nda oynad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 rol sayesinde v\\u00fccut i\\u00e7erisindeki hemen her h\\u00fccrenin ihtiya\\u00e7 duydu\\u011fu bir B vitamini t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sinir sisteminin sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, beyin fonksiyonlar\\u0131 ve alyuvarlar\\u0131n \\u00fcretimi i\\u00e7in gereklidir. Kobalamin, B12 vitamininin bir di\\u011fer ad\\u0131d\\u0131r.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini,\\u00a0<\\/span>en b\\u00fcy\\u00fck ve yap\\u0131sal olarak en karma\\u015f\\u0131k vitamindir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Vitaminler genel olarak ya v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan hi\\u00e7 \\u00fcretilmeyen ya da olumsuz sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131n\\u0131 veya hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 \\u00f6nlemek i\\u00e7in yetersiz miktarda \\u00fcretilebilen temel besinlerdir. Bu sebeple uygun beslenmeyle ve sadece t\\u0131bbi a\\u00e7\\u0131dan gerekli oldu\\u011fu durumlarda vitamin takviyeleriyle v\\u00fccuda vitamin sa\\u011flamak gereklidir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"B12 Vitaminin Faydalar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, beynin ve sinir sisteminin normal i\\u015flevini s\\u00fcrd\\u00fcrmesi i\\u00e7in \\u00e7ok \\u00f6nemlidir. Ayr\\u0131ca alyuvarlar\\u0131n olu\\u015fumunda \\u00f6nemli bir rol oynar. DNA\'n\\u0131n olu\\u015fturulmas\\u0131na ve d\\u00fczenlenmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccuttaki hemen her h\\u00fccrenin metabolizmas\\u0131, ya\\u011f asitlerinin sentezinde ve enerji \\u00fcretiminde rol oynayan B12 vitaminine ba\\u011fl\\u0131d\\u0131r.\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini<\\/span>, insan v\\u00fccudunun folik asidi emmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olarak depolanan enerjinin sal\\u0131nmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flar.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130nsan v\\u00fccudu hemen her dakika s\\u00fcrekli milyonlarca alyuvar h\\u00fccresi \\u00fcretir. Bu h\\u00fccrelerin \\u00e7o\\u011falmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in B12 vitamini gereklidir. B12 vitamini seviyeleri \\u00e7ok d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fckse alyuvar h\\u00fccrelerinin \\u00fcretimi azal\\u0131r. Alyuvar h\\u00fccresi say\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131n d\\u00fc\\u015fmesi d\\u00fc\\u015ferse anemiye yol a\\u00e7ar.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yap\\u0131lan ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar sonucunda 14 ya\\u015f \\u00fczerindeki bireylerin g\\u00fcnde 2, 4 mikrogram (mcg)\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini<\\/span>\\u00a0t\\u00fcketmeleri tavsiye edilmektedir. Hamile kad\\u0131nlarda bu miktar 2.6 mikrogram iken anne s\\u00fct\\u00fc ile bebek emziren kad\\u0131nlarda bu miktar 2.8 mikrograma \\u00e7\\u0131kmaktad\\u0131r. A\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 B12 vitamini al\\u0131m\\u0131 toksik veya zararl\\u0131 nitelikler g\\u00f6stermemi\\u015ftir. Bununla birlikte vitamin takviyesi almaya ba\\u015flamadan \\u00f6nce her zaman doktora ba\\u015fvurulmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"B12 Vitamini Nelerde Bulunur?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 Vitaminini\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">bir\\u00e7ok besin kayna\\u011f\\u0131ndan elde edebilirsiniz.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 Vitamini\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">et \\u00e7ok hayvansal kaynakl\\u0131 besinlerde bulunur. Bitkilerde bulunmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in vegan tarz\\u0131 beslenen ki\\u015filerin, beslenmelerine dikkat etmesi gerekmektedir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 eksikli\\u011finin neden oldu\\u011fu ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sisteminin zay\\u0131flamas\\u0131, unutkanl\\u0131k gibi haf\\u0131za problemleri ve kans\\u0131zl\\u0131k gibi durumlar i\\u00e7in hayvansal g\\u0131da t\\u00fcketmeyen ki\\u015filer takviye \\u00fcr\\u00fcnlerden faydalanabilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B12 Vitamininin en \\u00e7ok bulundu\\u011fu besinler ise;\\u00a0<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Et<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">S\\u00fct<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Yumurta<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Peynir alt\\u0131 suyu gibi hayvansal besinlerdir.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Kimler B12 Eksikli\\u011fi Riski Ta\\u015f\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Diyetlerinde hayvansal g\\u0131da bulunmayan ki\\u015filer,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini eksikli\\u011fi\\u00a0<\\/span>riskiyle kar\\u015f\\u0131 kar\\u015f\\u0131yad\\u0131r. Hamilelik s\\u00fcreci ve sonras\\u0131nda emzirme d\\u00f6nemi vegan beslenmeden kaynaklanan B12 eksikli\\u011fini k\\u00f6t\\u00fcle\\u015ftirebilir. Bitki kaynakl\\u0131 g\\u0131dalar, insan sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 korumak i\\u00e7in yeterli B12 vitamini i\\u00e7ermezler.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Pernisiy\\u00f6z anemisi olan bireylerde\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitamini eksikli\\u011fi\\u00a0<\\/span>g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir. Pernisiy\\u00f6z anemisi kan\\u0131 etkileyen bir ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemi hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131d\\u0131r ve midede v\\u00fccudun\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 vitaminini\\u00a0<\\/span>emmesine izin veren bir protein olan intrinsik fakt\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcn (IF) yeterli miktarda bulunmamas\\u0131na neden olur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130nce ba\\u011f\\u0131rsa\\u011f\\u0131 cerrahi olarak k\\u0131salt\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f bireyler gibi ince ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak problemleri olanlar bulunur. Bu nedenle B12 vitamini v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan yeterli miktarda emilmeyebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Besinlerin emiliminin azalmas\\u0131na neden olan\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/gastrit\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">gastrit<\\/span><\\/a>,\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/colyak-hastaligi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00e7\\u00f6lyak hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">inflamatuar ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span>\\u00a0da\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B12 eksikli\\u011fine<\\/span>\\u00a0yol a\\u00e7abilir. Kronik alkolizm etkisi alt\\u0131nda olan bireyler de ayn\\u0131 nedenle B12 vitamini eksikli\\u011fi ya\\u015fayabilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"B\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 15:42:27', '2023-12-20 15:46:42'),
