(574, 574, 89, 79, 1, 'C Vitamini', 4, 'c-vitamini', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"C Vitamini\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ayn\\u0131 zamanda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">askorbik asit<\\/span>&nbsp;olarak bilinen&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini<\\/span>, insan v\\u00fccudunun, kan damarlar\\u0131, k\\u0131k\\u0131rdaklar\\u0131, kaslar\\u0131 ve kemiklerde bulunan kollajen proteini olu\\u015fturmak i\\u00e7in ihtiya\\u00e7 duydu\\u011fu bir vitamin t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;dokular\\u0131n olu\\u015fturulmas\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra v\\u00fccudunun \\u00e7e\\u015fitli yaralanmalardan sonra iyile\\u015fme s\\u00fcreci i\\u00e7in b\\u00fcy\\u00fck bir \\u00f6neme sahiptir. Askorbik asit bir monosakkarit t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr ve hemen b\\u00fct\\u00fcn canl\\u0131 dokular\\u0131nda bulunur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C vitamini, serbest radikaller olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131lan zararl\\u0131 molek\\u00fcllerin yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra toksik kimyasallar ve sigara duman\\u0131 gibi kirleticilerden kaynaklanan hasara kar\\u015f\\u0131 v\\u00fccudu koruyabilen birka\\u00e7 antioksidandan biridir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccutta olu\\u015fan&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/kanser-onkoloji\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kanser<\\/span><\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/kalp-hastaliklari\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kalp hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ve artrit gibi sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131n\\u0131n geli\\u015fmesine katk\\u0131da bulunaca\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in normal&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/beslenme-ve-diyet\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">diyetle&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>d\\u00fczenli ve yeterli&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 bu durumlar\\u0131n \\u00f6nlenmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fazla C vitamini normal \\u015fartlar alt\\u0131nda v\\u00fccuttan do\\u011frudan at\\u0131l\\u0131r ve depolanmaz. Bu nedenle normal \\u015fartlarda v\\u00fccutta a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 doz C vitamini birikmesi konusunda endi\\u015felenmeye gerek yoktur.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ancak her \\u015fart alt\\u0131nda v\\u00fccuda bir anda y\\u00fcksek dozlarda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>y\\u00fcklenmesinden kaynaklanacak mide yanmas\\u0131,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">mide bulant\\u0131s\\u0131, ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, mide kramplar\\u0131&nbsp;<\\/span>ve&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">diyare<\\/span>&nbsp;gibi olumsuz etkilerden ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmak i\\u00e7in g\\u00fcnde 2.000 miligraml\\u0131k g\\u00fcvenli \\u00fcst s\\u0131n\\u0131r\\u0131 a\\u015fmamak \\u00f6nemlidir. Bu g\\u00fcvenli \\u00fcst s\\u0131n\\u0131r\\u0131n a\\u015f\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ayn\\u0131 zamanda&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/bobrek-tasi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">b\\u00f6brek ta\\u015f\\u0131&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>riskini art\\u0131rabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"C Vitamininin Yararlar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130nsan v\\u00fccudu do\\u011fal olarak kendili\\u011finden&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>\\u00fcretmedi\\u011fi i\\u00e7in beslenme arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla do\\u011fal kaynaklardan v\\u00fccuda almak gereklidir. C vitamini v\\u00fccudun besinlerden ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 demirin sindirim sistemi taraf\\u0131ndan emilmesine ve daha sonra kullanmak \\u00fczere depolanmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uzmanlar, C vitamininin en g\\u00fcvenli ve v\\u00fccut i\\u00e7in en faydal\\u0131 besinlerden biri oldu\\u011funu ifade etmektedirler. C vitamininin faydalar\\u0131 aras\\u0131nda ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemini g\\u00fc\\u00e7lendirmek,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/kardiyovaskuler-cerrahi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kardiyovask\\u00fcler&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>hastal\\u0131klara,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/kadin-hastaliklari-ve-dogum\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">do\\u011fum<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;\\u00f6ncesi sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131na,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/goz-hastaliklari\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ve hatta cilt k\\u0131r\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131klar\\u0131na kar\\u015f\\u0131 koruma sa\\u011flamak say\\u0131labilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilen \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalar sonucunda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamininin<\\/span>&nbsp;stres nedeniyle ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemi zay\\u0131flam\\u0131\\u015f olan bireyler i\\u00e7in yararl\\u0131 oldu\\u011funu g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr. Alkol kullananlar\\u0131n, sigara i\\u00e7enlerin ve&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/obezite-tedavisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">obez&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>bireylerin v\\u00fccutlar\\u0131nda en h\\u0131zl\\u0131 t\\u00fckenen besin maddelerinden birisi oldu\\u011fu i\\u00e7in genel sa\\u011fl\\u0131k \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde \\u00f6nemli bir kriter olarak g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccudunda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck oranda C vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>bulunan bireyler ile kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131ld\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda y\\u00fcksek oranda C vitamini bulunan bireylerin inme (fel\\u00e7) riski ile daha d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck oranlarda oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. C vitamini v\\u00fccudun hem i\\u00e7indeki hem de d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131ndaki h\\u00fccreleri etkiledi\\u011fi i\\u00e7in cilt kurulu\\u011fu ve ya\\u015flanmaya kar\\u015f\\u0131 olumlu etkileri oldu\\u011fu d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcn\\u00fclmektedir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C vitamini eksikli\\u011fi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">nispeten nadir kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan bir durumdur ve yetersiz beslenen yeti\\u015fkinlerde daha yayg\\u0131n olarak g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr. Buna ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak baz\\u0131 kanser t\\u00fcrleri ve sindirim sistemi rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n C vitamini eksikli\\u011fine kar\\u015f\\u0131 daha duyarl\\u0131 olabilece\\u011fi ihtimali \\u00fczerinde durulmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">A\\u011f\\u0131r C vitamini eksikli\\u011fi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen bireylerde&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/anemi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">anemi (kans\\u0131zl\\u0131k)<\\/span><\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/agiz-ve-dis-sagligi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">di\\u015f eti kanamas\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a>, ciltte morarma gibi durumlar g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir. Baz\\u0131 durumlarda ise yara iyile\\u015fmesinde yava\\u015flama ile tan\\u0131mlanan,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">iskorb\\u00fct<\\/span>&nbsp;ad\\u0131 verilen bir hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilece\\u011fi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Meyve ve sebze a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan zengin bir diyet ile beslenmenin meme, kolon ve akci\\u011fer kanserleri gibi bir\\u00e7ok kanser t\\u00fcr\\u00fcn\\u00fcn ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kmas\\u0131 riskinin azald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcn\\u00fclmektedir. Ancak bu koruyucu etkilerin do\\u011frudan g\\u0131dada bulunan&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>ile ili\\u015fkili olup olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 a\\u00e7\\u0131k de\\u011fildir.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunun yerine meyve ve sebzeler ile sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 beslenmenin bu etkiye yol a\\u00e7t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 kan\\u0131s\\u0131 t\\u0131p uzmanlar\\u0131nca daha yayg\\u0131n bir \\u015fekilde kabul g\\u00f6rmektedir. Ayn\\u0131 zamanda oral C vitamini takviyelerinin do\\u011fal beslenme yoluyla al\\u0131nan C vitamini kadar fayda sa\\u011flad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcn\\u00fclmemektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Nezle, so\\u011fuk alg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 durumunda ise, a\\u011f\\u0131zdan C vitamini takviyeleri almak so\\u011fuk alg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 engellemez. Bununla birlikte, d\\u00fczenli olarak&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini takviyesi<\\/span>&nbsp;alan bireylerde so\\u011fuk alg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde, hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n daha k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcre devam etti\\u011fi ve hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n seyri boyunca ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan semptomlar\\u0131n daha az \\u015fiddetli oldu\\u011funu g\\u00f6steren baz\\u0131 kan\\u0131tlar vard\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ancak so\\u011fuk alg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ba\\u015flad\\u0131ktan sonra&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">C vitamini takviyesine<\\/span>&nbsp;ba\\u015flamak bu t\\u00fcr hastal\\u0131klara kar\\u015f\\u0131 bir fayda sa\\u011flamamaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C vitamini takviyelerinin di\\u011fer vitaminler ve minerallerle birlikte al\\u0131nmas\\u0131n\\u0131n, ya\\u015fa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 makula dejenerasyonunun ya da di\\u011fer ad\\u0131yla sar\\u0131 nokta hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n daha a\\u011f\\u0131r bir hal almas\\u0131na kar\\u015f\\u0131 \\u00f6nleyici etkileri oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. Buna ek olarak beslenmeleri esnas\\u0131nda daha y\\u00fcksek C vitamini t\\u00fcketen bireylerin katarakt geli\\u015ftirme riskinin daha d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"G\\u00fcnl\\u00fck C Vitamini \\u0130htiyac\\u0131 Nas\\u0131l Kar\\u015f\\u0131lan\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C vitamini en yayg\\u0131n olarak narenciye \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri, \\u00e7e\\u015fitli meyveler ve sebzelerde bulunur. Bunun yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra kaps\\u00fcl halinde ve \\u00e7i\\u011fnenebilir tabletler \\u015feklinde a\\u011f\\u0131zdan al\\u0131nan takviyeler halinde de C vitamini almak m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ancak t\\u0131p uzmanlar\\u0131 antioksidan \\u00f6zellikleri i\\u00e7in al\\u0131nan takviye C vitamininin g\\u0131dalarda do\\u011fal olarak bulunan antioksidanlarla ayn\\u0131 derecede fayda sa\\u011flamad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Suda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnen vitaminlerin v\\u00fccut i\\u00e7inde sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 seviyelerde bulunmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flamak i\\u00e7in bu t\\u00fcr vitaminlere diyette s\\u00fcrekli olarak yer verilmelidir. C vitamini a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan zengin meyve ve sebzelerin uygun olanlar\\u0131 iyice temizledikten sonra \\u00e7i\\u011f olarak yemek, kalanlar\\u0131n\\u0131 da m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn oldu\\u011fu kadar az suyla pi\\u015firmek, suda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcr vitaminlerin bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131n\\u0131n pi\\u015firme suyunda kaybolmas\\u0131n\\u0131 engelleyecektir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bireyler i\\u00e7in normal beslenme yoluyla g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 tavsiye edilen C vitamini miktarlar\\u0131 a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131da verilmi\\u015ftir. Ancak bu miktarlara g\\u00f6re diyet belirlemeden \\u00f6nce doktora ba\\u015fvurulmas\\u0131 tavsiye edilir.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">0 ila 6 ay aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 40 miligram<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">7 ila 12 ay aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 50 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 ila 3 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar:&nbsp;<\\/span>g\\u00fcnde 15 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">4 ila 8 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar:&nbsp;<\\/span>g\\u00fcnde 25 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">9 ila 13 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuklar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 45 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">14 ila 18 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131 kad\\u0131nlar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 65 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">14 ila 18 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131 erkekler:&nbsp;<\\/span>g\\u00fcnde 75 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">19 ya\\u015f ve \\u00fczeri kad\\u0131nlar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 75 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">19 ya\\u015f ve \\u00fczeri erkekler:&nbsp;<\\/span>g\\u00fcnde 90 miligram<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Hamile kad\\u0131nlar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 80\\/85 miligram&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Emziren kad\\u0131nlar:<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00fcnde 115\\/120 miligram<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"C Vitamini Hangi Besinlerde Bulunur? \",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yap\\u0131lan ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalara g\\u00f6re C vitamini a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan en zengin yiyeceklerin narenciye \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri, ye\\u015filbiber, \\u00e7ilek, domates, brokoli, patates ve tatl\\u0131 patates oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Zengin C vitamini kaynaklar\\u0131&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">aras\\u0131nda ayn\\u0131 zamanda koyu yaprakl\\u0131 ye\\u015fillikler, kavun, papaya, mango, karpuz, Br\\u00fcksel lahanas\\u0131, karnabahar, lahana, k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131biber, ahududu, yaban mersini, k\\u0131\\u015f kaba\\u011f\\u0131 ve ananas bulundu\\u011fu bilinmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7e\\u015fitli besinlerde bulunan ortalama C vitamini miktar\\u0131 a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131da verilmi\\u015ftir.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 b\\u00fcy\\u00fck dilim kavun:<\\/span>&nbsp;59 mg (miligram)<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 adet orta boy kivi:&nbsp;<\\/span>70 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 adet orta boy portakal:&nbsp;<\\/span>90 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 bardak domates suyu:&nbsp;<\\/span>33 mg.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 bardak portakal suyu:&nbsp;<\\/span>97 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1 porsiyon pi\\u015fmi\\u015f brokoli:&nbsp;<\\/span>74 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1\\/2 porsiyon (bardak) k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 biber, \\u00e7i\\u011f:&nbsp;<\\/span>95 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1\\/2 porsiyon (bardak) k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 lahana:<\\/span>&nbsp;40 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1\\/2 porsiyon (bardak) ye\\u015fil biber:&nbsp;<\\/span>60 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1\\/2 porsiyon (bardak) \\u00e7ilek:&nbsp;<\\/span>49 mg<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1\\/2 porsiyon (bardak) pi\\u015fmi\\u015f br\\u00fcksel lahanas\\u0131:<\\/span>&nbsp;48 mg<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Nas\\u0131l Daha Fazla C Vitamini Al\\u0131n\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">C Vitamininin v\\u00fccuda beslenme yoluyla do\\u011fal olarak al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 tercih edilmelidir. Bireylerin C vitamini i\\u00e7eren meyve ve sebzeleri g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck beslenmelerine daha fazla dahil etmesi i\\u00e7in \\u00e7e\\u015fitli y\\u00f6ntemler mevcuttur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00d6rnek verilmesi gerekirse \\u00e7orba ve k\\u00f6fte tariflerine p\\u00fcre haline getirilmi\\u015f veya rendelenmi\\u015f sebzeler eklenebilir, ya da kek tariflerine ayn\\u0131 \\u015fekilde haz\\u0131rlanm\\u0131\\u015f meyve eklemek m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">H\\u0131zl\\u0131 bir at\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131rmal\\u0131k olmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in \\u00f6nceden kesilmi\\u015f meyve ve sebzeleri haz\\u0131r bir \\u015fekilde tutmak faydal\\u0131 olabilir. T\\u00fcm sandvi\\u00e7 ve d\\u00fcr\\u00fcm t\\u00fcrlerine marul, domates ve rendelenmi\\u015f brokoli ya da lahana eklenebilir. \\u015eekerli i\\u00e7ecekler yerine \\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcn aras\\u0131 i\\u00e7ecek olarak bir bardak sebze suyu tercih edilebilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"C\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 15:50:13', '2023-12-20 15:53:03'),
