(578, 578, 89, 79, 1, 'Çarpık Ayak (Pes Ekinovarus)', 5, 'carpik-ayak', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7arp\\u0131k Ayak (Pes Ekinovarus)\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7arp\\u0131k ayak hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, ayaklardan birinin veya her ikisinin birden do\\u011fal pozisyonunda hafif\\u00e7e i\\u00e7e ve a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131 do\\u011fru olmas\\u0131yla seyreden ve bebeklik d\\u00f6neminde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan bir hastal\\u0131kt\\u0131r. Hastalar\\u0131n yar\\u0131s\\u0131nda sadece tek ayak etkilenirken, di\\u011fer yar\\u0131s\\u0131nda iki ayak birden etkilenmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Nedeni net olarak a\\u00e7\\u0131klanamamakla beraber, ikiz karde\\u015flerde yakla\\u015f\\u0131k 1\\/3 oran\\u0131nda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcyor olmas\\u0131, hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda genetik yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131k olabilece\\u011fini d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnd\\u00fcrmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Tan\\u0131 Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fte anne karn\\u0131ndaki duru\\u015f bozuklu\\u011fu sebebi ile meydana geldi\\u011fi d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcn\\u00fclen bu rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k, geli\\u015fen t\\u0131p teknolojisi ve detayl\\u0131 ultrason g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fclemeleriyle gebeli\\u011fin 16. haftas\\u0131nda saptanabiliyor. Baz\\u0131 durumlarda bebe\\u011fin duru\\u015f pozisyonundan kaynakl\\u0131 olarak fark edilmese bile do\\u011fum sonras\\u0131nda kolayl\\u0131k tan\\u0131 konulabiliyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bebek do\\u011far do\\u011fmaz yap\\u0131lan kontrollerde ayaklarda i\\u00e7e d\\u00f6n\\u00fckl\\u00fck \\u015feklinde e\\u011frilikler g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebiliyor. Hekim, yapaca\\u011f\\u0131 muayenede<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Ayak kiri\\u015finin y\\u00fcksek olmas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Ba\\u015fparma\\u011f\\u0131n i\\u00e7e d\\u00f6n\\u00fck olmas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Topu\\u011fun i\\u00e7e d\\u00f6n\\u00fck olmas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Ayak bile\\u011finin a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131 bak\\u0131yor olmas\\u0131 gibi bulgulara g\\u00f6re te\\u015fhis koyabilmektedir.<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7arp\\u0131k ayak hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n en ay\\u0131rt edici \\u00f6zelli\\u011fi \\u201caya\\u011f\\u0131n e\\u011frili\\u011fini d\\u00fczeltmeye \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131zda d\\u00fczelmemesidir\\u201d.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Tedavi Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7arp\\u0131k ayak tedavisinde<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;\\u00f6zel bir manevra ile ayaklar esnetilerek, kas\\u0131\\u011fa kadar uzayan bir al\\u00e7\\u0131 tak\\u0131l\\u0131yor. Ortalama bir hafta kadar kalan bu al\\u00e7\\u0131lama ile bebe\\u011fin ayaklar\\u0131nda belirli bir d\\u00fczelme g\\u00f6zle g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr \\u015fekilde ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015fiyor. Devam\\u0131nda yine \\u00f6zel bir manevra ile ayaklar biraz daha esnetilerek ikinci al\\u00e7\\u0131lamaya ge\\u00e7iliyor. D\\u00fczelme oran\\u0131na g\\u00f6re bu i\\u015flem yakla\\u015f\\u0131k 1 ay boyunda her hafta yeniden tekrarlan\\u0131yor. Bir ay sonunda ayaklar\\u0131n do\\u011fal pozisyona getirilmesi sa\\u011flan\\u0131yor.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bir ayl\\u0131k s\\u00fcre\\u00e7 sonunda ayaklar yeniden kontrol ediliyor ve 20 derecenin \\u00fczerinde rahat bir \\u015fekilde esnetilip esnetilemedi\\u011fine bak\\u0131l\\u0131yor. E\\u011fer ayaklar rahat\\u00e7a esnetilebiliyorsa ve topuk kemi\\u011fi yerindeyse tedavi tamamlanm\\u0131\\u015f oluyor.<\\/p><p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/div><div class=\\\"author\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/div><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\">E\\u011fer, topuk kemi\\u011fi yerinde de\\u011fil veya ayaklar rahat esnetilemiyorsa a\\u015filotomi yani a\\u015fil tendonun uzat\\u0131lmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in basit bir cerrahi operasyon ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftiriliyor. Operasyon sonras\\u0131 yine al\\u00e7\\u0131lama i\\u015flemi yap\\u0131l\\u0131yor ve sonras\\u0131nda aya\\u011f\\u0131n \\u015feklini koruyan ortez denilen aras\\u0131 \\u00e7ubuklu \\u00f6zel bir ayakkab\\u0131 giydirilmesi gerekiyor. Bu tedaviden sonu\\u00e7 alabilmek i\\u00e7in \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n g\\u00fcnde 23 saat boyunca ve \\u00fc\\u00e7 ay s\\u00fcreyle giymesi gerekiyor.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 15:55:14', '2023-12-20 15:56:36'),
