(582, 582, 89, 79, 1, 'D Vitamini', 6, 'd-vitamini', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"D Vitamini\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 kemikler olu\\u015fturmak ve kemik sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 korumak i\\u00e7in&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">D vitaminin<\\/span>&nbsp;varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00e7ok m\\u00fchimdir. Bunun esas nedeni, kemi\\u011fin birincil bile\\u015feni olan kalsiyumun ancak D vitamini varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan emilmesidir. G\\u00fcne\\u015f \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nlar\\u0131n\\u0131n, ciltteki bir kimyasal\\u0131 aktif bir vitamin (kalsiferol) formuna d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcrmesiyle v\\u00fccutta&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">D vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;\\u00fcretilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Cildinizin \\u00fcretti\\u011fi D vitamini miktar\\u0131; g\\u00fcn\\u00fcn saatine, mevsime, cilt pigmentasyonuna ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterebilmektedir. Ya\\u015fan\\u0131lan yere, ya\\u015fam tarz\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak, D vitamin \\u00fcretiminde azalma olabilir ya da tamamen yok olabilir. G\\u00fcne\\u015f kremi \\u00f6nlemli olsa bile D vitamini \\u00fcretimini azaltabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"D Vitamini Nas\\u0131l Al\\u0131n\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcne\\u015fe maruz kalma, \\u00e7o\\u011fu ki\\u015fi i\\u00e7in&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">D vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;alman\\u0131n kolay ve g\\u00fcvenilir bir yoludur. Ellerin, y\\u00fcz\\u00fcn, kollar\\u0131n ve bacaklar\\u0131n haftada 2-3 kez g\\u00fcne\\u015f \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kalmas\\u0131, hafif bir hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n geli\\u015fmesi i\\u00e7in gereken s\\u00fcrenin yakla\\u015f\\u0131k d\\u00f6rtte biri kadar s\\u00fcrer. G\\u00fcne\\u015fe \\u00e7ok fazla maruz kalman\\u0131n da negatif etkileri s\\u00f6z konusudur \\u00e7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc maruz kalma s\\u00fcresi ya\\u015fa, cilt tipine, mevsime, g\\u00fcn\\u00fcn saatine vb. fakt\\u00f6rlere ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcne\\u015f kremi olmadan sadece 6 g\\u00fcn boyunca g\\u00fcne\\u015f \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kalma, 49 g\\u00fcn boyunca hi\\u00e7 g\\u00fcne\\u015f \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kalmamay\\u0131 telafi edebilir. V\\u00fccut ya\\u011flar\\u0131 D vitamini fazlas\\u0131n\\u0131 ya\\u011fda depolar ve ihtiya\\u00e7 olunan d\\u00f6nemde serbest b\\u0131rak\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"D Vitamininin Faydalar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kanser:&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalara g\\u00f6re d vitamini kalsiyumla birlikte al\\u0131nd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda baz\\u0131 kanserlerin \\u00f6nlenmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bili\\u015fsel Sa\\u011fl\\u0131k:&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">D vitamini takviyesi almak bili\\u015fsel i\\u015flevi iyile\\u015ftirmeye yard\\u0131mc\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kal\\u0131tsal Bozukluklar:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;D vitamini takviyeleri, ailesel hipofosfatemi gibi D vitamini emiliminin engellenmesi ya da i\\u015flenememesinden kaynakl\\u0131 kal\\u0131tsal bozukluklar\\u0131n tedavisi amac\\u0131yla kullan\\u0131labilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Multipl Skleroz:&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar, uzun s\\u00fcreli D vitamini takviyesinin multipl skleroz riskini azaltt\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 g\\u00f6stermektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Osteomalazi:&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">D vitamini takviyeleri, kemik mimeral i\\u00e7eri\\u011fi kayb\\u0131, kemik a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, kas zay\\u0131fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, yumu\\u015fak kemikler gibi ciddi D vitamini eksikli\\u011fi olan yeti\\u015fkinleri tedavi etmek amac\\u0131yla kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Osteoporoz (Kemik erimesi):&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yeterli miktarda D vitamini ve kalsiyum alan ki\\u015filerin kemik mineral kayb\\u0131 yava\\u015flayabilir, kemik k\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131 azalabilir ve osteoporozu \\u00f6nlenebilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sedef Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;D vitamini ya da bir D vitamini bile\\u015fi\\u011fini cilde uygulamak sedef hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavi edilmesinde rol oynayabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ra\\u015fitizm:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;D vitamini eksikli\\u011fi olan \\u00e7ocuklarda geli\\u015fir, D vitamini takviyesi ile beraber tedavi edilebilir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"D Vitamini Kaynaklar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">D vitamininin temel kayna\\u011f\\u0131 g\\u00fcne\\u015ftir. D vitamini ultraviyole \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nlar\\u0131n\\u0131n cilde temas\\u0131n\\u0131n ard\\u0131ndan olu\\u015fan baz\\u0131 metabolik s\\u00fcre\\u00e7ler neticesinde \\u00fcretilmektedir. Bu sebeple, her g\\u00fcn, y\\u00fczler ve kollar a\\u00e7\\u0131k, g\\u00fcne\\u015fin geli\\u015f a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak (en ideal saatler: 11.00-15.00) 20 ila 30 dakika g\\u00fcne\\u015flenme sayesinde yeterli oranda D vitamini \\u00fcretilebilir.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcnl\\u00fck D vitamini ihtiyac\\u0131n\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;sadece besinler ile sa\\u011flamak m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn de\\u011fildir. \\u00c7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc besinlerle g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ihtiyac\\u0131n yaln\\u0131zca %20\\u2019si kar\\u015f\\u0131lanmaktad\\u0131r. Bu y\\u00fczden g\\u00fcne\\u015f \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndan yararlanamayan bireyler b\\u00fcy\\u00fck risk alt\\u0131ndad\\u0131r. Bu y\\u00fczden hekimle bu bilgilerin payla\\u015f\\u0131l\\u0131p, gerekli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc takdirde de D vitamini takviyesi verilmesi gereklidir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Koruyucu krem, k\\u0131yafetle ve pencere arkas\\u0131ndan g\\u00fcne\\u015flenmek, D vitamini \\u00fcretimini sekteye u\\u011frat\\u0131yor olabilir. D\\u00fczenli bir \\u015fekilde uyumak, D vitamininden daha fazla faydalanman\\u0131za olanak tan\\u0131yor.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"D Vitamini Eksikli\\u011fi Kimlerde G\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kapal\\u0131 ortamda \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fan ki\\u015filer<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ya\\u015fl\\u0131lar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Beslenme bozuklu\\u011fu olanlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Y\\u00fcksek fakt\\u00f6rl\\u00fc g\\u00fcne\\u015f kremi kullananlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kapal\\u0131 giysi giyenler<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Gebe ve emziren kad\\u0131nlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">B\\u00f6brek hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 olan ki\\u015filer<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 olanlar<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"D\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 15:58:49', '2023-12-20 16:01:23'),
