(586, 586, 89, 79, 1, 'E Vitamini', 7, 'e-vitamini', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"E Vitamini\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">E vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, d\\u00f6rd\\u00fc tokoferol ve d\\u00f6rd\\u00fc tocotrienol olmak \\u00fczere ya\\u011fda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnen sekiz farkl\\u0131 bile\\u015fi\\u011fin olu\\u015fan bir gruba verilen isimdir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">E vitamini,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">beyin, cilt, g\\u00f6z, ve dola\\u015f\\u0131m sistemi sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra g\\u00f6rme i\\u00e7in de \\u00f6nemli bir besin bile\\u015fi\\u011fidir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"E Vitamininin Faydalar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">E vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, insan v\\u00fccudundaki h\\u00fccre zarlar\\u0131n\\u0131 \\u00e7e\\u015fitli reaktif oksijen tiplerinden koruyan ve ya\\u011fda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnen bir antioksidand\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Antioksidanlar, bireyin v\\u00fccudundaki sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 h\\u00fccreleri yani v\\u00fccut yiyecekleri par\\u00e7alad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda, ya da t\\u00fct\\u00fcn duman\\u0131 veya radyasyona maruz kald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda \\u00fcretilen zararl\\u0131 molek\\u00fcller serbest radikallerin etkilerine kar\\u015f\\u0131 koruyabilen maddelerdir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Serbest radikaller kalp hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, kanser ve di\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n geli\\u015fiminde rol oynayabilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitaminini&nbsp;<\\/span>takviye olarak alan ki\\u015filer,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamininin<\\/span>&nbsp;antioksidan \\u00f6zellikleri nedeniyle g\\u0131dalardan do\\u011fal olarak bulunan antioksidanlarla ayn\\u0131 faydalar\\u0131 her zaman sa\\u011flamad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 unutmamal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hem do\\u011fal hem de sentetik tokoferoller oksidasyona tabidir. Bu nedenle diyet takviyelerinde esterle\\u015ftirilir ve stabilite amac\\u0131yla tokoferil asetat olu\\u015fturulur.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"E Vitamini Eksikli\\u011fi Nelere Yol A\\u00e7ar?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">T\\u0131p uzmanlar\\u0131 genel olarak yeti\\u015fkinlerin g\\u00fcnde 7 ila 15 mg aral\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>t\\u00fcketmelerini tavsiye edilmektedir.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;E vitamini eksikli\\u011fi&nbsp;<\\/span>nadir g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen bir durumdur ve sinir sistemi \\u00fczerinde sinir a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, yani n\\u00f6ropati gibi sorunlara neden olabilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">E vitamini eklikli\\u011fi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;genellikle E vitamini a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck bir diyetten ziyade diyet ya\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n sindirilmesi s\\u00fcrecinde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan bir sorun nedeniyle olu\\u015fur.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"E Vitamini Fazlal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 Nelere Yol A\\u00e7ar?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uygun dozlarda al\\u0131nd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda, oral olarak E vitamini kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 genellikle g\\u00fcvenli kabul edilir. Nadir vakalarda&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamininin<\\/span>&nbsp;a\\u011f\\u0131zdan takviye olarak al\\u0131nmas\\u0131, bulant\\u0131, ishal, ba\\u011f\\u0131rsakta kramplar, yorgunluk, zay\\u0131fl\\u0131k, ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, bulan\\u0131k g\\u00f6rme, d\\u00f6k\\u00fcnt\\u00fc, gonadal i\\u015flev bozuklu\\u011fu, ve idrarda kreatin konsantrasyonunun art\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 yani creatinuriaya sebep olabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yap\\u0131lan \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalar&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ihtiyac\\u0131n \\u00e7ok \\u00fczerinde al\\u0131nmas\\u0131n\\u0131n&nbsp; kardiyovask\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar, kanser, demans ve di\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kma olas\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcrse bile t\\u00fcm nedenlere ba\\u011fl\\u0131 \\u00f6l\\u00fcm oranlar\\u0131nda da m\\u00fctevaz\\u0131 bir art\\u0131\\u015fla ili\\u015fkili oldu\\u011funa dair baz\\u0131 g\\u00f6stergeler oldu\\u011funa i\\u015faret etmektedir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;i\\u00e7eren cilt bak\\u0131m \\u00fcr\\u00fcnlerinin kullan\\u0131m\\u0131n\\u0131n etkili oldu\\u011funa dair klinik bir kan\\u0131t yoktur.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Baz\\u0131 ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar, y\\u00fcksek doz&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamininin<\\/span>, hafif ya da orta derecede Alzheimer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 te\\u015fhisi konan ki\\u015filerde&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/alzheimer-ve-yaslanma\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Alzheimer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ilerlemesini geciktirebilece\\u011fine i\\u015faret etse bile, ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilen di\\u011fer \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalarda bu yarar \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fclememi\\u015ftir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini takviyelerinin<\\/span>, hafif bili\\u015fsel bozuklu\\u011fu olan ki\\u015filerin&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Alzheimer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na<\\/span>&nbsp;ge\\u00e7i\\u015fini engellemesi \\u00fczerinde hi\\u00e7bir etkisi yoktur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yap\\u0131lan t\\u0131bbi ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar sonucunda,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamininin<\\/span>&nbsp;alkols\\u00fcz ya\\u011fl\\u0131 karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 semptomlar\\u0131n\\u0131 iyile\\u015ftirebilece\\u011fi g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. Bununla birlikte, bu ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalarda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan baz\\u0131 kan\\u0131tlar, bu ama\\u00e7 i\\u00e7in iki y\\u0131l boyunca a\\u011f\\u0131z yoluyla&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini takviyesi<\\/span>&nbsp;alman\\u0131n&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/insulin-direnci\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ins\\u00fclin direnci&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>geli\\u015ftirilmesi ile alakal\\u0131 olabilece\\u011fini g\\u00f6stermektedir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">E vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;al\\u0131m\\u0131n\\u0131 art\\u0131rman\\u0131n, gebelik s\\u00fcrecinde kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyen ve preeklampsi ad\\u0131 verilen durumu \\u00f6nledi\\u011fine dair kesin bir kan\\u0131t elde edilememi\\u015ftir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yap\\u0131lan \\u00e7e\\u015fitli t\\u0131bbi ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar sonucunda, yayg\\u0131n inan\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n aksine&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;ve selenyum takviyelerinin prostat kanserini \\u00f6nlemedi\\u011fi g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. Bunun yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini takviyelerinin<\\/span>&nbsp;kullan\\u0131m\\u0131n\\u0131n prostat kanseri riskini art\\u0131rabilece\\u011fi endi\\u015fesi de vard\\u0131r.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K vitamini eksikli\\u011fi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;olan, retinitis pigmentosa ad\\u0131 verilen g\\u00f6z sorunu olan, kanama bozukluklar\\u0131 olan, diyabet olan, ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fte&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/kalp-krizi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kalp krizi<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;veya inme ge\\u00e7irmi\\u015f, ba\\u015f ve boyun kanseri olan ya da karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndan muzdarip bireyler<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;E vitamini takviyesi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">almadan \\u00f6nce uzman bir doktor ile durumlar\\u0131 hakk\\u0131nda konu\\u015fmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"G\\u00fcnl\\u00fck E Vitamini \\u0130htiyac\\u0131 Nas\\u0131l Kar\\u015f\\u0131lan\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7o\\u011fu insan i\\u00e7in dengeli bir diyet yeterli&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;sa\\u011flar. E vitamini a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan zengin g\\u0131dalar aras\\u0131nda avokado, ay\\u00e7i\\u00e7e\\u011fi ve soya ya\\u011f\\u0131, ay\\u00e7i\\u00e7e\\u011fi \\u00e7ekirde\\u011fi, badem, bu\\u011fday tohumu ya\\u011f\\u0131, f\\u0131st\\u0131k, f\\u0131st\\u0131k ezmesi, \\u0131spanak, kabak, kanola ya\\u011f\\u0131, kara lahana, k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 biber, ku\\u015fkonmaz, mango pancar ye\\u015fillikleri, yer f\\u0131st\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve zeytinya\\u011f\\u0131 bulunur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ayr\\u0131ca et, s\\u00fct, yaprakl\\u0131 ye\\u015fillikler ve g\\u00fc\\u00e7lendirilmi\\u015f tah\\u0131llardan&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span>al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr. E vitamini, oral bir takviye olarak&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">E vitamini kaps\\u00fcl\\u00fc<\\/span>&nbsp;veya E vitamini amp\\u00fcl damlas\\u0131 olarak al\\u0131nabilir. Ameliyat olacak bireyler, ameliyattan iki hafta \\u00f6nce E vitamini takviyesi almay\\u0131 b\\u0131rakmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"E\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:03:11', '2023-12-20 16:05:10'),
