(594, 594, 89, 79, 1, 'Ganglion Kisti', 9, 'ganglion-kisti', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Ganglion Kisti\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, en s\\u0131k bilek ya da ellerin tendonlar\\u0131 veya eklemleri boyunca geli\\u015fen ve kanserli olmayan \\u015fi\\u015fliklere verilen isimdir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kisti<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;ayak bileklerinde ve ayaklarda da meydana gelebilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;tipik olarak yuvarlak yada oval bir formdad\\u0131r.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;i\\u00e7i sinovyal s\\u0131v\\u0131 ad\\u0131 verilen j\\u00f6le benzeri, yap\\u0131\\u015fkan \\u015feffaf&nbsp; bir s\\u0131v\\u0131 ile doludur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistlerinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;boyutlar\\u0131 bezelye b\\u00fcy\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnden yakla\\u015f\\u0131k 2, 5 santimetre \\u00e7ap\\u0131na kadar de\\u011fi\\u015febilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, yak\\u0131ndaki bir sinire bask\\u0131 yapt\\u0131klar\\u0131 zaman a\\u011fr\\u0131ya neden olabilir. Kistin konumu baz\\u0131 vakalarda eklem hareketini engelleyebilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistinin bireyin ya\\u015fam kalitesine sorun \\u00e7\\u0131kard\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 vakalarda doktor kisti bir i\\u011fne ile bo\\u015faltmay\\u0131 denemeyi \\u00f6nerebilir. Kistin cerrahi olarak \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lmas\\u0131 da bir se\\u00e7enektir. Ancak herhangi bir olumsuz komplikasyonun olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 durumlarda tedaviye gerek g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmez. Bir\\u00e7ok vakada kistler kendili\\u011finden kaybolur.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Ganglion Kisti Neden Olur?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">T\\u0131p uzmanlar\\u0131&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kistinin<\\/span>&nbsp;geli\\u015fmesine neyin sebep oldu\\u011funu tam olarak belirleyebilmi\\u015f de\\u011fildir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span>&nbsp;bir eklemden veya bir tendonun astar\\u0131ndan geli\\u015fmeye ba\\u015flar ve bir k\\u00f6ke yap\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015f bir balon gibi bir g\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcme sahiptir. Yayg\\u0131n olarak bir eklemi veya \\u00e7evreleyen doku yerinden oynad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 zaman ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kar.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kistin i\\u00e7inde bulunan sinovyal s\\u0131v\\u0131s\\u0131 eklemler ile tendonlar\\u0131n \\u00e7evresinde bulunan kal\\u0131n ya\\u011f s\\u0131v\\u0131s\\u0131na benzerlik g\\u00f6sterir. Bu durum&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kistinin<\\/span>&nbsp;eklem ya da tendonlar\\u0131 \\u00e7evreleyen sinovyal s\\u0131v\\u0131n\\u0131n d\\u0131\\u015far\\u0131 s\\u0131zarak bir kesede toplanmas\\u0131 nedeniyle olu\\u015ftu\\u011funa i\\u015faret etmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Ganglion Kistinin Belirtileri Ve Tipleri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;ile ili\\u015fkili \\u015fi\\u015fler konumlar\\u0131, \\u015fekil ile boyutlar\\u0131 ve a\\u011fr\\u0131 dereceleri ile karakterize edilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri&nbsp;<\\/span><u style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">en \\u00e7ok bilekler veya ellerdeki tendonlar ya da eklemleri boyunca geli\\u015fir<\\/u><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">. \\u0130kinci en yayg\\u0131n olarak ayak bilekleri ve ayaklarda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr.&nbsp;<\\/span><u style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri v\\u00fccutta bulunan herhangi bir eklemin yak\\u0131n\\u0131nda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilir.<\\/u><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri yuvarlak veya ovaldir. Yayg\\u0131n olarak \\u00e7aplar\\u0131 2 - 3 santimden daha k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fckt\\u00fcr. Baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 temas ile hissedilmeyecek kadar k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck olabilir. Kistin boyutlar\\u0131 zaman i\\u00e7inde dalgalanarak ufal\\u0131p irile\\u015febilir. Genel olarak yan\\u0131nda geli\\u015fti\\u011fi eklemin tekrarlanan hareketler i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ganglion kistinin b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmesine neden olur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;yayg\\u0131n olarak a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131zd\\u0131r. Ancak kist fark edilir bir yumru olu\\u015fturamayacak kadar k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck olsa bile herhangi bir sinire bask\\u0131 yapt\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 vakalarda bireyde&nbsp;<\\/span><u style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">a\\u011fr\\u0131, kar\\u0131ncalanma, uyu\\u015fma veya kas g\\u00fc\\u00e7s\\u00fczl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc<\\/u><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;gibi belirti ve semptomlara neden olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bile\\u011finde, elinde, ayak bile\\u011finde veya aya\\u011f\\u0131nda g\\u00f6zle g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr bir yumru g\\u00f6ren veya a\\u011fr\\u0131 hisseden bireyler mutlaka doktora g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnmelidir. Doktor durumun ne oldu\\u011funa dair do\\u011fru te\\u015fhis koyabilir ve bireyin herhangi bir tedaviye ihtiyac\\u0131 olup olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 belirleyebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Ganglion Kisti Nas\\u0131l Te\\u015fhis Edilir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kisti tan\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131n<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;konulmas\\u0131 s\\u00fcrecinde doktor \\u00f6ncelikle bir fizik muayene ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirir ve hastan\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131k ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fi hakk\\u0131ndaki bilgileri soraca\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sorular ile \\u00f6\\u011frenmeyi hedefler. Birey g\\u00f6zlemledi\\u011fi b\\u00fct\\u00fcn belirtilerini bu muayene s\\u00fcrecinde doktor ile konu\\u015fmal\\u0131 ve sahip olabilece\\u011fi di\\u011fer ko\\u015fullar veya hastal\\u0131klarla ilgili bilgileri payla\\u015fmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fizik muayene s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda, doktor bireyde olas\\u0131 hassasiyet veya rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k durumunu test etmek i\\u00e7in kiste bask\\u0131 uygulayabilir. Kitlenin kat\\u0131 m\\u0131 oldu\\u011fu yoksa s\\u0131v\\u0131yla m\\u0131 dolu oldu\\u011funu belirlemek i\\u00e7in kistin i\\u00e7inden ge\\u00e7ecek \\u015fekilde bir \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131k tutmaya \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Doktor ayr\\u0131ca&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">artrit<\\/span>&nbsp;veya&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">t\\u00fcm\\u00f6r<\\/span>&nbsp;gibi di\\u011fer durumlar\\u0131n varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ihtimalini ortadan kald\\u0131rmak i\\u00e7in r\\u00f6ntgen, ultrason veya manyetik rezonans g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme yani MRG gibi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme testlerinin de gerekli oldu\\u011funu belirtebilir. Yap\\u0131lan manyetik rezonans g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme ve ultrason testleri ayr\\u0131ca gizli kistlerin de varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131karabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bir&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kisti te\\u015fhisi<\\/span>, doktorun kistteki s\\u0131v\\u0131y\\u0131 \\u00e7ekmek yani aspire etmek i\\u00e7in bir i\\u011fne ve \\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131nga kulland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 bir i\\u015flem olan aspirasyonla do\\u011frulanabilir. Bir&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kistinden<\\/span>&nbsp;gelen s\\u0131v\\u0131 yo\\u011fun ve berrak veya yar\\u0131 saydam olacakt\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Ganglion Kisti Nas\\u0131l Tedavi Edilir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;a\\u011fr\\u0131ya neden oldu\\u011fu vakalarda doktor immobilizasyon yani hareketsizle\\u015ftirme, aspirasyon ve cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale se\\u00e7eneklerinden birisini uygulayabilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130mmobilizasyon tedavisi hareketin ganglion kistinin b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmesine neden olmas\\u0131ndan dolay\\u0131 b\\u00f6lgeyi bir atel veya destek ile ge\\u00e7ici olarak hareketsiz hale getirmesine dayan\\u0131r. Hareketsiz kalan b\\u00f6lgedeki&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kisti<\\/span>&nbsp;zaman i\\u00e7inde k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcld\\u00fck\\u00e7e s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131rd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 sinirler \\u00fczerindeki bask\\u0131y\\u0131 azalt\\u0131r ve bu sayede a\\u011fr\\u0131 hafifleyebilir. Ganglion kistlerinin k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fclmesi uzun zaman alabilir, bu nedenle bireyler kistin bulundu\\u011fu eklem ile ili\\u015fkili kaslar\\u0131n zay\\u0131flamas\\u0131na neden olabilecek kadar uzun s\\u00fcreli atel veya destek kullanmaktan ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Aspirasyon prosed\\u00fcr\\u00fcnde doktor bir enjekt\\u00f6r yard\\u0131m\\u0131yla s\\u0131v\\u0131y\\u0131 kistten bo\\u015falt\\u0131r. Bu prosed\\u00fcrden sonra kist tekrarlayabilir. Bireyler aspirasyon prosed\\u00fcr\\u00fcn\\u00fc kendi uygulamamal\\u0131d\\u0131r, \\u00e7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc yanl\\u0131\\u015f bir hareket tendonlara zarar verebilir ya da enfeksiyon gibi sorunlara yol a\\u00e7abilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Di\\u011fer yakla\\u015f\\u0131mlar\\u0131n etkili olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 vakalarda cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale uygun bir se\\u00e7enek olabilir. Cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale s\\u00fcrecinde doktor hem kisti ve hem de onu eklem veya tendona ba\\u011flayan k\\u00f6k\\u00fc \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131r. \\u00c7ok nadir vakalarda ameliyat \\u00e7evredeki sinirlere, kan damarlar\\u0131na veya tendonlara zarar verebilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Ganglion kistinin<\\/span>&nbsp;baz\\u0131 vakalarda ameliyattan sonra tekrarlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fclm\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcr.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ganglion kistini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;\\u00e7\\u0131karmak kullan\\u0131lan iki cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale t\\u00fcr\\u00fcne&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">a\\u00e7\\u0131k ameliyat<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;ve&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">artroskopik ameliyat<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;isimleri verilir. A\\u00e7\\u0131k ameliyat s\\u00fcrecinde cerrah etkilenen eklem veya tendon \\u00fczerinde genellikle yakla\\u015f\\u0131k 5 cm uzunlu\\u011funda orta b\\u00fcy\\u00fckl\\u00fckte bir kesi yapar.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Artroskopik ameliyat<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;s\\u00fcrecinde ise cerrah \\u00e7ok k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir kesi yapar, ve eklemin i\\u00e7ine- bir t\\u00fcr k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck kesilerin yap\\u0131ld\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve cerrah taraf\\u0131ndan eklemin i\\u00e7ine bakmak i\\u00e7in artroskop ad\\u0131 verilen k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir kameran\\u0131n kullan\\u0131ld\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 anahtar deli\\u011fi ameliyat\\u0131; artroskopu k\\u0131lavuz olarak kullanarak, kisti \\u00e7\\u0131karmak i\\u00e7in aletleri kesikten ge\\u00e7irirler. Her artroskopik cerrahi s\\u00fcrecinde ise cerrah \\u00e7ok daha k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir kesik yapar ve eklemin i\\u00e7ine bakmak i\\u00e7in artroskop ad\\u0131 verilen k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir kamera kullan\\u0131r. Cerrah i\\u00e7in bir k\\u0131lavuz i\\u015flevini g\\u00f6ren artroskop daha sonra kistin \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131lacak aletlerin kesiden ge\\u00e7irilmesine de yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Her iki teknik bireyin uyan\\u0131k oldu\\u011fu ancak herhangi bir a\\u011fr\\u0131 hissetmedi\\u011fi lokal anestezi alt\\u0131nda veya tamamen uyudu\\u011fu genel anestezi alt\\u0131nda yap\\u0131labilir. Hangi tekni\\u011fin kullan\\u0131laca\\u011f\\u0131 ganglionun konumu ile boyutlar\\u0131na, bireyin hangi anesteziyi tercih etti\\u011fine ve cerrah\\u0131n hangi y\\u00f6ntemin en etkili olaca\\u011f\\u0131na dair d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncelerine dayan\\u0131r. Her iki teknikte hem kistin \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lmas\\u0131nda ve hem de tekrarlama riskini azaltmada e\\u015fit derecede etkilidir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Artroskopik cerrahi, ameliyattan sonra daha az a\\u011fr\\u0131ya neden olma e\\u011filiminde olsa dahi, iyile\\u015fme i\\u00e7in bekleme s\\u00fcreci genellikle daha uzundur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ameliyattan sonra cerrah yaray\\u0131 diker ve b\\u00f6lgeye bir bandaj yerle\\u015ftirir. D\\u00fczenli olarak yenilenen bandaj yaran\\u0131n temiz kalmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur, enfeksiyon riskini azalt\\u0131r ve kaza eseri bir \\u00e7arpmadan korunmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flar. Yara genellikle a\\u011fr\\u0131l\\u0131 de\\u011fildir, ancak ameliyattan sonra bireyin herhangi bir rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k hissetmesi durumunda kullanmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in a\\u011fr\\u0131 kesici re\\u00e7ete edilebilir. Bile\\u011finden veya elinden kist \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lan bireylerin kolu kazara herhangi bir darbeye kar\\u015f\\u0131 korumaya yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in ilk birka\\u00e7 g\\u00fcn kol ask\\u0131s\\u0131 takmas\\u0131 gerekebilir. Kol ask\\u0131s\\u0131 \\u015fi\\u015flik ile rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 azaltmaya da yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir. Birey eklemlerin esnek kalmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olmak doktor aksini s\\u00f6ylemediyse i\\u00e7in parmaklar\\u0131n\\u0131 d\\u00fczenli olarak hareket ettirmelidir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bir&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">ganglion kistinin<\\/span>&nbsp;\\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ameliyat\\u0131 k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir cerrahi i\\u015flemdir, bu nedenle komplikasyonlar nadirdir olarak olu\\u015fur ve yine nadiren ciddidir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Baz\\u0131 vakalarda ganglion kistini \\u00e7\\u0131karmak i\\u00e7in yap\\u0131lan ameliyat sonras\\u0131nda, b\\u00f6lgede kal\\u0131n ve k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 bir yara izi kalabilir. Nadir vakalarda ise cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale sonras\\u0131 yara b\\u00f6lgesi uyu\\u015fuk kal\\u0131r. Ameliyattan sonra b\\u00f6lgede geli\\u015fen bir miktar morarma h\\u0131zla ge\\u00e7ecektir. E\\u011fer b\\u00f6lgede ge\\u00e7ici bir sertlik, \\u015fi\\u015fme veya a\\u011fr\\u0131 ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131karsa, bunun nedeni antibiyotiklerle tedavi edilebilen k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir enfeksiyon olabilir. Kal\\u0131c\\u0131 a\\u011fr\\u0131 veya sertlik ise fizyoterapi ile daha ileri tedavi y\\u00f6ntemlerine ba\\u015fvurmay\\u0131 gerekli k\\u0131labilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"G\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:09:31', '2023-12-20 16:11:03'),
