(598, 598, 89, 79, 1, 'Hafıza Kaybı', 10, 'hafiza-kaybi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Haf\\u0131za Kayb\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ya da t\\u0131bbi ad\\u0131yla\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">amnezi;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0hakikatler, bilgiler ve deneyimler gibi an\\u0131lar\\u0131n kayb\\u0131 ya da birey taraf\\u0131ndan hat\\u0131rlanmamas\\u0131 durumuna verilen isimdir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bireyin kim oldu\\u011funu unutmas\\u0131 filmlerde ve televizyonda yayg\\u0131n bir hikaye \\u00f6rg\\u00fcs\\u00fc arac\\u0131 olsa da, ger\\u00e7ek hayatta g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131 vakalar\\u0131nda durum\\u00a0 genellikle b\\u00f6yle de\\u011fildir. Ayn\\u0131 zamanda\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">amnestik sendrom<\\/span>\\u00a0olarak da adland\\u0131r\\u0131lan\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131<\\/span>\\u00a0durumundan muzdarip bireyler genellikle kim olduklar\\u0131n\\u0131 bilirler. Ancak,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">amnezi<\\/span>\\u00a0olan bireyler yeni bilgileri \\u00f6\\u011frenirken ve yeni an\\u0131lar olu\\u015ftururken g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fck \\u00e7ekebilirler.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0haf\\u0131zan\\u0131n i\\u015flenmesi i\\u00e7in hayati \\u00f6nem ta\\u015f\\u0131yan beyin b\\u00f6lgelerinde meydana gelen hasardan kaynaklanabilir. Ge\\u00e7ici bir haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131 olay\\u0131n\\u0131n yani ge\\u00e7ici\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">k\\u00fcresel amnezi aksine<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">,\\u00a0<\\/span><u style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">amnezi kal\\u0131c\\u0131 olabilir<\\/u><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131 i\\u00e7in spesifik bir tedavi y\\u00f6ntemi yoktur, ancak haf\\u0131zay\\u0131 geli\\u015ftirme teknikleri ile ve profesyonel psikolojik destek, haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131 olan bireylerin ve ailelerinin durum ile ba\\u015fa \\u00e7\\u0131kmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Haf\\u0131za Kayb\\u0131 Neden Olur?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Normal haf\\u0131za s\\u00fcreci beynin birden fazla farkl\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015fir. Bu nedenle beyni etkileyen herhangi bir hastal\\u0131k veya yaralanma haf\\u0131za s\\u00fcrecine m\\u00fcdahale edebilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Haf\\u0131za kayb\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0bireyin duygular\\u0131n\\u0131 ve an\\u0131lar\\u0131n\\u0131 kontrol eden limbik sistemi olu\\u015fturan beyin yap\\u0131lar\\u0131n\\u0131n zarar g\\u00f6rmesinden kaynaklanabilir. Bu yap\\u0131lar aras\\u0131nda beynin merkezinin derinliklerinde yer alan\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">talamus<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ile beynin\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">temporal loblar\\u0131nda<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0yer alan\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">hipokampal<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0olu\\u015fumlar bulunur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appear