(602, 602, 89, 79, 1, 'İdrar Yolu Enfeksiyonu', 11, 'idrar-yolu-enfeksiyonu', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u0130drar Yolu Enfeksiyonu\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00dcriner sistem enfeksiyonlar\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;olarak da adland\\u0131r\\u0131lan idrar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131, idrar yolunun herhangi bir b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde, b\\u00f6brekler ve \\u00fcreterlerden mesaneye ve idrar yoluna kadar olan enfeksiyonlard\\u0131r. Sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir insan\\u0131n idrar\\u0131nda bakteri (mikrop) yoktur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bazen, v\\u00fccut d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131ndaki bakteriler idrar yoluna girer ve enfeksiyona neden olur. Enfeksiyon, \\u00fcretray\\u0131 (idrar\\u0131 mesaneden d\\u0131\\u015far\\u0131yla y\\u00f6nlendiren t\\u00fcp), b\\u00f6brekleri veya mesaneyi etkileyebilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n<\\/span>&nbsp;i\\u00e7inde en s\\u0131k g\\u00f6r\\u00fclenlerin ba\\u015f\\u0131nda mesanenin enfeksiyonu olan sistit hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 gelmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u0130drar Yolu Enfeksiyonu Belirtileri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonunun belirtileri \\u015funlard\\u0131r;<\\/span><\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">S\\u0131k idrara \\u00e7\\u0131kma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drar yaparken a\\u011fr\\u0131 veya yanma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Ate\\u015f<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Yorgunluk<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drarda kan\\u0131n var olabilece\\u011fini g\\u00f6steren koyu renkli, bulan\\u0131k veya k\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131ms\\u0131 renkte olan idrar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">K\\u00f6t\\u00fc kokulu idrar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">\\u00d6zellikle kad\\u0131nlarda, pelvik (alt kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesi) a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kaburgalar\\u0131n alt\\u0131nda arka veya yanda a\\u011fr\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Bulant\\u0131 ve \\/ veya kusma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">S\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k hissine ra\\u011fmen sadece az miktarda idrar yapmak<\\/li><\\/ul><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kad\\u0131nlarda s\\u0131kl\\u0131kla g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n ba\\u015f\\u0131nda gelmektedir. Bir\\u00e7ok kad\\u0131n ya\\u015famlar\\u0131 boyunca birden fazla defa idrar yolu enfeksiyonu ge\\u00e7irebilir. Bunun temel nedeni, \\u00fcretra ad\\u0131 verilen ve idrar\\u0131 mesaneden d\\u0131\\u015f ortama ta\\u015f\\u0131yan t\\u00fcp \\u015feklindeki yap\\u0131n\\u0131n kad\\u0131nlarda erkeklere k\\u0131yasla daha k\\u0131sa olmas\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">D\\u0131\\u015f ortamdaki bakteriler, kad\\u0131nlarda daha k\\u0131sa bir yol kat ederek mesaneye ula\\u015fabilmektedir. Buna ek olarak, idrar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n cinsel olarak aktif olan kad\\u0131nlarda ve do\\u011fum kontrol y\\u00f6ntemi olarak diafram ve spermisidal (sperm \\u00f6ld\\u00fcr\\u00fcc\\u00fc) krem kullanan kad\\u0131nlarda daha s\\u0131k oldu\\u011fu saptanm\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131r. Bunlar\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra, idrar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na menopoz sonras\\u0131 d\\u00f6nemde de s\\u0131k rastlanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\\u0130drar Yolu Enfeksiyonu Tan\\u0131 Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Normal idrar sterildir. \\u0130\\u00e7inde herhangi bir bakteri, vir\\u00fcs veya mantar bulunmaz, \\u00e7o\\u011fu zaman sindirim sistemindeki mikroplar idrar yoluna girdi\\u011finde ve \\u00e7o\\u011falmaya ba\\u015flad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda idrar yolu enfeksiyonu olu\\u015fur. Bu \\u015fekilde olu\\u015fan enfeksiyonlar genellikle sindirim sisteminde do\\u011fal olarak bulunan koli basili (Escherichia coli)&nbsp; bakterisinden kaynaklan\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunun yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">herpes, gonore, klamidya&nbsp;<\\/span>ve&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">mikoplazma<\\/span>&nbsp;gibi cinsel yolla bula\\u015fan enfeksiyonlar da, idrar yollar\\u0131 enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na, \\u00f6zellikle \\u00fcretritlere, yol a\\u00e7abilirler. \\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131 te\\u015fhis etmek i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131lan baz\\u0131 testler a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131daki gibidir:<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drar Tahlili<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drarda bulunabilecek kanamalar\\u0131, savunma h\\u00fccrelerini, mikroplar\\u0131 (bakteriler), \\u00e7e\\u015fitli proteinleri ve idrar\\u0131n \\u00f6zelliklerini tespit eder.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drar K\\u00fclt\\u00fcr\\u00fc<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Enfeksiyona neden olan bakteri veya mantarlar\\u0131 te\\u015fhis ederek ve bunlara uygun tedaviyi tespit etmeye olanak sa\\u011flar<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonu<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;tekrarlanan bir problem haline gelirse, idrar yolunun normal olup olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 g\\u00f6rmek i\\u00e7in ba\\u015fka testler de kullan\\u0131labilir. Bu testlerden baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Sistoskopi<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu tetkikte hekim mesanenizin ve idrar yolunuzun i\\u00e7 k\\u0131sm\\u0131n\\u0131 inceler. Genellikle idrar yolu iltihab\\u0131, b\\u00f6brek veya mesane ta\\u015flar\\u0131 ve mesane t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri gibi idrar yolu rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 te\\u015fhis etmek ve de\\u011ferlendirmek i\\u00e7in de kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">B\\u00f6brek ve Mesane Ultrasonu<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Y\\u00fcksek frekansl\\u0131 ses dalgalar\\u0131n\\u0131 kullan\\u0131larak, mesane ve b\\u00f6breklerin b\\u00fcy\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcn\\u00fc, \\u015feklini g\\u00f6sterir. Tekrarlayan idrar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na neden olabilecek kitle, ta\\u015f, kist, t\\u0131kan\\u0131kl\\u0131k ve anormallikleri kontrol eder.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Bilgisayarl\\u0131 Tomografi (BT)<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drar yolunun ayr\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fclemesini yapmak i\\u00e7in X-\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nlar\\u0131 kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\\u0130drar Yolu Enfeksiyonu Tedavi Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Antibiyotikler genellikle idrar yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131 i\\u00e7in ilk basamak olarak kullan\\u0131lan tedavilerdir. Hangi ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n re\\u00e7ete edilece\\u011fi ve ne kadar s\\u00fcreyle kullan\\u0131laca\\u011f\\u0131 sa\\u011fl\\u0131k durumunuza ve idrar\\u0131n\\u0131zda bulunan bakteri t\\u00fcr\\u00fcne g\\u00f6re hekiminiz taraf\\u0131ndan belirlenecektir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunun d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda, su t\\u00fcketimini artt\\u0131rman\\u0131z da tedavinizin bir par\\u00e7as\\u0131 olarak hekiminiz taraf\\u0131ndan tavsiye edilebilir. \\u0130drar yolu enfeksiyonu ge\\u00e7irme riskini azaltmak i\\u00e7in al\\u0131nabilecek \\u00f6nlemler a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131daki gibidir:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Bol miktarda su t\\u00fcketmek<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">\\u0130drar tutmaktan ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Tuvalet sonras\\u0131 temizli\\u011fi \\u00f6nden arkaya do\\u011fru yapmak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Cinsel ili\\u015fkiden \\u00f6nce ve sonra genital b\\u00f6lgeyi temizlemek<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Cinsel ili\\u015fki sonras\\u0131nda idrar yapmak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Genital b\\u00f6lge temizli\\u011finde sabun kullan\\u0131m\\u0131ndan ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Hijyenik pedleri s\\u0131k de\\u011fi\\u015ftirmek<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Pamuklu i\\u00e7 \\u00e7ama\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 giymek ve s\\u0131k\\u0131, oturan k\\u0131yafetlerden ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmak.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u0130\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:20:42', '2023-12-20 16:22:41'),
