(606, 606, 89, 79, 1, 'Jinekomasti', 12, 'jinekomasti', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Jinekomasti\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">erkeklerde \\u00f6strojen ve testosteron hormonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n dengesizli\\u011fi nedeniyle meme dokusu miktar\\u0131ndaki anormal ancak iyi huylu b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmeye verilen isimdir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">baz\\u0131 vakalarda bir, baz\\u0131 vakalarda iki memeyi birden etkileyebilir. Her iki meme de d\\u00fczensiz olarak etkilenip birbirinden farkl\\u0131 boyutlara ula\\u015fabilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yenido\\u011fanlar, ergenlik \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131ndaki erkekler ve ya\\u015fl\\u0131 erkekler, hormon d\\u00fczeylerindeki normal de\\u011fi\\u015fikliklerin bir sonucu olarak jinekomasti geli\\u015ftirebilirler. Ancak jinekomasti geli\\u015fmesi i\\u00e7in ba\\u015fka nedenler de mevcuttur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;bir\\u00e7ok vakada ciddi bir sorun de\\u011fildir, ancak bu durumla ba\\u015f etmek bireyler i\\u00e7in zor olabilir. Jinekomastili erkeklerin g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcslerinde a\\u011fr\\u0131 hissetti\\u011fi durumlar g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. Baz\\u0131 vakalarda ise bireyin durumdan dolay\\u0131 utanma hissetmesi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilmektedir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f nedenine g\\u00f6re, kimi hastalarda kendili\\u011finden iyile\\u015febilir, kimi hastalarda ise sorunun \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcm\\u00fc i\\u00e7in ila\\u00e7 tedavisi veya ameliyat gerekli olabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Jinekomasti Neden Olur?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, s\\u0131kl\\u0131kla testosteron hormonunun d\\u00fczeyindeki dalgalanmalardan kaynaklan\\u0131r. Testosteron hormonu miktar\\u0131ndaki d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fc\\u015f bireyde testosteronun etkilerini bloke eden, testosteronu azaltan veya \\u00f6strojen seviyesini art\\u0131ran ko\\u015fullardan kaynaklanabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccuttaki hormon dengesi bir\\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 nedenden dolay\\u0131 bozulabilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Jinekomastinin nedenleri&nbsp;<\\/span>aras\\u0131nda do\\u011fal hormon de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikleri, ila\\u00e7 kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, uyu\\u015fturucu ve alkol kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sa\\u011fl\\u0131k ko\\u015fullar\\u0131ndan kaynaklanan komplikasyonlar ve baz\\u0131 bitkisel \\u00fcr\\u00fcnler ile takviyelerin kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 yer al\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Testosteron ve \\u00f6strojen hormonlar\\u0131 hem erkeklerde hem de kad\\u0131nlarda cinsiyet \\u00f6zelliklerini kontrol eder. Testosteron, kas k\\u00fctlesi ve v\\u00fccut k\\u0131l\\u0131 gibi erkeksi \\u00f6zellikleri kontrol ederken, \\u00f6strojen, g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcslerin b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmesi de dahil olmak \\u00fczere kad\\u0131ns\\u0131 \\u00f6zellikleri kontrol eder.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00d6strojen kad\\u0131nl\\u0131k hormonu olarak tan\\u0131mlansa dahi, normal \\u015fartlar alt\\u0131nda \\u00e7ok k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck miktarlarda erkeklerde de \\u00fcretir. Normalin \\u00e7ok \\u00fczerinde \\u00f6strojen \\u00fcretimi, ya da testosteron seviyesi ile dengesiz oranda \\u00f6strojen \\u00fcretimi jinekomastiye neden olabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Erkek bebekler, do\\u011fumdan \\u00f6nce annelerinin v\\u00fccudunda bulunan \\u00f6strojeninin etkisiyle b\\u00fcy\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u015f g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcslerle do\\u011fabilir. Bu \\u015fi\\u015fmi\\u015f meme dokusu bir \\u00e7ok vakada do\\u011fumdan sonra iki ila \\u00fc\\u00e7 hafta i\\u00e7inde kaybolur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ergenlik d\\u00f6neminde s\\u00fcrekli de\\u011fi\\u015fen hormon seviyeleri nedeniyle&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">jinekomasti<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmesi ihtimali nispeten yayg\\u0131nd\\u0131r. Ergenlik d\\u00f6neminde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">jinekomasti&nbsp;<\\/span>vakalar\\u0131n\\u0131n b\\u00fcy\\u00fck bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131nda \\u015fi\\u015fmi\\u015f meme dokusu tedavi edilmeden kaybolur.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Jinekomasti Belirtileri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomastinin belirti&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ve<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;semptomlar\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;aras\\u0131nda \\u00f6ncelikle \\u015fi\\u015fmi\\u015f meme dokusu ve kimi zaman g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcslerde hassasiyet bulunur. G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcste \\u015fi\\u015flik, a\\u011fr\\u0131, veya hassasiyet ya da bir bir veya her iki memede meme ba\\u015f\\u0131 ak\\u0131nt\\u0131s\\u0131 olmas\\u0131 durumunda bireyin bir an \\u00f6nce doktora ba\\u015fvurmas\\u0131 gereklidir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Jinekomasti Nas\\u0131l Te\\u015fhis Edilir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti tan\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131n<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;konulmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in doktor \\u00f6ncelikle bir fizik muayene ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirir ve hem hastan\\u0131n hem de ailesinin sa\\u011fl\\u0131k ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fi hakk\\u0131ndaki bilgileri soraca\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sorular ile \\u00f6\\u011frenmeyi hedefler. Hasta g\\u00f6zlemledi\\u011fi b\\u00fct\\u00fcn belirtilerini bu muayene s\\u00fcrecinde doktor ile konu\\u015fmal\\u0131 ve sahip olabilece\\u011fi di\\u011fer ko\\u015fullar veya hastal\\u0131klarla ilgili bilgileri payla\\u015fmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Doktor fizik muayene s\\u00fcrecinde meme dokusunu de\\u011ferlendirerek di\\u011fer sistem kontrollerini ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirecektir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Jinekomasti tan\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/span>&nbsp;konulan vakalarda doktor durumun nedenini belirlemek i\\u00e7in kan testleri yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131 uygun g\\u00f6rebilir. Bu ilk test sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak bilgisayarl\\u0131 tomografi taramalar\\u0131, manyetik rezonans g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme taramalar\\u0131, testis ultrasonu ve doku biyopsisi gibi daha ileri testlerin yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131na ihtiya\\u00e7 duyulabilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;s\\u00fcrecinde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen meme \\u015fi\\u015fli\\u011fine benzer belirti ve semptomlara sahip birka\\u00e7 di\\u011fer durum vard\\u0131r. Bunlardan ilki a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 ya\\u011fl\\u0131 meme dokusudur. Baz\\u0131 erkeklerde jinekomastiye benzeyen g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs ya\\u011f\\u0131 tabakas\\u0131 vard\\u0131r. Bu&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">jinekomasti<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;ile ayn\\u0131 durum de\\u011fildir ve ek de\\u011ferlendirmeye ihtiya\\u00e7 duymaz.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Meme kanseri erkeklerde nadiren g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr. Tek memenin b\\u00fcy\\u00fcd\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc, ya da meme i\\u00e7inde sert bir nod\\u00fcl\\u00fcn varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n oldu\\u011fu durumlarda erkek meme kanseri olmas\\u0131 ihtimali g\\u00f6z \\u00f6n\\u00fcne al\\u0131nmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Meme dokusunun enfeksiyonu olan g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs apsesi de memede b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmeye yol a\\u00e7abilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Jinekomasti Nas\\u0131l Tedavi Edilir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kendili\\u011finden d\\u00fczelmezse ya da bireyin hayat kalitesini etkileyecek kadar ciddi a\\u011fr\\u0131, hassasiyet veya psikolojik sorunlar yarat\\u0131rsa tedavi gerekebilir. Uygulanan tedaviler ila\\u00e7 kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 veya cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale \\u015feklinde olabilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Jinekomasti i\\u00e7in yayg\\u0131n olarak kullan\\u0131lan iki farkl\\u0131 cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale yakla\\u015f\\u0131m\\u0131 vard\\u0131r.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Liposuction<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, yani ya\\u011f emme ameliyat\\u0131nda cerrah sadece meme ya\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 al\\u0131r, ancak meme bezi dokusunu geride b\\u0131rak\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Mastektomi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">t\\u00fcr\\u00fc cerrahi m\\u00fcdahalelerde ise meme bezi dokusu cerrah taraf\\u0131ndan b\\u00fct\\u00fcn\\u00fcyle \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131l\\u0131r. Bu ameliyat genellikle sadece k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck kesiler kullan\\u0131larak yap\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"J\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:23:13', '2023-12-20 16:25:07'),
