(610, 610, 89, 79, 1, 'K Vitamini', 13, 'k-vitamini', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"K Vitamini\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K vitamini,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 kanamalar\\u0131 \\u00f6nlemek i\\u00e7in kan\\u0131n p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur. Di\\u011fer bir\\u00e7ok vitaminin aksine,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;tipik olarak bir besin takviyesi olarak kullan\\u0131lamamaktad\\u0131r. \\u00c7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc K vitamini asl\\u0131nda bir grup bile\\u015fiktir ve bu bile\\u015fiklerin en \\u00f6nemlileri&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K1&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ve&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K2&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">vitaminidir.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K1 Vitamini&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00e7o\\u011funlukla filokinon bitkilerden yani ye\\u015fil yaprakl\\u0131 sebzelerden elde edilir.<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;K2 Vitamini<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;(menakinon), b\\u00fcy\\u00fck \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcde et, peynir ve yumurtadan elde edilir ve bakterilerden sentezlenir. Her iki alt t\\u00fcr\\u00fc de v\\u00fccutta benzer \\u015fekilde \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">K vitamini,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kan p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131nda \\u00f6nemli rol oynar. P\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fma, v\\u00fccudun hem i\\u00e7inde hem de d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 kanamay\\u0131 \\u00f6nlemeye yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 bir i\\u015flemdir. P\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fma s\\u00fcrecinde i\\u015fe yarayan proteinleri \\u00fcretmek i\\u00e7in v\\u00fccudun K vitaminine ihtiyac\\u0131 vard\\u0131r. K vitamini eksikli\\u011fi olan ki\\u015filerin v\\u00fccudunda bu protein yeterli de\\u011fildir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bebeklerde - yeti\\u015fkinlerde&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">K vitamini eksikli\\u011fi&nbsp;<\\/span>nadirdir \\u00e7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc yenilen yiyeceklerin \\u00e7o\\u011fu yeterli miktarda K1 i\\u00e7erir ve v\\u00fccut kendi ba\\u015f\\u0131na K2 yapar. Ayr\\u0131ca v\\u00fccut mevcut K vitamini kayna\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 geri d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fcrmede de iyidir. \\u0130\\u00e7inde olunan belli ko\\u015fullar ya da kullan\\u0131lan baz\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lara ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak, besinlerle beraber al\\u0131nan miktar\\u0131n yeterli olmamas\\u0131, v\\u00fccutta \\u00fcretiminde problem olmas\\u0131 gibi nedenlerle K vitamini emilimi ve olu\\u015fumu yetersiz kalabilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">K vitamini eksikli\\u011fi<\\/span>, kanama bozukluklar\\u0131 ile kendini g\\u00f6stermektedir. Bebeklerde kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan K vitamini eksikli\\u011finde d\\u0131\\u015far\\u0131dan vitamin takviyesi verilmesi gerekebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u0130nsanlar Neden K Vitamini Al\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">D\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">K vitamini seviyeleri<\\/span>, kontrols\\u00fcz kanama riskini art\\u0131rabilir. Yeti\\u015fkinlerde K vitamini eksiklikleri nadir olmakla birlikte yeni do\\u011fan bebeklerde \\u00e7ok yayg\\u0131nd\\u0131r. Yeni do\\u011fanlar i\\u00e7in tek bir K vitamini enjeksiyonu standartt\\u0131r.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">K Vitamini<\\/span>&nbsp;ayr\\u0131ca kan inceltici ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 dozunu \\u00f6nlemek i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Hangi Besinler K Vitamini Y\\u00f6n\\u00fcnden Zengindir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<section class=\\\"part hashContent detailedContent general\\\" id=\\\"general\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px;\\\"><p style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\">K vitamini ya\\u011fda \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcnen bir vitamindir ve tereya\\u011f\\u0131, zeytinya\\u011f\\u0131 gibi ya\\u011flarla bir arada t\\u00fcketmek emilimini artt\\u0131r\\u0131r.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ispanak, paz\\u0131, brokoli, karnabahar, pancar yapra\\u011f\\u0131, maydanoz, ku\\u015fkonmaz, kekik, fesle\\u011fen, taze so\\u011fan, marul, &nbsp; lahana, bezelye, domates, kereviz taze fasulye gibi sebzeler<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Et \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri, s\\u00fct \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri, yumurta, sakatatlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Nar, kivi, b\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcrtlen, \\u00e7ilek, avokado, incir gibi meyveler<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">F\\u0131nd\\u0131k, ceviz, kaju, pikan cevizi gibi kuru yemi\\u015fler<\\/li><\\/ul><\\/section>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"K Vitamini Eksikli\\u011fi Nedenleri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Besinler beraberinde K vitamini al\\u0131nmamas\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra bir\\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 nedenden \\u00f6t\\u00fcr\\u00fc geli\\u015febilen bir problemdir.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kan suland\\u0131r\\u0131c\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n kullan\\u0131m\\u0131<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Antibiyotik kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 v\\u00fccutta \\u00fcretilen K vitamini miktar\\u0131n\\u0131n azalt\\u0131lmas\\u0131nda rol oynar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">K vitamini y\\u00f6n\\u00fcnden yetersiz bir beslenme plan\\u0131n\\u0131n uygulanmas\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">V\\u00fccutta besinlerle al\\u0131nan ya\\u011flar\\u0131n emiliminde bozukluklara neden olan hastal\\u0131klar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/colyak-hastaligi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7\\u00f6lyak<\\/span><\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/crohn-ve-kolit-tedavisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Crohn<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ve&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/iltihabi-bagirsak-hastaliklari-crohn-hastaligi-ve-ulseratif-kolit\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00fclseratif kolit<\\/span><\\/a>gibi inflamatuar ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/pankreas-karaciger-ve-safra-yollari-hastaliklarinin-tedavisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Karaci\\u011fer<\\/span><\\/a>ve&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/safra-kesesi-iltihabi-kolesistit\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">safra yollar\\u0131na<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ili\\u015fkin rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/kistik-fibrosiz\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kistik fibrozis<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Ba\\u011f\\u0131rsaklar\\u0131n belli bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f olmas\\u0131<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Yenido\\u011fan bebeklerde K vitamini eksikli\\u011finde rol oynayan nedenler:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Anne s\\u00fct\\u00fcn\\u00fcn K vitamini bak\\u0131m\\u0131ndan yeterli olmamas\\u0131<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">K vitamininin anne plasentas\\u0131ndan bebe\\u011fe do\\u011fru bir \\u015fekilde ge\\u00e7memesi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Yenido\\u011fan bebeklerde ya\\u015fam\\u0131n ilk d\\u00f6neminde v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan K2 vitamini \\u00fcretememesi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Yenido\\u011fan bebekte ya\\u015fam\\u0131n ilk d\\u00f6neminde karaci\\u011ferin yeterli \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcde kullan\\u0131lam\\u0131yor olmas\\u0131<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"K Vitamini Hangi Hastal\\u0131klardan Korur?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/karaciger-kanseri\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Karaci\\u011fer kanseri<\\/span><\\/a><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/osteoporoz-kemik-erimesi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Osteoporoz<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/prostat-kanseri\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Prostat kanseri<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/buyuk-damar-hastaliklari\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kalp ve damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/kireclenme\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Eklem kire\\u00e7lenmeleri<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/alzheimer-ve-yaslanma\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Alzheimer<\\/span><\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/kalp-krizi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Kalp krizi<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;ve damar sertli\\u011fi<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"K\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:27:56', '2023-12-20 16:29:42'),
