(614, 614, 89, 79, 1, 'Laparoskopi', 14, 'laparoskopi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Laparoskopi\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">geli\\u015fen \\u00e7e\\u015fitli hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ya da tedavisi s\\u00fcrecinde kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesindeki organlar\\u0131 incelemek i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131lan cerrahi bir te\\u015fhis prosed\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Halk aras\\u0131nda kapal\\u0131 ameliyat olarak da bilinen laparoskopi, bat\\u0131n i\\u00e7erisine k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck kesiler ile girilerek bir kamera ve cerrahi enstr\\u00fcmanlarla yap\\u0131lan bir cerrahi y\\u00f6ntemdir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesindeki organlara bakmak i\\u00e7in&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">laparoskop<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;ad\\u0131 verilen bir alet kullan\\u0131r. Laparoskop, \\u00f6n\\u00fcnde y\\u00fcksek yo\\u011funluklu bir \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131k ve y\\u00fcksek \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcrl\\u00fckl\\u00fc bir kamera bulunan uzun, ince bir t\\u00fcpt\\u00fcr. Alet, kar\\u0131n duvar\\u0131ndaki bir kesiden kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesine sokulur. Kamera ilerledik\\u00e7e elde etti\\u011fi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleri bir video monit\\u00f6r\\u00fcne g\\u00f6nderir ve doktorun v\\u00fccudun i\\u00e7ini a\\u00e7\\u0131k ameliyat olmadan ger\\u00e7ek zamanl\\u0131 olarak g\\u00f6rmesini sa\\u011flar. Bu i\\u015flem s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda gerekli oldu\\u011fu takdirde biyopsi \\u00f6rne\\u011fi al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 da m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Laparoskopi Neden Yap\\u0131l\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bir\\u00e7ok vakada abdominal sorunlar v\\u00fccut g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fclerini olu\\u015fturmak i\\u00e7in y\\u00fcksek frekansl\\u0131 ses dalgalar\\u0131n\\u0131 kullanan ultrason, \\u00f6zel t\\u00fcr r\\u00f6ntgen \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nlar\\u0131ndan faydalanan bilgisayarl\\u0131 tomografi ve m\\u0131knat\\u0131slar ile&nbsp; radyo dalgalar\\u0131n\\u0131 kullanan manyetik rezonans g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme taramas\\u0131 gibi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme teknikleriyle de te\\u015fhis edilebilir.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;Laparoskopi<\\/span>, bu testler te\\u015fhis i\\u00e7in yeterli bilgi veya \\u00f6ng\\u00f6r\\u00fc sa\\u011flamad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 durumlarda yap\\u0131labilir. Prosed\\u00fcr ayn\\u0131 zamanda kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesindeki belirli bir organdan bir biyopsi veya doku \\u00f6rne\\u011fi almak i\\u00e7in de kullan\\u0131labilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Doktor bireyin&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">apandisit, safra kesesi, karaci\\u011fer, pankreas, ince&nbsp;<\\/span>ve&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kal\\u0131n ba\\u011f\\u0131rsaklar, dalak, mide<\\/span>&nbsp;ya da&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">pelvik<\\/span>&nbsp;veya&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00fcreme organlar\\u0131<\\/span>&nbsp;gibi organlar\\u0131n\\u0131n incelenmesi ve bu organlar \\u00fczerinde ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilecek i\\u015flemler i\\u00e7in laparoskopi \\u00f6nerebilir. Laparoskop yard\\u0131m\\u0131yla doktor bu b\\u00f6lgeleri g\\u00f6zlemleyerek abdominal kitle veya t\\u00fcm\\u00f6r varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131, bir kanserin ilerleme derecesini, kar\\u0131n bo\\u015flu\\u011funda s\\u0131v\\u0131 olup olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131, karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131, ve belirli tedavilerin etkinlik seviyelerini saptayabilir.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;Laparoskopi i\\u015fleminin&nbsp;<\\/span>tercih edilme sebeplerinden biri de<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span>hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n te\\u015fhisinden hemen sonra, bireyin durumunu tedavi etmek i\\u00e7in doktorlara m\\u00fcdahale yapabilme f\\u0131rsat\\u0131 sa\\u011flar.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopik cerrahiyle<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;i\\u015fkili riskler aras\\u0131nda, di\\u011fer ameliyat t\\u00fcrlerinde de g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilecek kanama, enfeksiyon ve kar\\u0131n i\\u00e7i organlar\\u0131n hasar g\\u00f6rmesi bulunur. Ancak bu durumlar nadir g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen olaylard\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Laparoskopiye Nas\\u0131l Haz\\u0131rlan\\u0131l\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Birey doktoruna mutlaka kulland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 re\\u00e7eteli veya re\\u00e7etesiz ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 bildirmelidir. Doktor bireye i\\u015flemden \\u00f6nce ve sonra hangi ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 nas\\u0131l kullan\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gerekti\\u011fini ifade edecektir. Doktor, laparoskopinin sonucunu etkileyebilecek kan incelticiler ya da kan\\u0131n p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyen di\\u011fer ila\\u00e7lar, her t\\u00fcrl\\u00fc bitkisel veya diyet takviyeleri ile K vitamini gibi herhangi bir ilac\\u0131n dozunu de\\u011fi\\u015ftirebilir.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hamile olan veya hamile oldu\\u011funu d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnen bireyler bunu da doktora bildirmelidir. Bu geli\\u015fmekte olan fet\\u00fcse zarar verme riskini azaltacakt\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi \\u00f6ncesinde doktor kan testleri, idrar tahlili, elektrokardiyogram ile g\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs r\\u00f6ntgeni&nbsp; isteyebilir ve ayr\\u0131ca ultrason, bilgisayarl\\u0131 tomografi taramas\\u0131 veya manyetik rezonans g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme taramas\\u0131 dahil olmak \\u00fczere g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme testlerinin yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131 da gerekli g\\u00f6rebilir. Bu testler, doktorun laparoskopi s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda incelenen anormalli\\u011fi daha iyi anlamas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir. Sonu\\u00e7lar ayr\\u0131ca doktora bireyin karn\\u0131n\\u0131n i\\u00e7 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri i\\u00e7in g\\u00f6rsel bir rehber sa\\u011flar ve laparoskopinin etkinli\\u011fini art\\u0131r\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Doktor bireye laparoskopiden \\u00f6nce muhtemelen en az sekiz saat boyunca yemekten ve i\\u00e7mekten ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmas\\u0131 gerekti\\u011fini ifade edecektir. \\u00d6te yandan laparoskopi yayg\\u0131n olarak genel anestezi kullan\\u0131larak yap\\u0131l\\u0131r, bu da bireyi uykulu hale getirebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Laparoskopi Nas\\u0131l Yap\\u0131l\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu t\\u00fcr ameliyatlar i\\u00e7in yayg\\u0131n olarak genel&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/tibbi-birim\\/anesteziyoloji\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">anestezi<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;verilir. Bu, prosed\\u00fcr boyunca bireyin uyuyaca\\u011f\\u0131 ve herhangi bir ac\\u0131 hissetmeyece\\u011fi anlam\\u0131na gelir. Genel anestezi s\\u00fcrecinde bireyin damarlar\\u0131ndan birine intraven\\u00f6z yani damar i\\u00e7i bir hat yerle\\u015ftirilir. Bu intraven\\u00f6z hat arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla, anestezi uzman\\u0131 bireye \\u00f6zel ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 verebilir ve s\\u0131v\\u0131larla gerekli hidrasyon sa\\u011flayabilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda cerrah g\\u00f6bek deli\\u011finin alt\\u0131na bir kesi yapar ve ard\\u0131ndan bu kesinin i\\u00e7ine kan\\u00fcl ad\\u0131 verilen k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck bir t\\u00fcp yerle\\u015ftirir. Kan\\u00fcl, bireyin karn\\u0131n\\u0131 karbondioksit gaz\\u0131 ile \\u015fi\\u015firmek i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r. Bu gaz, doktorun kar\\u0131n organlar\\u0131n\\u0131z\\u0131 daha net g\\u00f6rmesini sa\\u011flar. Kar\\u0131n b\\u00f6lgesinin karbondioksit gazi ile \\u015fi\\u015firilmesinin ard\\u0131ndan cerrah trokar ad\\u0131 verilen kanallar vas\\u0131tas\\u0131yla laparoskopu kesiden i\\u00e7eriye sokar. Laparoskop ucunda yer alan kamera, g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleri bir ekranda g\\u00f6stererek bireyin organlar\\u0131n\\u0131n ger\\u00e7ek zamanl\\u0131 olarak g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fclenmesini sa\\u011flar.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda a\\u00e7\\u0131lacak kesilerin say\\u0131s\\u0131 ve boyutu, cerrah\\u0131n hangi belirli hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 do\\u011frulamaya veya ekarte etmeye \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na g\\u00f6re de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterebilir. Yayg\\u0131n olarak her biri 1 ila 2 santimetre uzunlu\\u011funda bir ila d\\u00f6rt kesi yap\\u0131l\\u0131r. Bu kesiler sayesinde cerrah\\u0131n biyopsi yapmak i\\u00e7in kullanmas\\u0131 gereken ba\\u015fka bir cerrahi alet gibi di\\u011fer aletleri de kar\\u0131n bo\\u015flu\\u011funa yerle\\u015ftirmek m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn olur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopi i\\u015flemleri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;tamamland\\u0131ktan sonra aletler \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131l\\u0131r. Kesiler daha sonra diki\\u015flerle kapat\\u0131l\\u0131r. Baz\\u0131 durumlarda kesilerin \\u00fczerine bandaj yerle\\u015ftirilebilir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Laparoskopi Kesileri Ne Kadar S\\u00fcrede \\u0130yile\\u015fir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Genellikle&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">laparoskopi&nbsp;<\\/span>sonras\\u0131nda bir hafta i\\u00e7inde birey t\\u00fcm normal aktivitelere devam edebilir. Laparoskopiden yakla\\u015f\\u0131k iki hafta sonra doktor ile bir takip randevusuna yap\\u0131lmal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Taburcu olma s\\u00fcresi bireyin genel fiziksel durumu, prosed\\u00fcr s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda kullan\\u0131lan anestezi t\\u00fcr\\u00fc ve bireyin v\\u00fccudunun ameliyata verdi\\u011fi tepkiye g\\u00f6re de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterir.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Laparoskopiyi takip eden g\\u00fcnlerde, birey kesi yap\\u0131lan b\\u00f6lgelerde orta derecede a\\u011fr\\u0131 hissedebilir. Herhangi bir a\\u011fr\\u0131 veya rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k birka\\u00e7 g\\u00fcn i\\u00e7inde ge\\u00e7melidir. Doktor a\\u011fr\\u0131y\\u0131 hafifletmek i\\u00e7in ila\\u00e7 yazabilir. Birey iyile\\u015fme s\\u00fcrecini daha sorunsuz bir hale getirmek \\u00fczere \\u00e7e\\u015fitli ad\\u0131mlar atabilir. Bu ad\\u0131mlar aras\\u0131nda kan p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131 riskini azaltmak i\\u00e7in m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn olan en k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcrede hafif aktivitelere ba\\u015flamak ve bol k\\u0131yafetler giymek bulunur.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"L\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:30:50', '2023-12-20 16:33:28'),
