(618, 618, 89, 79, 1, 'Magnezyum', 15, 'magnezyum', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Magnezyum\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">v\\u00fccudun i\\u015flevi i\\u00e7in \\u00e7ok \\u00f6nemli bir mineraldir ve v\\u00fccutta en bol bulunan 4. mineraldir. V\\u00fccut bu minerali kendi ba\\u015f\\u0131na \\u00fcretmedi\\u011fi i\\u00e7in g\\u0131dalar ve gerekti\\u011finde de takviyeler vas\\u0131tas\\u0131yla al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 gereklidir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Enerji \\u00fcretimi, kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131n\\u0131n d\\u00fczenlenmesi, sinir sinyal iletimi ve kas kas\\u0131lmas\\u0131 dahil olmak \\u00fczere insan sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in gerekli olan 300\\u2019den fazla metabolik reaksiyonda yer al\\u0131r. B\\u00fct\\u00fcn bu fonksiyonlar\\u0131n yerine getirilebilmesi i\\u00e7in d\\u00fczenli olarak al\\u0131nmas\\u0131 ve v\\u00fccuttaki rezervlerin doldurulmas\\u0131 gerekir. \\u0130nsan v\\u00fccudunda magnezyumun %60\\u2019\\u0131 kemik ve di\\u015flerde, %39\\u2019u yumu\\u015fak dokularda, kalan %1\\u2019i ise kanda bulunmaktad\\u0131r.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Magnezyum<\\/span>, beyin ve kalpte di\\u011fer organlara nazaran daha yo\\u011fun olarak yer almaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131n\\u0131n normal seviyede seyretmesine, kemiklerin g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fc ve kalp ritminin sabit kalmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur. Ayr\\u0131ca d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck magnezyum seviyeleri k\\u0131sa vadede belirtilere neden olmasa da, tip 2 diyabet, kalp hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, duygu bozukluklar\\u0131 ve migren gibi rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klarla ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Tavsiye edilen magnezyum miktar\\u0131ndan daha az\\u0131n\\u0131 alan yeti\\u015fkinlerin, iltihap belirte\\u00e7lerinin artmas\\u0131 daha olas\\u0131d\\u0131r. \\u0130ltihaplanma ise kalp sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, diyabet ve baz\\u0131 kanserler ile ili\\u015fkilendirilmi\\u015ftir. Ayr\\u0131ca d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">magnezyum seviyesi<\\/span>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/osteoporoz-kemik-erimesi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">osteoporoz&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/a>i\\u00e7in bir risk fakt\\u00f6r\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Magnezyum ve di\\u011fer mineraller a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan zengin yiyecekler yemenin, prehipertansiyonlu ki\\u015filerde y\\u00fcksek tansiyonu \\u00f6nlemede yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilece\\u011fine dair kan\\u0131tlar mevcuttur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Damar i\\u00e7ine ya da kas i\\u00e7ine enjekte edilmi\\u015f magnezyum, hamilelikte eklampsi ve \\u015fiddetli ast\\u0131m ataklar\\u0131 gibi durumlar\\u0131 tedavi etmek i\\u00e7in kullan\\u0131l\\u0131r. Magnezyum, bir\\u00e7ok antasit ve m\\u00fcshildeki ana bile\\u015fendir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">4 ya\\u015f ve \\u00fczeri sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bireylerin g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck olarak 375 mg magnezyum almas\\u0131 gereklidir. Magnezyum eksikli\\u011fi durumunun varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda, doktorlar daha y\\u00fcksek dozajlar al\\u0131nmas\\u0131n\\u0131 tavsiye edebilir. Hastan\\u0131n takviyeye ihtiyac\\u0131 olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 noktada da kesebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Magnezyum Faydalar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kortizolu beyinde dengeleyen en etkili vitamin magnezyumdur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>V\\u00fccudun i\\u00e7 dengesinin sa\\u011flanabilmesi i\\u00e7in kan d\\u00fczeyinin normal seyretmesi gerekir. Ancak yanl\\u0131\\u015f beslenme ve v\\u00fccuda al\\u0131nan baz\\u0131 besinler kan d\\u00fczeyinin olumsuz etkilenmesine sebep olurken, magnezyumun g\\u00f6revi bu dengeyi sa\\u011flamakt\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>Mutluluk hormonunun dengede kalmas\\u0131 ad\\u0131na magnezyum elementi m\\u00fchimdir. Magnezyum v\\u00fccudunuzda yeterli bir miktarda varsa, depresyon ve kayg\\u0131 bozuklu\\u011fu ihtimalinin ya\\u015fanma ihtimali azalmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>V\\u00fccutta yorgunlu\\u011fun ve bitkinli\\u011fin azalmas\\u0131na katk\\u0131da bulunur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>Elektrolit dengesine katk\\u0131da bulunur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>Di\\u015f sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n korunmas\\u0131nda etkin bir elementtir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>H\\u00fccre b\\u00f6l\\u00fcnmesinde \\u00f6nemli g\\u00f6revleri vard\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>Kas fonksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n, enerji olu\\u015fum mekanizmalar\\u0131n\\u0131n ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015fmesine katk\\u0131da bulunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>H\\u00fccreleri al\\u00fcminyum, nikel, kadmiyum, c\\u0131va, kur\\u015fun gibi zararl\\u0131 elementlerden korur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre;\\\"> <\\/span>V\\u00fccutta kalsiyum ve potasyumun i\\u015flevini art\\u0131r\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Magnezyum Eksikli\\u011fi \",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde besinlerin i\\u015flenmesi esnas\\u0131nda i\\u00e7eri\\u011findeki magnezyumun azalmas\\u0131 durumu s\\u00f6z konusudur. Ya da uzun s\\u00fcre pi\\u015firilen sebzelerde magnezyum oran\\u0131 olduk\\u00e7a az seyretmektedir. Hem ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131m\\u0131z besinlerde yer alan magnezyum oranlar\\u0131n\\u0131n azalmas\\u0131 hem de beslenme al\\u0131\\u015fkanl\\u0131klar\\u0131m\\u0131z\\u0131n farkl\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131yla magnezyum eksikli\\u011fi kavram\\u0131 olduk\\u00e7a reva\\u00e7tad\\u0131r.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum eksikli\\u011fine<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;t\\u0131p dilinde hipomagnezemi ad\\u0131 verilmektedir. Fazla terleyen ya da baz\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 kullanan ki\\u015filerde magnezyum at\\u0131l\\u0131m\\u0131 daha fazlad\\u0131r. Stres ve hamilelik gibi durumlarda v\\u00fccudun ihtiya\\u00e7 duydu\\u011fu magnezyum miktar\\u0131 art\\u0131\\u015f g\\u00f6stermektedir. Ya\\u015f ilerledik\\u00e7e ya da gastrointestinal hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndan \\u00f6t\\u00fcr\\u00fc ba\\u011f\\u0131rsaklardaki emilimin azalmas\\u0131yla, gerek duyulan magnezyum miktar\\u0131 artar. Ve v\\u00fccut gerek duydu\\u011fu magnezyumu yeterli miktarda d\\u0131\\u015far\\u0131dan temin edemezse, kemiklerde depolanan magnezyumu t\\u00fcketmeye ba\\u015flar.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum eksikli\\u011fe<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;neden olan fakt\\u00f6rler; tip 2 diyabet hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, uyu\\u015fturucu ba\\u011f\\u0131ml\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, sigara kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, b\\u00f6brek ve karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, yanl\\u0131\\u015f beslenme al\\u0131\\u015fkanl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, stresli bir ya\\u015fam s\\u00fcrmek, idrar s\\u00f6kt\\u00fcr\\u00fcc\\u00fc ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, antibiyotiklerin s\\u0131k ve d\\u00fczenli kullan\\u0131lmas\\u0131na ba\\u011fl\\u0131, yetersiz beslenme, a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 alkol t\\u00fcketimi,&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/colyak-hastaligi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00e7\\u00f6lyak hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">,&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/crohn-ve-kolit\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Crohn hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, ya\\u015fl\\u0131l\\u0131kt\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum eksikli\\u011fi belirtileri&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">aras\\u0131nda;&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">i\\u015ftahs\\u0131zl\\u0131k, bulant\\u0131, kusma, sa\\u00e7 d\\u00f6k\\u00fclmesi, kab\\u0131zl\\u0131k, yorgunluk&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ve&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">halsizlik<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;say\\u0131labilir. Daha \\u015fiddetli vakalarda ise;&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kas kramplar\\u0131, kardiyak aritmiler, uyu\\u015fma, konsantrasyon eksikli\\u011fi, zihinsel bulan\\u0131kl\\u0131k, fibromiyalji<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Magnezyum eksikli\\u011fi tedavisinde<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, magnezyum ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 ve magnezyum i\\u00e7eren multivitaminler vard\\u0131r. Eksikli\\u011fin \\u00e7ok y\\u00fcksek d\\u00fczeylerde oldu\\u011fu durumlarda damar yoluyla magnezyum verilebilir. Do\\u011fal olarak y\\u00fcksek oranda magnezyum i\\u00e7eren besinleri t\\u00fcketmek, sigara ve alkol\\u00fc b\\u0131rakmak da tedavi plan\\u0131n\\u0131n i\\u00e7erisinde yer alabilir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Hipomagnezeminin (Magnezyum Eksikli\\u011fi) Yol A\\u00e7t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 Sa\\u011fl\\u0131k Sorunlar\\u0131\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; white-space: pre