(622, 622, 89, 79, 1, 'Narkolepsi', 16, 'narkolepsi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Narkolepsi\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ya da halk aras\\u0131nda bilinen ad\\u0131yla&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">uyku hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">normal d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 zamanlarda uyku hali ve ani uyku ataklar\\u0131 ile tan\\u0131mlanan&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kronik bir uyku bozuklu\\u011fudur.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi ma\\u011fduru olan bireyler, i\\u00e7inde bulunduklar\\u0131 \\u00e7evresel \\u015fartlara uzun s\\u00fcreli uyan\\u0131k kalmakta g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fck \\u00e7ekerler ve g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck hayatta b\\u00fcy\\u00fck zorluklar ile kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015fabilirler.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi genel olarak iki tip olarak tan\\u0131mlanmaktad\\u0131r. Baz\\u0131 vakalarda narkolepsinin yan\\u0131nda yani g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fc duygular sonucunda tetiklenebilen ani bir kas tonusu kayb\\u0131 olan&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">katapleksi<\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmesi m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr. Katapleksi ile ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan narkolepsi t\\u00fcr\\u00fcne&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">tip 1 narkolepsi&nbsp;<\\/span>ad\\u0131 verilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Katapleksi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmeden ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan narkolepsi t\\u00fcr\\u00fc ise&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">tip 2 narkolepsi&nbsp;<\\/span>olarak bilinir. Narkolepsi tipik olarak bireylerde ilk defa 10 ila 30 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131nda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcr.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Narkolepsi Neden Olur?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsinin nedeni&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">t\\u0131p uzmanlar\\u0131 taraf\\u0131ndan kesin olarak bilinmemektedir. Bununla birlikte&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Tip 1 narkolepsisi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">olan bireylerin hipokretinin seviyelerinin d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6zlemlenmi\\u015ftir. Hipokretin, bireyin beyninde uyan\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve REM uykusunu d\\u00fczenlemeye yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olan \\u00f6nemli bir n\\u00f6rokimyasald\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00d6zellikle katapleksi ya\\u015fayan bireylerde hipokretin seviyesi d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fckt\\u00fcr. Beyindeki hipokretin \\u00fcreten h\\u00fccrelerin neden kayboldu\\u011fu kesin olarak bilinmemekle birlikte, bir\\u00e7ok t\\u0131p uzman\\u0131 bunun ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sisteminin bir tepkisinden dolay\\u0131 kaynakland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndan \\u015f\\u00fcphelenmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kal\\u0131t\\u0131msal fakt\\u00f6rler de narkolepsinin geli\\u015fiminde rol oynamaktad\\u0131r. Ancak bir ebeveynin bu bozuklu\\u011fu \\u00e7ocu\\u011funa ge\\u00e7irmesi riskinin sadece yakla\\u015f\\u0131k y\\u00fczde 1 civar\\u0131nda oldu\\u011fu g\\u00f6zlemlenmektedir. Aile \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc. Ancak bir bireyin ailesinde narkolepsi varsa, o bireyin narkolepsi geli\\u015ftirmesi riski 20 ila 40 kat daha y\\u00fcksektir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Narkolepsi Belirtileri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;birden fazla belirtisi vard\\u0131r. Bu belirti ve semptomlar durumun ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kmas\\u0131ndan sonraki ilk birka\\u00e7 y\\u0131l i\\u00e7erisinde daha da a\\u011f\\u0131rla\\u015fabilir ve daha sonra \\u00f6m\\u00fcr boyu bireyi etkilemeye devam edebilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Birey ayn\\u0131 zamanda g\\u00fcn boyunca odaklanma ve uykulu olma sorunlar\\u0131 ya\\u015fayabilir. G\\u00fcnd\\u00fcz saatlerinde a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 uykulu olma hali narkolepsinin genellikle ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan ilk semptom. Bireyin konsantre olmas\\u0131n\\u0131 ve tam olarak \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 zorla\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131r.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;bir di\\u011fer belirtisi ise g\\u00fcnd\\u00fcz a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 uykuya dalma halidir. Narkolepsisi olan bireyler, herhangi bir yerde ve herhangi bir anda, aniden uykuya dalabilirler. Bu kontrol edebildikleri bir durum de\\u011fildir. Birey g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck hayat\\u0131n\\u0131 s\\u00fcrd\\u00fcr\\u00fcrken, \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131rken, veya yan\\u0131nda bulunan ba\\u015fkalar\\u0131 ile konu\\u015furken aniden birka\\u00e7 dakika ila bir ka\\u00e7 saatlik bir uykuya dalabilir. Bu s\\u00fcrenin sonunda uyand\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda uykusunu alm\\u0131\\u015f gibi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnebilir, ama k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcre i\\u00e7erisinde yine uyku ata\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kalabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Katapleksi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, yani ani kas tonusu kayb\\u0131, narkolepsinin bir ba\\u015fka belirtisidir. Bu durum bireyin konu\\u015fmas\\u0131nda bozukluktan, v\\u00fccudundaki bir \\u00e7ok kas\\u0131n tamamen zay\\u0131flamas\\u0131na kadar bir dizi fiziksel de\\u011fi\\u015fikli\\u011fe neden olabilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Katapleksi genellikle kahkaha veya heyecan gibi olumlu, ancak bazen korku, \\u015fa\\u015f\\u0131rma veya \\u00f6fke gibi yo\\u011fun duygular taraf\\u0131ndan tetiklenir ve birey taraf\\u0131ndan kontrol edilemez. Mesela birey g\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde, boyun kaslar\\u0131n\\u0131n tonusunu kaybetmesi nedeniyle kafas\\u0131 aniden kontrols\\u00fcz bir \\u015fekilde bir \\u015fekilde sarkabilir veya bacak kaslar\\u0131n\\u0131n tonusunu yitirmesi nedeniyle dizleri aniden b\\u00fck\\u00fclebilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsinin<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;g\\u00f6r\\u00fclme s\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 vakadan vakaya de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterir. Baz\\u0131 bireyler y\\u0131lda sadece bir veya iki katalepsi ata\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kal\\u0131rkenn, di\\u011ferleri her g\\u00fcn \\u00e7ok say\\u0131da atak ge\\u00e7irebilir. Narkolepsisi olan vakada katapleksi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmez.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uyku felci&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">narkolepsinin bir ba\\u015fka belirtisidir. Narkolepsisi olan bireyler genellikle uykuya dald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda veya uyand\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda ge\\u00e7ici olarak hareket edemez veya konu\\u015famazlar. Bu durum bir \\u00e7ok vakada sadece birka\\u00e7 saniye veya dakika s\\u00fcrer. Birey kendi \\u00fczerinde hi\\u00e7bir kontrol\\u00fc olmasa bile bu fel\\u00e7 durumunun fark\\u0131nda olabilir ve sonradan olay\\u0131 hat\\u0131rlamakta zorluk \\u00e7ekmeyebilir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uyku felci, REM uykusu s\\u00fcrecinde meydana gelen ge\\u00e7ici fel\\u00e7 tipini taklit eder. REM uykusu s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan bu ge\\u00e7ici hareketsizlik durumu normal \\u015fartlar alt\\u0131nda v\\u00fccudun g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen r\\u00fcyadaki hareketleri yapmas\\u0131n\\u0131 engeller. Ancak, uyku felci olan her bireyin narkolepsisi yoktur. Narkolepsisi olmayan bireyler de uyku felci ataklar\\u0131 ge\\u00e7irebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">REM uykusunda meydana gelen de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikler narkolepsinin bir di\\u011fer semptomudur. REM uykusu tipik olarak en \\u00e7ok r\\u00fcya g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc zamand\\u0131r. Narkolepsisi olan bireylerde REM uykusu g\\u00fcn\\u00fcn herhangi bir saatinde ba\\u015flayabilir.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Narkolepsisi&nbsp;<\\/span>olan bireyler genellikle uykuya dald\\u0131ktan 15 dakika sonra, yani \\u00e7ok h\\u0131zl\\u0131 bir \\u015fekilde REM uykusuna ge\\u00e7er.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi bireyin hal\\u00fcsinasyon g\\u00f6rmesine neden olabilir. Bu hal\\u00fcsinasyonlar, birey uykuya dald\\u0131ktan sonra meydana gelirse hipnagojik hal\\u00fcsinasyonlar olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131l\\u0131r. Uyand\\u0131ktan sonra ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan hal\\u00fcsinasyonlar ise hipnopompik hal\\u00fcsinasyonlar olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131l\\u0131r. Bu hal\\u00fcsinasyonlar birey i\\u00e7in olduk\\u00e7a canl\\u0131 ve korkutucu olabilir, \\u00e7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc birey r\\u00fcya g\\u00f6rmeye ba\\u015flad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131zda tam olarak uykuya dalmam\\u0131\\u015f olabilir ve bu nedenler r\\u00fcyalar\\u0131n\\u0131 ger\\u00e7ekmi\\u015f gibi hissedebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsisi olan bireyler daha nadir vakalarda, obstr\\u00fcktif uyku apnesi yani nefes alman\\u0131n gece boyunca ba\\u015flay\\u0131p durmas\\u0131, huzursuz bacak sendromu ve hatta insomnia, yani uykusuzluk hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 gibi di\\u011fer uyku bozukluklar\\u0131na sahip olabilirler.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsisi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;olan bireyler baz\\u0131 vakalarda, \\u00f6zellikle k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcreli narkolepsi ataklar\\u0131 s\\u00fcrecinde belirli davran\\u0131\\u015flar\\u0131 otomatik olarak tekrarlamaya ba\\u015flayabilirler. \\u00d6rnek olarak, yaz\\u0131 yazarken uyuya kalan bir birey yaz\\u0131 yazmaya, ya da ara\\u00e7 kullan\\u0131rken narkolepsi ata\\u011f\\u0131na maruz kalan bir birey ara\\u00e7 kullanmaya, ya da y\\u00fcr\\u00fcyen bir birey y\\u00fcr\\u00fcmeye devam edebilir. Birey uyand\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda ne yapt\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 hat\\u0131rlamayacakt\\u0131r ve yapt\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 aktivite de muhtemelen iyi sonu\\u00e7 vermeyecektir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bireyler \\u00f6zellikle g\\u00fcnd\\u00fczleri ki\\u015fisel veya i\\u015f hayatlar\\u0131n\\u0131 bozacak seviyede a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 uyku hali ya da uyuklama hali ya\\u015f\\u0131yorsa, doktora ba\\u015fvurmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Narkolepsi Nas\\u0131l Te\\u015fhis Edilir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Doktorlar normal \\u015fartlar alt\\u0131nda bireyin g\\u00fcnd\\u00fcz vakti a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 uykulu olmas\\u0131na veya varsa ani kas tonusu kayb\\u0131na yani katapleksi durumuna ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">narkolepsi \\u00f6n tan\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131<\\/span>&nbsp;koyabilirler. Doktor, bu \\u00f6n tan\\u0131dan sonra daha iyi ve kesin bir de\\u011ferlendirme i\\u00e7in bireyi bir uyku uzman\\u0131na y\\u00f6nlendirecektir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsinin kesin tan\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131n<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;konulmas\\u0131 ise&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/acibadem-de\\/uyku-bozukluklari-tedavisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">uyku uzmanlar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;taraf\\u0131ndan derinlemesine bir uyku analizi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmesi i\\u00e7in bir uyku merkezinde bir gece kalmay\\u0131 gerektirir. Bu narkolepsi testi sayesinde varsa narkolepsi te\\u015fhisi konulabilir ve \\u015fiddeti belirlenebilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu s\\u00fcre\\u00e7te doktor \\u00f6ncelikle bireyden uyku ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fini ayr\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 bir \\u015fekilde \\u00f6\\u011frenmek isteyecektir. Bunun i\\u00e7in bir ka\\u00e7 k\\u0131sa sorudan meydana gelen<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;Epworth Uykululuk&nbsp;<\\/span>\\u00d6l\\u00e7e\\u011fi doldurulacakt\\u0131r. Bu \\u00f6l\\u00e7ekteki sorular aras\\u0131nda bireyin \\u00f6rne\\u011fin \\u00f6\\u011fle yeme\\u011finden sonras\\u0131 gibi belirli durumlarda uyuma oran\\u0131 ve s\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n ne kadar oldu\\u011fu bulunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunun yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra doktor bireyden bir veya iki hafta boyunca uyku d\\u00fczeninin ayr\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 bir program\\u0131n\\u0131 tutmas\\u0131n\\u0131 isteyebilir, ve bu sayede aradaki&nbsp; ili\\u015fkiyi belirlemek \\u00fczere uyku d\\u00fczeni ile uyan\\u0131kl\\u0131k d\\u00f6nemini kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015ft\\u0131rabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Buna ek olarak doktor bireyden bir aktigraf kullanmas\\u0131n\\u0131 isteyebilir. Bir kol saatine benzeyen bu cihaz, hem bireyin hareket etme ve dinlenme d\\u00f6nemlerini \\u00f6l\\u00e7er hem de ne zaman ve nas\\u0131l&nbsp; uyudu\\u011funu dolayl\\u0131 olarak \\u00f6l\\u00e7er.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uyku merkezinde polisomnografi testi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilebilir. Polisomnografi testi, bireyin kafa derisine yerle\\u015ftirilen elektrotlar arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sinyalleri uyku s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda \\u00f6l\\u00e7er. Bu test, bireyin elektroensefalogram yani beynin elektriksel aktivite de\\u011ferlerini, elektrokardiyogram yani kalbin elektriksel aktivite de\\u011ferlerini, elektromiyogram yani kaslar\\u0131n elektriksel aktivite de\\u011ferlerini ve elektrook\\u00fclogram yani g\\u00f6zlerin hareket de\\u011ferlerini \\u00f6l\\u00e7er. Bireyin solunum de\\u011ferleri de \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcl\\u00fcr.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi te\\u015fhisinde kullan\\u0131lan bir ba\\u015fka test olan \\u00e7oklu uyku gecikme testi ise, bireyin g\\u00fcn boyunca uykuya dalmas\\u0131n\\u0131n ne kadar s\\u00fcrd\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcn\\u00fc \\u00f6l\\u00e7er. Bireyin her biri iki saat arayla d\\u00f6rt veya be\\u015f defa \\u015fekerleme yapmas\\u0131 istenir. Uzmanlar bu s\\u00fcre\\u00e7te bireyin uyku d\\u00fczenini g\\u00f6zlemler. Narkolepsisi olan bireyler uykuya kolayl\\u0131kla dalar ve do\\u011frudan REM uykusuna&nbsp; girerler.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu testler sayesinde bireyin belirti ve semptomlar\\u0131n\\u0131n kronik uyku yoksunlu\\u011fu, yat\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131c\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 ve&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/uyku-apnesi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">uyku apnesi<\\/span><\\/a>&nbsp;gibi g\\u00fcnd\\u00fcz a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 uykuya neden olabilen di\\u011fer olas\\u0131 nedenlerini d\\u0131\\u015flamas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Narkolepsi Nas\\u0131l Tedavi Edilir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ne yaz\\u0131k ki kal\\u0131c\\u0131 tedavisi olmayan, kronik bir durumdur. Bununla birlikte, \\u00e7e\\u015fitli t\\u0131bbi ila\\u00e7lar ile ya\\u015fam tarz\\u0131 de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikleri bireyin semptomlar\\u0131 y\\u00f6netmesine yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir. Ayn\\u0131 zamanda bireyin \\u00e7evresindeki yak\\u0131nlar\\u0131ndan alaca\\u011f\\u0131 destek&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">narkolepsi ile ba\\u015fa \\u00e7\\u0131kmas\\u0131na<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi y\\u00f6netimi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;s\\u00fcrecinde kullan\\u0131labilecek \\u00e7e\\u015fitli ila\\u00e7 t\\u00fcrleri vard\\u0131r. Bu ila\\u00e7lar her zaman bir doktor tavsiyesi ve re\\u00e7etesi ile birlikte, bir t\\u0131p uzman\\u0131n\\u0131n g\\u00f6zetimi alt\\u0131nda kullan\\u0131lmal\\u0131d\\u0131r. \\u00d6zellikle y\\u00fcksek tansiyon veya diyabet gibi ba\\u015fka sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131 olan bireyler doktorlar\\u0131na bu durumlar\\u0131 ifade etmeli ve di\\u011fer durumlar i\\u00e7in ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n narkolepsi i\\u00e7in al\\u0131nan ila\\u00e7larla nas\\u0131l etkile\\u015fime girebilece\\u011fini sormal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bununla birlikte alerji ve so\\u011fuk alg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 gibi re\\u00e7etesiz sat\\u0131lan baz\\u0131 ila\\u00e7lar metabolizmada uyu\\u015fuklu\\u011fa neden olabilir. Doktorlar&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">narkolepsisi olan bireylerin<\\/span>&nbsp;bu ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 almaktan ka\\u00e7\\u0131nmas\\u0131n\\u0131 yayg\\u0131n olarak \\u00f6nerebilirler.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Narkolepsi tedavisi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;i\\u00e7in ara\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131lan yeni y\\u00f6ntemler aras\\u0131nda histamin kimyasal sistemine etki eden ila\\u00e7lar,&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">hipokretin replasman\\u0131, hipokretin gen tedavisi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ve&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">imm\\u00fcnoterapi&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">mevcuttur. Ancak bu y\\u00f6ntemler aras\\u0131nda kesin etkili olan bir tane hen\\u00fcz belirlenmemi\\u015ftir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Uyar\\u0131c\\u0131lar, yani&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">narkolepsisi&nbsp;<\\/span>olan bireylerin g\\u00fcn boyunca uyan\\u0131k kalmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olmak i\\u00e7in merkezi sinir sistemini uyaran ila\\u00e7lar, \\u00f6ncelikli olarak kullan\\u0131lan tedavi y\\u00f6ntemidir. Bu t\\u00fcr ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n yan etkileri aras\\u0131nda<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/bas-agrisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\">ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/mide-bulantisi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\">bulant\\u0131<\\/a><\\/span>&nbsp;veya&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.acibadem.com.tr\\/ilgi-alani\\/anksiyete\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(9, 44, 116);\\\">anksiyete<\\/a><\\/span>&nbsp;g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"N\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:37:05', '2023-12-20 16:38:47'),
