(626, 626, 89, 79, 1, 'Obsesif Kompulsif Bozukluk (OKB)', 17, 'obsesif-kompulsif-bozukluk', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Obsesif Kompulsif Bozukluk (OKB)\",\"content_1\":\"<p><section class=\\\"part hashContent detailedContent nedenleri\\\" id=\\\"nedenleri\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/section><\\/p><section class=\\\"part hashContent detailedContent general\\\" id=\\\"general\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><strong style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB)<\\/strong>, insanlar\\u0131n obsesyon ad\\u0131 verilen s\\u00fcrekli tekrar eden d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncelere sahip olmas\\u0131 ve bu d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncenin kendisini rahats\\u0131z etmesinden \\u00f6t\\u00fcr\\u00fc, genellikle rahatlamak amac\\u0131yla rit\\u00fcel veya kompulsiyon ad\\u0131 verilen s\\u00fcrekli tekrar eden davran\\u0131\\u015flarda bulunmas\\u0131yla karakterize bir durumdur.<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fa (OKB) sahip hastalar, kontrol edemedikleri d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceleri, korkular\\u0131 veya imgeleri saplant\\u0131 halinde ya\\u015farlar. Bu durum hem kendileri hem de \\u00e7evresindekiler i\\u00e7in son derece rahats\\u0131z edici olabilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\">Bu d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncelerin \\u00fcretti\\u011fi kayg\\u0131, gerginlik, kendini tekrarlayan davran\\u0131\\u015flar\\u0131, rit\\u00fceller veya rutinlerin zorunlu hale gelmesine neden olur.<span>&nbsp;<\\/span><strong style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) hastalar\\u0131<span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/strong>t\\u00fcm bu zorunluluklar\\u0131, tak\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceleri \\u00f6nlemek veya ortadan kald\\u0131rmay\\u0131 sa\\u011flamak amac\\u0131yla t\\u00fcm bunlar\\u0131 bir rutin haline getirir.<\\/p><strong style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) hastalar\\u0131<\\/strong><span>&nbsp;<\\/span>tak\\u0131nt\\u0131lar\\u0131n\\u0131 g\\u00f6rmezden gelmeye ya da durdurmaya \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fsa da bu durumu engelleyemeyece\\u011fi gibi endi\\u015felerini de art\\u0131r\\u0131r. Ki\\u015fi, stresini hafifletmek i\\u00e7in zorlay\\u0131c\\u0131 eylemlerde bulunmaya ba\\u015flad\\u0131k\\u00e7a kendin zorlar. Tak\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceler veya d\\u00fcrt\\u00fclerden kurtulmaya \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fsalar da bu durum bazen daha k\\u00f6t\\u00fc sonu\\u00e7lara neden olabilir.<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\"><\\/p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px;\\\"><\\/div><\\/section>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Obsesif Kompulsif Bozuklu\\u011fun Nedenleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fun (OKB) nedeni&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">tam olarak anla\\u015f\\u0131lmamas\\u0131na ra\\u011fmen, biyolojik ve \\u00e7evresel fakt\\u00f6rlerin etkili oldu\\u011fu d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcn\\u00fclmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Biyolojik fakt\\u00f6rler<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">V\\u00fccudun normal i\\u015fleyi\\u015finde devam edebilmesi i\\u00e7in beyindeki milyarlarca n\\u00f6ronun (sinir h\\u00fccresinin) birbirleriyle ileti\\u015fim kurmas\\u0131 gereklidir ve n\\u00f6ronlar elektriksel sinyallerle haberle\\u015fir. N\\u00f6rotransmiterler ad\\u0131 verilen \\u00f6zel kimyasallar, bu elektriksel mesajlar\\u0131n n\\u00f6rondan n\\u00f6ronlara ta\\u015f\\u0131nmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">durumunda, beynin belirli b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 aktivite bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Hasta obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) semptomlar\\u0131n\\u0131 ya\\u015fad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda ise beyin daha da aktif hale gelir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7evresel Fakt\\u00f6rler<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fu (OKB)&nbsp; olan baz\\u0131 ki\\u015filer ise \\u00e7evresel stres fakt\\u00f6rlerinden etkilenmektedir. Ki\\u015finin ya\\u015fad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 baz\\u0131 \\u00e7evresel fakt\\u00f6rler ve ciddi hayat de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikleri semptomlar\\u0131n k\\u00f6t\\u00fcle\\u015fmesine neden olabilir. Bu fakt\\u00f6rler \\u015funlar\\u0131 i\\u00e7erir:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Taciz<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Ya\\u015fam durumundaki de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikler<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Hastal\\u0131k<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Sevilen birinin kayb\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">\\u0130\\u015f veya okulla ilgili de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikler veya sorunlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">\\u0130li\\u015fki kayg\\u0131lar\\u0131<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Obsesif Kompulsif Bozuklu\\u011fun Belirtileri\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk, genellikle hem saplant\\u0131 hem de ki\\u015finin kendini zorlamas\\u0131n\\u0131 i\\u00e7erir. Ancak, sadece obsesyon semptomlar\\u0131 olmas\\u0131 da m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcnd\\u00fcr.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk hastalar\\u0131nda<\\/span>&nbsp;tak\\u0131nt\\u0131lar\\u0131n ve zorlamalar\\u0131n a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 oldu\\u011fu kolayl\\u0131kla fark edebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk hastalar\\u0131 tak\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceleri oldu\\u011funda endi\\u015felerini kontrol etmeye yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olacak kurallar veya rit\\u00fceller olu\\u015fturabilir. Fakat kontrol etme \\u00e7abalar\\u0131 genellikle d\\u00fczeltmeyi ama\\u00e7lad\\u0131klar\\u0131 sorunla ger\\u00e7ek\\u00e7i bir \\u015fekilde ili\\u015fkili de\\u011fildir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">kendini tekrarlayan bir hastal\\u0131k t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk istenmeyen d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceler, s\\u00fcrekli m\\u00fcdahil olma, s\\u0131k\\u0131nt\\u0131 veya endi\\u015fe veren d\\u00fcrt\\u00fclerdir. Bu hastal\\u0131\\u011fa sahip ki\\u015filer kendilerini zorlayarak t\\u00fcm d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncelerini g\\u00f6rmezden gelmeye veya onlardan kurtulmaya \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fabilir. Fakat hasta bu tip saplant\\u0131lardan kurtulmaya \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131rken daha da zorlanabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk genellikle gen\\u00e7lik veya erken yeti\\u015fkinlik y\\u0131llar\\u0131nda ba\\u015flar. Semptomlar yava\\u015f yava\\u015f ba\\u015flayarak t\\u00fcm ya\\u015fam boyunca de\\u011fi\\u015fim g\\u00f6sterebilir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk belirtileri&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">ki\\u015finin \\u00e7ok fazla stres alt\\u0131nda kald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda daha da k\\u00f6t\\u00fcle\\u015fir. Genellikle ya\\u015fam boyu s\\u00fcren bir hastal\\u0131k olarak kabul edilen obsesif kompulsif bozukluk hafif ila orta \\u015fiddette semptomlara sahip olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kirlenme korkusu<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">D\\u00fczenli ve simetrik olma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kendisini veya sevdiklerinin zarar g\\u00f6rmesine ait d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcncelere kap\\u0131lma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Ba\\u015fkalar\\u0131n\\u0131n dokundu\\u011fu nesnelere dokunamamak<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Nesneler d\\u00fczenli olmad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda strese girme<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">El s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fmaktan rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131k duyma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">S\\u00fcrekli el y\\u0131kama&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">A\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 temizlik tak\\u0131nt\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Mikroplardan korkma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">S\\u00fcrekli du\\u015f alma iste\\u011fi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">S\\u00fcrekli bir \\u015feyleri kontrol etme ihtiyac\\u0131 duyma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Bir \\u015feyleri sayma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kilitlendiklerinden emin olmak i\\u00e7in kap\\u0131lar\\u0131 tekrar tekrar kontrol etme<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kapal\\u0131 oldu\\u011fundan emin olmak i\\u00e7in oca\\u011f\\u0131 tekrar tekrar kontrol etme<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Belirli kal\\u0131plarda sayma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Bir duay\\u0131, kelimeyi veya ifadeyi i\\u00e7ten i\\u00e7e tekrarlamak<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Tan\\u0131 Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">i\\u00e7in laboratuvar ortam\\u0131nda ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilebilen bir test yoktur. Te\\u015fhis, hastan\\u0131n semptomlar\\u0131 ve hastan\\u0131n genel davran\\u0131\\u015flar\\u0131 \\u00fczerine uzman bir doktor taraf\\u0131ndan konulabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Psikiyatrist taraf\\u0131ndan ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilen psikolojik de\\u011ferlendirme esnas\\u0131nda d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceler, duygular, semptomlar ve davran\\u0131\\u015f kal\\u0131plar\\u0131 incelenir.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fu (OKB) te\\u015fhis&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">etmek bazen zordur, \\u00e7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc semptomlar obsesif-kompulsif ki\\u015filik bozuklu\\u011fu, anksiyete bozukluklar\\u0131, depresyon, \\u015fizofreni veya di\\u011fer mental sa\\u011fl\\u0131k bozukluklar\\u0131na benzer olabilir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ki\\u015filer hem obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fa (OKB), hem de di\\u011fer mental bozukluklara sahip olabilir. Bu sebeple hastay\\u0131 de\\u011ferlendirecek olan psikiyatr\\u0131n t\\u00fcm etkenleri d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnmesi gereklidir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Tedavi Y\\u00f6ntemleri\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) tedavi<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;edilmedi\\u011fi takdirde kendili\\u011finden iyile\\u015fmeyebilir, bu nedenle tedavi almak son derece \\u00f6nemlidir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ki\\u015fi, zihinsel hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n te\\u015fhisi ve tedavisi i\\u00e7in \\u00f6zel olarak e\\u011fitilmi\\u015f bir sa\\u011fl\\u0131k uzman\\u0131na y\\u00f6nlendirilebilir.<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">&nbsp;Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk&nbsp; (OKB) tedavisinde<\\/span>&nbsp;en etkili yakla\\u015f\\u0131m, ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131 uygun terapiler ile birle\\u015ftirmektedir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Davran\\u0131\\u015f Terapisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) hastalar\\u0131nda s\\u0131kl\\u0131kla g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen abart\\u0131l\\u0131 veya tak\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnceleri azaltmaya odakl\\u0131 bir tedavi y\\u00f6ntemidir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ama\\u00e7, Obsesif kompulsif bozuklu\\u011fu (OKB) olan ki\\u015filere, zorlay\\u0131c\\u0131 davran\\u0131\\u015flarda bulunmadan kayg\\u0131 yaratan inan\\u00e7lar\\u0131yla y\\u00fczle\\u015fmeleri konusunda yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olmakt\\u0131r.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u0130la\\u00e7 Tedavisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Obsesif kompulsif bozukluk (OKB) hastalar\\u0131nda beyindeki serotonin seviyelerini art\\u0131rmaya y\\u00f6nelik ila\\u00e7lar kullan\\u0131labilir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"O\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 16:41:14', '2023-12-20 16:43:57'),
