(630, 630, 86, 79, 1, 'Anesteziyoloji ve Reanimasyon', 1, 'anesteziyoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Anesteziyoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Anesteziyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri, t\\u00fcm hastanelerimizde ve cerrahi t\\u0131p merkezlerimizde hasta bak\\u0131m ve tedavi hizmeti d\\u00e2hilinde bir\\u00e7ok cerrahi giri\\u015fim \\u00f6ncesi hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Verilen hizmet giri\\u015fim \\u00f6ncesi t\\u0131bbi de\\u011ferlendirme, giri\\u015fim esnas\\u0131nda ve sonras\\u0131nda a\\u011fr\\u0131 tedavisi ile ya\\u015famsal sorunlarla ba\\u015f etmeyi i\\u00e7erir. Cerrahi, tan\\u0131sal veya tedavi edici giri\\u015fimlerde analjezi, g\\u00fcn\\u00fcbirlik cerrahi, a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131z do\\u011fum, beyin ve omurilik cerrahisi anestezileri b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn kapsam\\u0131 d\\u00e2hilindedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Anesteziyoloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/div><div class=\\\"author\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; font-style: italic; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/div><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\">Kalp cerrahisi, Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi, \\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi, Kad\\u0131n ve Do\\u011fum, Jinekoloji, Ortopedi, G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs Cerrahisi, Damar Cerrahisi, Kulak Burun Bo\\u011faz, \\u00dcroloji ve G\\u00f6z b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde anestezi uygulamalar\\u0131 yapmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"A\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:20:49', '2023-12-27 15:48:55'),
