(634, 634, 86, 79, 1, 'Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi', 2, 'beyin-ve-sinir-cerrahisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi (N\\u00f6ro\\u015firurji) b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri ba\\u015fta; beyin t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, beyin pili (derin beyin stimulasyonu), beyin biyopsisi, \\u00e7ocuk n\\u00f6ro\\u015firurjisi, spinal cerrahi ve y\\u00fcr\\u00fcme analizi konular\\u0131nda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti veriyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc; N\\u00f6roloji, N\\u00f6roradyoloji, N\\u00f6roanestezi ve Psikiyatri birimlerinden hekimlerle i\\u015fbirli\\u011fi i\\u00e7erisinde \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131yor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">PET\\/BT, CyberKnife ve Gamma Knife adl\\u0131 medikal teknoloji cihazlar\\u0131 beyin t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rlerinin tan\\u0131 ve tedavi s\\u00fcrecinde kullan\\u0131l\\u0131yor.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Disk Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve Dejeneratif Omurga Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Servikal, lomber ve torasik diskektomiler, vertebrektomi, laminektomi, omurga stabilizasyon (instrumentasyon) ameliyatlar\\u0131 bu birimin kapsam\\u0131ndad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"N\\u00f6roonkoloji\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Her \\u00e7e\\u015fit beyin ve omurilik t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rlerinin cerrahi tedavisi; meningiomalar, glial t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rler, serebellopontin k\\u00f6\\u015fe t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, hipofiz t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, beyin sap\\u0131, pineal b\\u00f6lge, posterior fossa t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, kafa kaidesi t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, ekstramed\\u00fcller veya intramed\\u00fcller spinal t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rler, kalvaryum lezyonlar\\u0131, kranioplasti ameliyatlar\\u0131, kraniofasiyal cerrahi, kraniosinostoz ve \\u015fekillendirme ameliyatlar\\u0131 bu birimin d\\u00e2hilindedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"N\\u00f6roendoskopi ve Hidrosefali Tedavisi\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu birimin kapsam\\u0131nda \\u015fant ameliyatlar\\u0131, n\\u00f6roendoskopik giri\\u015fimler, third ventriculostomy ve araknoid kistlerin fenestrayonu yer almaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Fonksiyonel N\\u00f6ro\\u015firurji\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hemifasiyal spazm ve trigeminal nevraljide mikrovask\\u00fclar dekompresyon, vagal sinir stimulat\\u00f6r\\u00fc yerle\\u015ftirilmesi ve sara hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgili birimdir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"B\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:24:43', '2023-12-27 15:50:14'),
