(638, 638, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Cerrahisi', 4, 'cocuk-cerrahisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri; bebeklik, \\u00e7ocukluk ve ilk gen\\u00e7lik d\\u00f6neminde, yani 0-16 ya\\u015f aras\\u0131nda rastlanan cerrahi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi i\\u00e7in hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde; \\u00e7ocuk hastalar\\u0131m\\u0131z i\\u00e7in tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetleri sunulurken cerrahi m\\u00fcdahale \\u00f6ncesi ve sonras\\u0131nda \\u00e7ocuk psikolojisinin \\u00f6nemi \\u00fczerinde de \\u00f6nemle durulmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"S\\u0131k Rastlanan \\u00c7ocuk Cerrahisi Hastal\\u0131klardan Baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 \\u015eu \\u015eekildedir\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Laparoskopik, torakoskopik, endoskopik, sistoskopik giri\\u015fimler<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7ocuklarda Apandisit ve Laparoskopik Tedavi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kas\\u0131k F\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, Hidrosel, Kordon Kisti<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u0130nmemi\\u015f Testis<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Testis ve Torbalar\\u0131n Acil Durumlar\\u0131 (Akut Skrotum ve Testis Torsiyonu vb.)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Testis d\\u00f6nmesi (Testis torsiyonu)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Testis ve Torbalarla \\u0130lgili Di\\u011fer Acil Durumlar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">G\\u00f6bek F\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">G\\u00f6bek Gran\\u00fclomu<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">E\\u011fri Boyun Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 (Tortikolis)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Labial Yap\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">An\\u00fcsten Kan Gelmesi Durumlar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak D\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcmlenmesi (\\u0130nvaginasyon)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Rektal Polip (Juvenil Polip)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">An\\u00fcste \\u00c7atlak (Anal Fiss\\u00fcr)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7ocuklarda Kab\\u0131zl\\u0131k ve D\\u0131\\u015fk\\u0131 Ka\\u00e7\\u0131rma Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Bebeklerin Mide \\u00c7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 T\\u0131kan\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 (\\u0130nfantil Pilor Stenozu)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">S\\u00fcnnet (Yenido\\u011fan ve \\u00c7ocukluk D\\u00f6neminde) ve \\u00c7ocuk \\u00dcrolojisi ile \\u0130lgili Hastal\\u0131klar (Hipospadias vb.)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">T\\u00fcm\\u00f6r Cerrahisi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hava ve Sindirim Yolundan Yabanc\\u0131 Cisimlerin \\u00c7\\u0131kart\\u0131lmas\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hirschsprung Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n Tek Evreli Tedavisi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Yenido\\u011fan\\u0131n Do\\u011fumsal Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (Diyafragma Hernisi, \\u00d6zofagus Atrezisi, Anal ve \\u0130ntestinal Atreziler\\u2026)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7ocuklar ve bebeklere gereken her durumda (k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck-b\\u00fcy\\u00fck t\\u00fcm ameliyatlar, s\\u00fcnnet, bilgisayarl\\u0131 tomografi ve manyetik rezonans gibi tetkikler s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda) genel anestezi verilebilmektedir.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:27:31', '2023-12-27 15:52:52'),
