(642, 642, 86, 79, 1, 'Deri ve Zührevi Hastalıkları (Cildiye)', 5, 'deri-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Deri ve Z\\u00fchrevi Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (Cildiye)\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Dermatoloji (Cildiye) b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri; deri, sa\\u00e7, t\\u0131rnak ve a\\u011f\\u0131z i\\u00e7i gibi mukoza hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi ile ilgilenmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Deri Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life hastane ve t\\u0131p merkezlerinde bulunan Dermotoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde; alerjik deri hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131,\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 terleme<\\/span><\\/font>,\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\\\">beh\\u00e7et hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/font>, cinsel yolla bula\\u015fan hastal\\u0131klar, deri enfeksiyonlar\\u0131, deri t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri, ila\\u00e7 reaksiyonlar\\u0131,\\u00a0<font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initia