(646, 646, 86, 79, 1, 'El Cerrahisi', 6, 'el-cerrahisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"El Cerrahisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life El Cerrahisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde el, el bile\\u011fi, dirsek ve kol ile ilgili sorunlar\\u0131 bulunan hastalar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavileri ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftiriliyor.<\\/p><div><br><\\/div>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"El Cerrahisi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El Cerrahisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde eri\\u015fkinlerde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen el ve kol b\\u00f6lgesindeki t\\u00fcm sorunlar\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 konularak, acil veya planl\\u0131 cerrahiler ya da cerrahi y\\u00f6ntemlerle tedavisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftiriliyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El ve kol b\\u00f6lgesinin t\\u00fcm k\\u0131r\\u0131klar\\u0131, \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve bunlara ba\\u011fl\\u0131 yanl\\u0131\\u015f kaynama, kaynamama ve eklem bozulmas\\u0131 gibi komplikasyonlara m\\u00fcdahale ediliyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El ve kol b\\u00f6lgesinde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rler, a\\u00e7\\u0131k yaralar damar, sinir, tendon yaralanmalar\\u0131 ve doku kay\\u0131plar\\u0131 da mikrocerrahi y\\u00f6ntemler kullan\\u0131larak tedavi ediliyor. G\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde giderek artan s\\u0131kl\\u0131kta kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan ve a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 kullan\\u0131ma ba\\u011fl\\u0131 g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen sinir s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fmalar\\u0131, tendinitler, eklem kire\\u00e7lenmeleri gibi sorunlara g\\u00fcn\\u00fcbirlik cerrahi i\\u015flemler uygulanabiliyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">El bile\\u011fi sorunlar\\u0131nda artroskopik cerrahi uygulanabiliyor. El ve kol b\\u00f6lgesinde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen fel\\u00e7lerde de kas transferleri ile tedavi yap\\u0131l\\u0131yor.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"E\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:32:20', '2023-12-27 16:10:40'),
