(650, 650, 86, 79, 1, 'Fizik Tıp ve Rehabilitasyon', 7, 'fizik-tedavi-ve-rehabilitasyon', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Fizik T\\u0131p ve Rehabilitasyon\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Fizik Tedavi ve Rehabilitasyon B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, medikal teknolojik cihazlarla, ki\\u015fiye odakl\\u0131 ve bilimsel verilerle \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fan ekip taraf\\u0131ndan hizmet sunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Fizik Tedavi ve Rehabilitasyonu Kimler Uygular?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fizik tedavi uzmanlar\\u0131n\\u0131n, hastan\\u0131n durumuna g\\u00f6re olu\\u015fturdu\\u011fu fizik tedavi program\\u0131, hekimin \\u00f6neri ve talimatlar\\u0131na uygun olarak, fizyoterapistler taraf\\u0131ndan ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Fizik Tedavi ve Rehabilitasyon Nedir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fizik tedavi ve rehabilitasyon, ki\\u015finin hareket ve fonksiyonel aktivitelerini k\\u0131s\\u0131tlayan, ya\\u015fam kalitesini azaltan kemik, eklem, kas ve sinir sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n \\/yaralanmalar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisini kapsayan uygulamalard\\u0131r. Bu sistemler, kendisine ait hastal\\u0131klarla do\\u011frudan etkilendi\\u011fi gibi dolayl\\u0131 olarak di\\u011fer sistem bozukluklar\\u0131nda da etkilenir. Her iki durumda da bu programlar uygulan\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Fizik Tedavi ve Rehabilitasyonun Ama\\u00e7lar\\u0131 Nedir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fizik tedavi ve rehabilitasyon gerektiren pek \\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tedavisinde; a\\u011fr\\u0131y\\u0131 azaltmak, fonksiyon kay\\u0131plar\\u0131n\\u0131 gidermek, ya\\u015fam kalitesini artt\\u0131rmak ve g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ya\\u015fam aktivitelerine d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fc sa\\u011flamak ama\\u00e7lanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Fizik Tedavi ve Rehabilitasyonun Uyguland\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 Alanlar\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hareket sistemi ve di\\u011fer sistemlerin yap\\u0131 ve fonksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131 bozan akut veya kronik t\\u00fcm hastal\\u0131klarda kullan\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bunlar a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131daki gibi s\\u0131ralanabilir:<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">1. Hareket Sistemi Bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h3><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Omurga Rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022Bel ve Boyun, Eklem ve Kas \\u0130ncinmelerine Ba\\u011fl\\u0131 A\\u011fr\\u0131lar<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Bel F\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Boyun F\\u0131t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022Duru\\u015f Bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Skolyoz<\\/span><\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Eklem Rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u2022\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Artroz (Kire\\u00e7lenme)<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;