(654, 654, 86, 79, 1, 'Hematoloji', 13, 'hematoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Hematoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hematoloji<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0kelime anlam\\u0131 olarak kan bilimini ifade eder. Hematoloji; kan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, kemik ili\\u011fi ile kan yap\\u0131c\\u0131 organlar\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla ilgilenen i\\u00e7 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Hematoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">lenfoma, l\\u00f6semiler ve di\\u011fer kanser hematolojisinde, kemik ili\\u011fi nakilleri, kans\\u0131zl\\u0131k, p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fma bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0tan\\u0131 ve tedavi alanlar\\u0131nda hizmet vermektedir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Hematoloji (Kan) Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kan h\\u00fccreleri kemik ili\\u011finde bulunan k\\u00f6k h\\u00fccreler taraf\\u0131ndan \\u00fcretilir. Yap\\u0131s\\u0131nda bulunan 3 temel h\\u00fccre \\u00e7e\\u015fidiyle kan; organlar aras\\u0131nda oksijenin ta\\u015f\\u0131nmas\\u0131, enfeksiyonlara kar\\u015f\\u0131 m\\u00fccadele, v\\u00fccuttaki doku ve organlar aras\\u0131ndaki ileti\\u015fim gibi bir\\u00e7ok \\u015feyden sorumludur. Kan h\\u00fccreleri kemik ili\\u011finde bulunan k\\u00f6k h\\u00fccreler taraf\\u0131ndan \\u00fcretilir.\\u00a0<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hematoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn ilgilendi\\u011fi kanda 3 temel h\\u00fccre \\u00e7e\\u015fidi bulunur. Bunlar; kanda oksijenin ta\\u015f\\u0131nmas\\u0131ndan sorumlu\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">alyuvar h\\u00fccreleri<\\/span>, enfeksiyonlarla m\\u00fccadele elen<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00a0akyuvar h\\u00fccreleri<\\/span>\\u00a0ve kanama halinde kan\\u0131n p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flayan\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">trombosit h\\u00fccreleri<\\/span>dir. Bu h\\u00fccrelerin miktar\\u0131ndaki ve yap\\u0131s\\u0131ndaki de\\u011fi\\u015fimler; kan tahlilleri ile izlenebilir. Bu h\\u00fccrelerin yap\\u0131s\\u0131ndaki ve say\\u0131s\\u0131ndaki de\\u011fi\\u015fiklikler yayg\\u0131n kan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n ve di\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n sonucu ya da semptomu olarak g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir.<\\/div>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Anemi\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Anemi<\\/span>, g\\u00fcndelik konu\\u015fma dilinde\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kans\\u0131zl\\u0131k<\\/span>\\u00a0olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131l\\u0131r. Kal\\u0131tsal dolay\\u0131s\\u0131yla da do\\u011fumsal olan anemiler vard\\u0131r. Kal\\u0131tsal olmayan anemilerin en \\u00f6nemli nedenleri; demir eksikli\\u011fi, B12 vitamini eksikli\\u011fi ve folik asit eksikli\\u011fidir. Kal\\u0131tsal ya da \\u00e7evresel nedenlerle ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan anemi t\\u00fcrleri;\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">orak h\\u00fccreli anemi, aplastik anemi, hemolitik anemi, pernisiy\\u00f6z anemi, megaloblastik anemidir.<\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Anemiler beslenmedeki eksiklere ek olarak kanamalar sonucunda da ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilirler. Aneminin yayg\\u0131n belirtileri aras\\u0131nda; halsizlik, ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi, renkte solgunluk, \\u00e7arp\\u0131nt\\u0131, zihinde bulan\\u0131kl\\u0131k ya da unutkanl\\u0131k, erken yorulma, \\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcme, sa\\u00e7 d\\u00f6k\\u00fclmesi bulunur.\\u00a0<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Anemi tedavisi nedenine ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak yap\\u0131l\\u0131r. Anemiye yol a\\u00e7an sebep ortadan kald\\u0131r\\u0131ld\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda aneminin ge\\u00e7mesi beklenir. Demir, B12, folik asit eksikli\\u011finden kaynaklan\\u0131yorsa hekim taraf\\u0131ndan beslenme program\\u0131 ya da ila\\u00e7 takviyesi \\u00f6nerilir.<\\/div>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"L\\u00f6semi\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><div style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">L\\u00f6semi<\\/span>\\u00a0g\\u00fcndelik dildeki ad\\u0131yla\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kan kanser<\\/span>i, kan h\\u00fccrelerinin \\u00fcretildi\\u011fi kemik ili\\u011finde baz\\u0131 h\\u00fccrelerin kontrols\\u00fczce \\u00e7o\\u011falmas\\u0131 sonucu ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan bir kanser t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Kemik ili\\u011finde \\u00fcretilen ve v\\u00fccudun savunma mekanizmas\\u0131nda rol olan akyuvarlar, l\\u00f6semi sonucunda kontrols\\u00fczce olu\\u015fmu\\u015f baz\\u0131 h\\u00fccreler nedeniyle g\\u00f6revlerini yerine getiremezler. Bu durumda anemi belirtilerine ek olarak; ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sisteminde yetersizlik, iyile\\u015fmesi uzun s\\u00fcren morluklar, kanamalar ve solgun ten rengi g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir.<\\/div><div style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">L\\u00f6semi yayg\\u0131n bir kanser t\\u00fcr\\u00fc olup tedavide ba\\u015far\\u0131 olas\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 y\\u00fcksektir. Kemoterapi ve kemik ili\\u011fi ya da k\\u00f6k h\\u00fccre nakliyle tedavide ba\\u015far\\u0131 sa\\u011flan\\u0131r.<\\/div><\\/div>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Hematolojik Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n Belirtileri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hematolojik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n kendine has belirtileri bulunabilir. Ancak geneli kans\\u0131zl\\u0131kla ifade edilebilen bu hastal\\u0131klarda ortak belirtiler \\u015fu \\u015fekildedir:<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Halsizlik<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ge\\u00e7meyen yorgunluk<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Fiziksel aktiviteler s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda \\u00e7abuk yorulma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">S\\u0131kl\\u0131kla v\\u00fccudun \\u00e7e\\u015fitli yerlerinde kanama g\\u00f6r\\u00fclmesi\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kanamalar\\u0131n uzun s\\u00fcrmesi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">P\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fman\\u0131n azl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">S\\u0131k s\\u0131k enfeksiyon ge\\u00e7irme\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Y\\u00fcksek ate\\u015f<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Lenf d\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcmlerinde; boyun, kas\\u0131k ve koltukalt\\u0131nda \\u015fi\\u015fme<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Uzun s\\u00fcren morluklar<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ciltte solgunluk<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"H\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:37:55', '2023-12-27 16:06:42'),
