(658, 658, 86, 79, 1, 'İç Hastalıkları (Dahiliye)', 10, 'ic-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u0130\\u00e7 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (Dahiliye)\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u0130\\u00e7 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde genel i\\u00e7 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131nda\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">hematoloji<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">onkoloji,\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">nefroloji<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">endokrinoloji<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">kardiyoloji<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">romatoloji<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">gastroenteroloji<\\/span>\\u00a0dallar\\u0131nda hizmet verilmektedir. Hastanelerimizde yatan hastalar\\u0131n tedavilerini, kons\\u00fcltasyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131, ameliyat \\u00f6ncesi haz\\u0131rl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 ve gerekli giri\\u015fimlerini \\u0130\\u00e7 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fcz ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u0130\\u00e7 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life hastaneleri ve t\\u0131p merkezlerinin \\u0130\\u00e7 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde, \\u015fu alt dallarda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti verilmektedir:<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Gastroenteroloji<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Gastroenteroloji; sindirim sistemi (mide, ba\\u011f\\u0131rsak), karaci\\u011fer, safra yollar\\u0131 ve pankreas hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilenen bir bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Gastroenteroloji birimi \\u00e7e\\u015fitli sindirim sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisiyle ilgilenir. 112Life Gastroenteroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde; hepatologlar taraf\\u0131ndan\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">siroz<\\/span>un komplikasyonlar\\u0131 dahil olmak \\u00fczere karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131nda tedaviler uygulanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Endokrinoloji ve Metabolizma Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life\'daki Endokrinoloji ve Metabolizma Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerimiz;\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">endokrin sistem fizyolojisi<\\/span>\\u00a0ve<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">\\u00a0tiroid hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">diyabet<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">obezite<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">lipidler<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">osteoporoz<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">b\\u00f6brek \\u00fcst\\u00fc bezi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, \\u00fcreme endokrinolojisi<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">hipofiz hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">hormonal otoimm\\u00fcn hastal\\u0131klar<\\/span>\\u00a0ile ilgilenmektedir. Endokrinoloji ve Metabolizma Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 112Life\'\\u0131n t\\u00fcm hizmet alanlar\\u0131nda klinik hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Hematoloji<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hemoglobinopatilerde tan\\u0131, tedavi ve genetik dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131k,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">lenfoma<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">l\\u00f6semiler<\\/span>\\u00a0ve koag\\u00fclasyon bozukluklar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavi alanlar\\u0131nda hizmet vermektedir. Hematoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, 112Life Genetik Departman\\u0131 ile i\\u015fbirli\\u011fi yaparak maj\\u00f6r bir hemoglobinopati tarama merkezi ve hematolojik maliniteler i\\u00e7in kemoterapi ve h\\u00fccre tedavisi uygulayan bir merkez olarak geli\\u015fmeyi planlamaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Nefroloji<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Nefroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerimizde b\\u00f6brek rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131 olan hastalara tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetleri verilmektedir. Birimimizde nefroloji kons\\u00fcltasyonlar\\u0131 ve hipertansiyon klini\\u011fi yer almaktad\\u0131r. Servislerde,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">b\\u00f6brek hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">hipertansiyon<\\/span>, preeklampsi hastalar\\u0131n\\u0131n m\\u00fcdahaleleri ve b\\u00f6brek biyopsileri yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. Gerekli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc durumlarda hemodiyaliz ve CVVH (continuous venovenus hemofiltrasyon) terapileri uygulanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">Romatoloji<\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Romatoid artrit<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">ankilozan spondilit<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">sistemik lupus eritematozus<\\/span>\\u00a0gibi iltihapl\\u0131 romatizma hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131nda, a\\u011fr\\u0131l\\u0131 yumu\\u015fak doku romatizmalar\\u0131, halk aras\\u0131nda kire\\u00e7lenme diye bilinen osteoartrit ve benzeri hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n da te\\u015fhis ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tedavisinde gerekli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc takdirde ortopedi, n\\u00f6roloji ve a\\u011fr\\u0131 poliklini\\u011fi gibi dallardan destek al\\u0131nmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">T\\u0131bbi Onkoloji<\\/span><\\/h4><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><p style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106);\\\">112Life b\\u00fcnyesindeki T\\u0131bbi Onkoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri; kanserden korunma, kanser taramas\\u0131, erken tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetlerini kapsamaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\"><\\/div><div class=\\\"author\\\" style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\\\"><\\/div><\\/span><\\/h4>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u0130\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:41:28', '2023-12-27 16:06:20'),
