(666, 666, 86, 79, 1, 'Radyasyon Onkolojisi', 18, 'radyasyon-onkolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Radyasyon Onkolojisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Radyasyon Onkolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri, iyonizan radyasyon kullanarak radyasyonun kansere etkilerini, t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rlerin davran\\u0131\\u015flar\\u0131n\\u0131 inceleyen ve bu alanda ara\\u015ft\\u0131rma ve uygulama yapan birimdir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Tedavi \\u015eekli Nas\\u0131l Belirlenir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Tedavilerin \\u015feklini etkileyen pek \\u00e7ok fakt\\u00f6r bulunuyor. Bunlar\\u0131n ba\\u015f\\u0131nda; hastan\\u0131n ya\\u015f\\u0131, genel sa\\u011fl\\u0131k durumu, te\\u015fhis edilen kanserin t\\u00fcr\\u00fc, yayg\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, yerle\\u015fim yeri geliyor. Tedavi kararlar\\u0131, bir\\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 bran\\u015ftan uzman doktorun hastay\\u0131 birlikte g\\u00f6r\\u00fcp de\\u011ferlendirmeleri (Multidisiplinler yakla\\u015f\\u0131m\\u0131) sonucu al\\u0131n\\u0131yor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Her hasta i\\u00e7in ayr\\u0131 bir tan\\u0131 ve tedavi s\\u00fcreci planlan\\u0131yor ve uygulan\\u0131yor. \\u00c7\\u00fcnk\\u00fc ki\\u015filer ayn\\u0131 tip kanser hastas\\u0131 bile olsalar, her hastan\\u0131n tedavisi, kendi ko\\u015fullar\\u0131na g\\u00f6re de\\u011ferlendirilmelidir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Tedavi Ekibi Kimlerden Olu\\u015fuyor?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Radyasyon onkolojisi uzman\\u0131: V\\u00fccudun hangi b\\u00f6lgesine, ne kadar radyoterapi uygulanaca\\u011f\\u0131na karar veren, doktordur. Tedavi boyunca hastan\\u0131n takibi, t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rdeki de\\u011fi\\u015fikliklere ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak gerekli tedavi de\\u011fi\\u015fimi, hastan\\u0131n ya\\u015fad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 yan etkilerin de\\u011ferlendirilmesi ve tedavisinden sorumludur.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Radyasyon fizik\\u00e7isi:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0Radyoterapinin tedavi planlamas\\u0131, kalitesi ve cihazlarla ilgili teknik destek ve bak\\u0131m s\\u00fcrecinin koordinasyonu ile g\\u00fcvenli\\u011finden sorumludur. Tedavi plan\\u0131 ve uygulamas\\u0131nda radyasyon onkolojisi uzman\\u0131 ile birlikte \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Radyoterapi teknikerleri:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0Radyoterapi cihazlar\\u0131n\\u0131 kullanmak \\u00fczere e\\u011fitim alm\\u0131\\u015f ki\\u015filerdir. Tedavi s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda odada hasta ile birlikte bulunmazlar, ancak kumanda odas\\u0131nda bulunan ekran arac\\u0131l\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla; hasta ile kesintisiz ileti\\u015fim halindedirler. Hastan\\u0131n do\\u011fru pozisyonunun sa\\u011flanmas\\u0131, cihaz\\u0131n \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ve tedavi esnas\\u0131nda de\\u011ferlendirme filmlerinin \\u00e7ekilmesinden sorumludurlar.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Onkoloji hem\\u015firesi:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0Hastan\\u0131n tedavisi ve takibi s\\u00fcresince radyasyon onkologu ile birlikte hastan\\u0131n en yak\\u0131n\\u0131nda bulunan ekip \\u00fcyesidir. Radyoterapinin yan etkileri, hastan\\u0131n yapmas\\u0131 ve yapmamas\\u0131 gerekenler gibi konularda hekim ile hasta aras\\u0131nda k\\u00f6pr\\u00fc g\\u00f6revi yaparlar.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sekreterya:<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0Hastan\\u0131n do\\u011fru y\\u00f6nlendirilmesi, randevular\\u0131n d\\u00fczenlenmesi, dosyalar\\u0131n olu\\u015fturulmas\\u0131 ve bulundurulmas\\u0131, tedavi \\u00fccreti konusunda bilgilendirme ve hastan\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131k g\\u00fcvencesinin gerektirdi\\u011fi i\\u015flemlerin yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131ndan sorumludur.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Radyoterapinin Etkisi Nedir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Radyoterapide kullan\\u0131lan \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nlar, t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rl\\u00fc dokular\\u0131n h\\u00fccre \\u00e7ekirde\\u011findeki DNA\\u2019y\\u0131 etkiliyor. H\\u00fccre \\u00e7ekirde\\u011findeki DNA yeterince zarar g\\u00f6rd\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde ise h\\u00fccreler \\u00e7o\\u011falma yetene\\u011fini kaybediyor.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kanserli dokuda \\u00f6len h\\u00fccreler yenilenmedi\\u011finde, kanserin b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmesi duruyor ve kitle k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcl\\u00fcyor. Radyoterapi seans\\u0131 s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda verilen y\\u00fcksek dozdaki radyasyon, h\\u00fccreleri \\u00f6ld\\u00fcr\\u00fcyor veya \\u00e7o\\u011falmalar\\u0131n\\u0131 engelliyor. T\\u00fcm\\u00f6r h\\u00fccreleri bir\\u00e7ok normal h\\u00fccreden daha h\\u0131zl\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcnd\\u00fcklerinden radyoterapi bu h\\u00fccreleri y\\u00fcksek oranda \\u00f6ld\\u00fcr\\u00fcyor. Normal h\\u00fccreler de radyoterapiden belli \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcde etkilense de t\\u00fcm\\u00f6r h\\u00fccrelerinde olmayan \\u00f6zel onar\\u0131m mekanizmalar\\u0131yla bu etkiden k\\u0131sa s\\u00fcrede kurtulabiliyorlar.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Radyocerrahi\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Radyasyon onkolojisinin uygulama alanlar\\u0131ndan biri olan radyocerrahide temel ama\\u00e7; \\u00e7ok say\\u0131da d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck enerjili \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n demetlerinin hastal\\u0131kl\\u0131 b\\u00f6lgeye y\\u00f6nlendirilmesi ve hastal\\u0131kl\\u0131 noktada odaklan\\u0131p, sadece bu noktada y\\u00fcksek enerji sa\\u011flayarak dokuda de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik yarat\\u0131lmas\\u0131d\\u0131r. B\\u00f6ylece hastal\\u0131kl\\u0131 b\\u00f6lgeye yo\\u011fun \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n verilerek kanser h\\u00fccrelerinin k\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fclmesi ya da \\u00f6lmesi sa\\u011flan\\u0131rken, \\u00e7evresindeki normal dokular da radyasyonun zararl\\u0131 etkilerinden korunmu\\u015f oluyor.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"R\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:47:18', '2023-12-27 16:01:53'),
