(670, 670, 86, 79, 1, 'Spor Hekimliği', 19, 'spor-hekimligi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Spor Hekimli\\u011fi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life Spor Hekimli\\u011fi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde amat\\u00f6r ve profesyonel sporcular\\u0131n sezon \\u00f6ncesi muayeneleri, spora \\u00f6zel performans d\\u00fczeyinin saptanmas\\u0131 ve art\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in egzersiz planlama, spor yaralanmalar\\u0131na yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n belirlenmesi ve buna ba\\u011fl\\u0131 gereken \\u00f6nlemlerin\\/egzersizlerin d\\u00fczenlenmesi, yaralanm\\u0131\\u015f sporcunun tetkik edilip, cerrahi veya cerrahi d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 tedavileri, kronik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 olan bireylere egzersiz plan\\u0131 yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><div><br><\\/div>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Spor Hekimli\\u011fi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Spor Hekimli\\u011fi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Her ya\\u015ftan ve her daldan sporcularda sezon \\u00f6ncesi muayeneleri yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. \\u0130lgili hekim muayenesi sonras\\u0131 gerek g\\u00f6r\\u00fcl\\u00fcrse gerekli di\\u011fer hekimlerden de g\\u00f6r\\u00fc\\u015f al\\u0131nmakta ve tetkikler planlanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Farkl\\u0131 spor bran\\u015flar\\u0131na g\\u00f6re sporcular\\u0131n performans testleri,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">VO2max,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Anaerobik e\\u015fik,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">T\\u00fcm eklemlere y\\u00f6nelik izokinetik g\\u00fc\\u00e7 testleri,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Hareket analizi,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Y\\u00fcr\\u00fcme ve ko\\u015fman\\u0131n de\\u011ferlendirilmesi,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Yaralanm\\u0131\\u015f sporcunun cerrahi d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 tedavisinin planlanmas\\u0131, gerekirse cerrahi tedavisi i\\u00e7in gerekli b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerle kons\\u00fclte edilmesi, cerrahi sonras\\u0131nda rehabilite edilmeleri ve sahaya geri d\\u00f6n\\u00fclmesini sa\\u011flama,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Cerrahi d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 tedavinin sporcunun fizyoterapist ve antrenman bilimcileri ile i\\u015fbirli\\u011fi i\\u00e7inde planlanmas\\u0131 ve maksimum d\\u00fczeyde sahaya\\/m\\u00fcsabakaya geri d\\u00f6nmesini sa\\u011flama,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sporcular\\u0131n sporuna uygun saha testleri, y\\u00fcksek h\\u0131zl\\u0131 kamera ve hareket analiz sistemleri kullan\\u0131larak yaralanmaya yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 belirleme,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sporculara ergojenik destek konusunda yard\\u0131m vermek i\\u00e7in spor diyetisyenleri ile kons\\u00fclte edip, beslenme profillerininin ortaya konmas\\u0131, do\\u011fru beslenme al\\u0131\\u015fkanl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n geli\\u015ftirilmesi ve gerekli ergojenik desteklerle takviyesi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sporcular\\u0131n performans\\u0131n\\u0131n art\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in spor bilimciler, antren\\u00f6rler ve spor biyomekanik uzmanlar\\u0131 ile de\\u011ferlendirilip gerekli destek sa\\u011flanmas\\u0131,<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kronik sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131 olan hastalar\\u0131n (koroner arter hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, \\u015feker, y\\u00fcksek tansiyon, obezite, vb..) tedavisinin bir par\\u00e7as\\u0131 olan egzersizi sorunsuz bir \\u015fekilde hayatlar\\u0131na adapte edilmesini sa\\u011flama hizmetleri verilmektedir.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"S\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:50:25', '2023-12-27 16:01:01'),
