(674, 674, 86, 79, 1, 'Tıbbi Genetik', 20, 'tibbi-genetik', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"T\\u0131bbi Genetik\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">T\\u0131bbi Genetik<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, genetik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve y\\u00f6netimi ile ailesel ve ki\\u015fisel genetik dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131k alan\\u0131nda hizmet veren bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fcz bilimsel geli\\u015fmeleri yak\\u0131ndan takip eden T\\u0131bbi Genetik uzmanlar\\u0131 ve teknolojik altyap\\u0131 sayesinde klinik bulgular\\u0131 laboratuvar sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131 ile yorumlayarak hastalara ve dan\\u0131\\u015fanlara tan\\u0131, tedavi ve hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 \\u00f6nlemede y\\u00f6n g\\u00f6sterebilen \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcm odakl\\u0131 bir anlay\\u0131\\u015fa sahiptir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Genetik bir miras olarak ebeveynlerimizden ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131m\\u0131z DNA\\u2019m\\u0131zda bizlere ait bireysel \\u00f6zellikleri i\\u00e7eren t\\u00fcm bilgiler bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Bu bilgiler kan grubu, boy, kilo gibi bireysel \\u00f6zelliklerimizden,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">diyabet<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">kanser<\\/span>,\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">kardiyovask\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar<\\/span>\\u00a0gibi y\\u00fczlerce farkl\\u0131 duruma yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131k ya da direnci belirleyen \\u00f6zelliklerle ili\\u015fkilidir. DNA\\u2019m\\u0131zdaki bu bilgilerin \\u00e7evresel fakt\\u00f6rlerle etkile\\u015fmesi sonucu ki\\u015fisel \\u00f6zelliklerimiz ve hastal\\u0131klar ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilmektedir. Bug\\u00fcn genetik alan\\u0131nda ula\\u015ft\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131m\\u0131z bilgi ve teknolojilerle uzun ve sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 ya\\u015fam anahtar\\u0131n\\u0131n elimizde oldu\\u011fu yepyeni bir d\\u00f6neme girmi\\u015f bulunmaktay\\u0131z.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Aile \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fcnde bulunan genetik hastal\\u0131klar ve hen\\u00fcz tan\\u0131 konmam\\u0131\\u015f ancak ailenin bir\\u00e7ok ferdinde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan hastal\\u0131klar (\\u00d6rne\\u011fin birden \\u00e7ok ki\\u015fide \\u00f6zellikle 50 ya\\u015f \\u00f6ncesi kanser, diyabet, n\\u00f6rolojik hastal\\u0131k, g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 vb bozukluklar), sebebi bilinmeyen bebek \\/ \\u00e7ocuk kayb\\u0131 \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc, akraba evlili\\u011fi sonras\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuk planlamas\\u0131 ve ailede kanser \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc gibi pek \\u00e7ok t\\u0131bbi durumun ara\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131larak ki\\u015filere buna y\\u00f6nelik dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131k verilmesi T\\u0131bbi Genetik b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftiriliyor.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Genetik Hastal\\u0131klar i\\u00e7in Neden Ta\\u015f\\u0131y\\u0131c\\u0131l\\u0131k Testleri Yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Genetik hastal\\u0131klar<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0i\\u00e7in ta\\u015f\\u0131y\\u0131c\\u0131l\\u0131k, san\\u0131lan\\u0131n aksine olduk\\u00e7a yayg\\u0131n bir durumdur. Mevcut t\\u0131bbi bilgiler ile her 100 ki\\u015fiden 4\'\\u00fcn\\u00fcn\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Fenilketon\\u00fcri<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve her 100 ki\\u015fiden 4\\u2019\\u00fcn\\u00fcn\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Kistik Fibrozis<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">, her 100 ki\\u015fiden 2\\u2019sinin\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Spinal Musk\\u00fcler Atrofi (SMA)<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0ve her 100 ki\\u015fiden 2\\u2019sinin\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\\">Akdeniz Anemisi (Talesemi)<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0i\\u00e7in ta\\u015f\\u0131y\\u0131c\\u0131 oldu\\u011fu bilinmektedir. T\\u0131bbi Genetik b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde evlilik ya da planlanan olas\\u0131 gebeliklerden \\u00f6nce oldu\\u011fu gibi gebelik s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda da t\\u00fcm ta\\u015f\\u0131y\\u0131c\\u0131l\\u0131k testleri h\\u0131zl\\u0131 ve ba\\u015far\\u0131l\\u0131 bir \\u015fekilde yap\\u0131larak sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir gebelik ve bebek sahibi olmak i\\u00e7in en uygun yol planlanabilmektedir.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"Preimplantasyon Genetik Tan\\u0131 (PGT) Nedir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">PGT<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0bilinen bir kal\\u0131tsal genetik hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 olan \\u00e7iftlerin sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bebek elde etmesi i\\u00e7in genetik tan\\u0131 ile t\\u00fcp bebek uygulamalar\\u0131n\\u0131n birlikte uygulanarak do\\u011facak bebekte bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kma ihtimalinin ekarte edilmesi i\\u00e7in uygulanan genetik tan\\u0131 y\\u00f6ntemidir.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">PGT i\\u015flemi nedeni bilinen hemen t\\u00fcm genetik hastal\\u0131klar i\\u00e7in uygulanabilmekte olup bu hastal\\u0131klardan baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 \\u00f6rnek olarak a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131da g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilir:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Spinal M\\u00fcsk\\u00fcler Atrofi (SMA)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Talasemi (Akdeniz Anemisi)<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Duchenne\\/Becker M\\u00fcsk\\u00fcler Distrofi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Frajil X<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Fenilketon\\u00fcri<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kromozomal hastal\\u0131klar vb.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Non-invazif (Giri\\u015fimsel olmayan) Prenatal Genetik Tan\\u0131 (NIPT) Nedir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">NIPT kromozomal hastal\\u0131klar ba\\u015fta olmak \\u00fczere bebek sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 tehdit eden bir\\u00e7ok genetik bozukluk i\\u00e7in anne kan\\u0131ndan yap\\u0131labilen en erken ve en kolay tarama testlerinden biridir. 9. gebelik haftas\\u0131ndan itibaren bebe\\u011fin serbest gezen DNA\\u2019s\\u0131 annenin kan\\u0131nda analiz edilebilecek d\\u00fczeye gelir. Anne kan\\u0131ndan \\u00f6rnek al\\u0131nd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in bebe\\u011fe zarar gelme ihtimali yoktur. Hatal\\u0131 sonu\\u00e7 y\\u00fczdesi olduk\\u00e7a d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fckt\\u00fcr.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">NIPT s\\u00fcreci nas\\u0131l ilerler?<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">NIPT s\\u00fcreci olduk\\u00e7a kolayd\\u0131r. Anne kolundan herhangi bir testte oldu\\u011fu gibi al\\u0131nan kan \\u00f6rne\\u011fi analiz sonras\\u0131nda 7-14 g\\u00fcn i\\u00e7inde raporlanmaktad\\u0131r. Test \\u00f6ncesi ve test sonras\\u0131 deneyimli T\\u0131bbi Genetik uzmanlar\\u0131m\\u0131z taraf\\u0131ndan genetik dan\\u0131\\u015fma verilebilmektedir.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Kanserde Genetik Dan\\u0131\\u015fma\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/div><div class=\\\"author\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; font-style: italic; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/div><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\">Kendinde ya da ailesinde<span>\\u00a0<\\/span><strong style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">kanser \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc<\\/strong><span>\\u00a0<\\/span>bulunan ya da kal\\u0131tsal kanser gen mutasyonu ta\\u015f\\u0131yan veya ta\\u015f\\u0131ma riski bulunan ki\\u015filere ve bu ki\\u015filerin akrabalar\\u0131na, hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n seyri, tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri, tekrarlama riskleri ve \\u00f6nlenmesi i\\u00e7in \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcm yollar\\u0131 belirlenmesinde, gerekli testlerin planlanmas\\u0131 ve bunlar\\u0131n sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131 ile ilgili bilgi verilmesi i\\u00e7in<span>\\u00a0<\\/span><strong style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">T\\u0131bbi Genetik<span>\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/strong>uzmanlar\\u0131m\\u0131z dan\\u0131\\u015fanlar\\u0131m\\u0131za ve hastalar\\u0131m\\u0131za hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"T\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:52:19', '2023-12-27 16:00:30'),
