(678, 678, 86, 79, 1, 'Üroloji', 22, 'uroloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00dcroloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00dcroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri, yeti\\u015fkin ve \\u00e7ocuk hastalara \\u00fcrolojik muayene, tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti vermektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00dcroloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00dcroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri; prostat ve mesane TUR ameliyatlar\\u0131, a\\u00e7\\u0131k ve kapal\\u0131 ta\\u015f ameliyatlar\\u0131 (\\u00fcreteroskopi, perk\\u00fctan nefrolitotomi), ta\\u015f k\\u0131rma (ESWL) tedavisi gibi rutin operasyonlar d\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131nda \\u00fcrolojik kanser ameliyatlar\\u0131, \\u00e7ocuk \\u00fcrolojisi ameliyatlar\\u0131, \\u00fcrodinami ve erkek cinsel i\\u015flev bozukluklar\\u0131 konular\\u0131nda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti sunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Prostat b\\u00fcy\\u00fcmesine (BPH) ba\\u011fl\\u0131 idrar rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavisinde ila\\u00e7 ve cerrahi tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">(TUR, Greenlight Lazer PVP, Greelight Lazer HPS, Holmium Lazer<\\/span>\\u00a0ile\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">yap\\u0131lan prostat ameliyat\\u0131 -HoLEP-, Thulium Lazer<\\/span>\\u00a0ile\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">yap\\u0131lan prostat ameliyat\\u0131 -ThuLEP-, \\u00a0Feedback Termoterapi)<\\/span>\\u00a0uygulanmaktad\\u0131r. Ayr\\u0131ca prostat kanseri taramas\\u0131 ve prostat enfeksiyonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavisi gibi prostat sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 ilgilendiren alanlarda yo\\u011fun \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalar yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\\u00dcroonkoloji\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B\\u00f6l\\u00fcmde sinir koruyucu radikal prostatektomi (prostat kanseri i\\u00e7in) ve radikal sistektomi (mesane kanseri i\\u00e7in) ameliyatlar\\u0131 s\\u0131kl\\u0131kla uygulanmaktad\\u0131r. Ayr\\u0131ca anesteziyoloji ve yo\\u011fun bak\\u0131m hizmetinin de deste\\u011fi ile b\\u00f6brek ve testis kanseri gibi di\\u011fer \\u00fcrolojik onkoloji ameliyatlar\\u0131 ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. Baz\\u0131 \\u00fcrolojik kanser vakalar\\u0131nda ise medikal onkoloji ve radyoterapi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri ile e\\u015fg\\u00fcd\\u00fcm i\\u00e7erisinde tedavi planlanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Endo\\u00fcroloji ve Ta\\u015f Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life\'da \\u00fcriner sistem ta\\u015f hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 tedavisinde endoskopik (kapal\\u0131 sistem) ameliyatlar da uygulanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Cerrahi tedavinin yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra ta\\u015f k\\u0131rma (ESWL) y\\u00f6ntemi kullan\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. \\u00dcroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc ta\\u015f hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n endo\\u00fcrolojik tedavisinde (\\u00fcreteroskopi, perk\\u00fctan b\\u00f6brek ta\\u015f\\u0131 cerrahisi \\u2013 PCNL) hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Kad\\u0131n \\u00fcrolojisi\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u0130drar ka\\u00e7\\u0131rma (stres ve s\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015fma inkontinans\\u0131), interstisyel sistit gibi hastal\\u0131klarda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti verilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00dcrodinami \\u00fcnitesi idrar tutabilme ve idrar yapabilme ile ilgili sorunlar\\u0131nda tan\\u0131sal incelenme olana\\u011f\\u0131 sa\\u011flar. Her tip idrar ka\\u00e7\\u0131rma sorunlar\\u0131n\\u0131n, \\u00f6rne\\u011fin \\u00e7ocuklarda gece \\u0131slatmalar\\u0131 ya da kad\\u0131nlarda idrar ka\\u00e7\\u0131rma rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n ve miyelodisplazi (spina bifida) hastalar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131, tedavi ve takibinde \\u00fcrodinamik incelemeler ve \\u00fcro-radyolojik y\\u00f6ntemler kullan\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00dc\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 17:54:31', '2023-12-27 15:59:58'),
