(682, 682, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Endokrinolojisi', 4, 'cocuk-endokrinolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Endokrinolojisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Endokrinoloji<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0hormon ve hormon salg\\u0131layan bezleri ilgilendiren hastal\\u0131klar ve metabolik sorunlar ile u\\u011fra\\u015fan bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. 112Life \\u00c7ocuk Endokrinolojisi (Pediatrik Endokrinoloji) b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde, yenido\\u011fan d\\u00f6neminden 16 ya\\u015f\\u0131na kadar olan bebek, \\u00e7ocuk ve ergenlerde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme-geli\\u015fmeye ait sorunlar\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra, hormonal ve metabolik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n \\u00e7\\u00f6z\\u00fcmlerine y\\u00f6nelik hizmetler verilmektedir.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Endokrinolojisi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme gerilikleri\\u00a0<br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 boy k\\u0131sal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme hormonu eksikli\\u011fi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><font color=\\\"#4f4f4f\\\">\\u00a0 <\\/font><font color=\\\"#6a6a6a\\\">erken ergenlik<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 gecikmi\\u015f ergenlik\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u015feker hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 (diyabet<\\/span>)<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">hipoglisemi (kan \\u015fekeri d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc)<\\/span><b>\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><b>\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/b><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u015fi\\u015fmanl\\u0131k (obezite)<\\/span>\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">guatr<\\/span>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">tiroid bezi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span>\\u00a0(<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">hipotiroidi<\\/span>-<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">hipertiroidi<\\/span>)<b>\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 cinsel geli\\u015fim bozukluklar\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 penis sorunlar\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 b\\u00f6brek \\u00fcst\\u00fc bezi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; transition: all 0.1s ease 0s; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">adet d\\u00fczensizlikleri<\\/span>\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0 a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 t\\u00fcylenme\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<span style=