(686, 686, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Enfeksiyon Hastalıkları', 4, 'cocuk-enfeksiyon-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Enfeksiyon Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00c7ocuk Enfeksiyon Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde; \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131nda en s\\u0131k doktora ba\\u015fvuru sebebi olan ate\\u015fli hastal\\u0131klar takip edilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00dcst ve alt solunum yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131, ishal ve idrar yolu enfeksiyonu vb. s\\u0131k kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan hastal\\u0131klar tetkik ve takip edilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ayr\\u0131ca g\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde artan s\\u0131kl\\u0131kla g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n d\\u00f6k\\u00fcnt\\u00fcl\\u00fc hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na, bula\\u015f\\u0131c\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na, hastane enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na, konjenital enfeksiyonlara, kanser hastalar\\u0131n\\u0131n zor enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na, \\u00e7e\\u015fitli nedenlerle\\u00a0 ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemi bask\\u0131lanan \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n f\\u0131rsat\\u00e7\\u0131 enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na ve\\/veya kazan\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f imm\\u00fcnyetmezlik vir\\u00fcs\\u00fc (HIV) ta\\u015f\\u0131yan \\u00e7ocuk ve ad\\u00f6lesanlara y\\u00f6nelik tetkik ve tedaviler planlanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">A\\u015f\\u0131yla korunabilen hastal\\u0131klara kar\\u015f\\u0131 bilgi verilmekte ve \\u00f6zel durumlar i\\u00e7in (ameliyat sonras\\u0131, seyahat \\u00f6ncesi a\\u015f\\u0131lama vb.) \\u00e7ocuklara \\u00f6zel a\\u015f\\u0131 takvimleri d\\u00fczenlenmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde h\\u0131zla artan alerjik vakalar\\u0131n diren\\u00e7li enfeksiyonlar\\u0131na ve s\\u0131k tekrar eden enfeksiyonlara kar\\u015f\\u0131 ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemi detayl\\u0131 olarak ara\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131lmakta ve gerekli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde enfeksiyon s\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131\\/\\u015fiddetini azaltmak amac\\u0131yla yakla\\u015f\\u0131mlar uygulanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 18:02:54', '2023-12-27 15:55:03'),
