(694, 694, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Genetik Hastalıkları', 4, 'cocuk-genetik-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Genetik Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Genetik Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fcz;<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0kal\\u0131tsal hastal\\u0131klar, do\\u011fumsal anomaliler, genetik sendromlar, ya da genetik yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131k sonucu ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan hastal\\u0131klara gebelik (prenatal d\\u00f6nem) d\\u00f6neminden ba\\u015flayarak tan\\u0131 koyar. 18 ya\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131 a\\u015fmam\\u0131\\u015f olan \\u00e7ocuklar ve bebeklerdeki genetik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n, te\\u015fhis, takip ve tedavi s\\u00fcre\\u00e7leri, \\u00e7ocuk genetik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 uzmanlar\\u0131n\\u0131n sorumlulu\\u011fundad\\u0131r.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bu birimimiz; genetik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n takip edilmesi, v\\u00fccutta meydana gelebilecek tahribatlar\\u0131n \\u00f6n\\u00fcne ge\\u00e7ilebilmesi, genel sa\\u011fl\\u0131k durumunun iyile\\u015ftirilmesi, ileri ki d\\u00f6nemlerde hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n kendi \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131na aktar\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131n engellenebilmesi, acil m\\u00fcdahale gerektirecek sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131n\\u0131n azalt\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ve hastal\\u0131k seyrinin yava\\u015flatabilmesi gibi durumlar a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan olduk\\u00e7a b\\u00fcy\\u00fck \\u00f6neme sahiptir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Ayr\\u0131ca genetik hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 mevcut ki\\u015filerin kal\\u0131tsal aktar\\u0131mdan korunup, sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 fertler d\\u00fcnyaya getirmek ad\\u0131na dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131k hizmetleri de bu birimimiz taraf\\u0131ndan sa\\u011flanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuklarda ve Bebeklerde Genetik Hastal\\u0131klar Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bebeklerde ve \\u00e7ocuklarda kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015f\\u0131lan genetik hastal\\u0131klar, ileri d\\u00f6nemlerde ya\\u015fam kalitelerinin d\\u00fc\\u015fmesine sebep olabilir. \\u00c7ocuklar\\u0131n, fizyolojik ve psikolojik sa\\u011fl\\u0131k durumlar\\u0131n\\u0131n kontroll\\u00fc bir \\u015fekilde devam edebilmesi ad\\u0131na yak\\u0131n takip esast\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Genetik Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tedavi Y\\u00f6ntemleri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">G\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fczde \\u00e7ocuk genetik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tamamen iyile\\u015ftirilmesini sa\\u011flayan tedaviler hen\\u00fcz bulunamam\\u0131\\u015f olsada yap\\u0131lan ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar ve y\\u00fcr\\u00fct\\u00fclen \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalar, tedavi imkanlar\\u0131n\\u0131n artmas\\u0131na ve genetik aktar\\u0131m\\u0131n \\u00f6n\\u00fcne ge\\u00e7ilmesine destek olmaktad\\u0131r. Semptomlar\\u0131n azalt\\u0131lmas\\u0131, genel sa\\u011fl\\u0131k durumunun muhafaza edilmesi, hastal\\u0131k ilerleyi\\u015finin yava\\u015flat\\u0131lmas\\u0131 ve g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck hayat\\u0131n kalitesinin art\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131na y\\u00f6nelik giri\\u015fimler uygulan\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"Akraba Evlili\\u011fine Ba\\u011fl\\u0131 Hastal\\u0131klar\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Akraba evlili\\u011fi ili\\u015fkilerinden meydana gelen gebelikler d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fck ya da \\u00f6l\\u00fc do\\u011fum gibi sonu\\u00e7lar\\u0131 beraberinde getirebilir. Ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015fen do\\u011fumlarda da zeka gerili\\u011fi, kal\\u0131tsal hastal\\u0131klar ve do\\u011fumsal anomalilerin g\\u00f6r\\u00fclme riski istatistiklere g\\u00f6re \\u00e7ok y\\u00fcksektir. Bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n te\\u015fhis edilmesi, \\u00f6nlenebilmesi i\\u00e7in uygun tedavilerin sa\\u011flanmas\\u0131 ve ailelerin bilin\\u00e7lendirilmesi bu birimin sorumlulu\\u011fundad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"Aile \\u00dcyelerinde Kal\\u0131tsal Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n G\\u00f6r\\u00fclmesi\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Di\\u011fer aile bireylerinde genetik y\\u00f6nden aktar\\u0131lan kal\\u0131tsal sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131 mevcutsa, bu sorunlar\\u0131n \\u00e7ocukta da g\\u00f6r\\u00fclme riski olduk\\u00e7a y\\u00fcksektir. Bu y\\u00fczden detayl\\u0131 analizlerin ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmesi, hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n g\\u00f6r\\u00fclme riskinin hesaplanmas\\u0131, koruyucu tedavilerin uygulanmas\\u0131 ve semptomlar\\u0131n m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn oldu\\u011funca azalt\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gerekir.<\\/p>\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 18:05:16', '2023-12-27 15:59:33');
