(698, 698, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Göğüs Hastalıkları', 4, 'cocuk-gogus-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131ndaki ki\\u015filerde akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131; kistik fibrozis, t\\u00fcberk\\u00fcloz, do\\u011fumsal anomaliler, premat\\u00fcrenin akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, bron\\u015fiyolit, bron\\u015fit, pn\\u00f6moni, bron\\u015fektazi, sistemik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n akci\\u011fer tutulumu, intersitisiyel akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, pulmoner hemosiderozis, gastro\\u00f6zofagiyel refl\\u00fc ve kist hidatik hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, tetkik tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 i\\u00e7in solunum fonksiyon testleri ve ter testi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. Gereksinim duyuldu\\u011funda 112Life\'\\u0131n di\\u011fer t\\u00fcm b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleriyle \\u00f6zellikle n\\u00fckleer t\\u0131p, biyokimya, patoloji, genetik ve di\\u011fer tan\\u0131 laboratuvarlar\\u0131yla i\\u015fbirli\\u011fi i\\u00e7inde faaliyet g\\u00f6sterilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\"