(702, 702, 86, 79, 1, 'Romatoloji', 18, 'romatoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Romatoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Romatoloji i\\u00e7 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn bir yan dal\\u0131 olarak romatizmal hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n, \\u00f6zellikle de iltihapl\\u0131 romatizmal hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi i\\u00e7in hizmet vermektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"Romatoloji B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Romatoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde, Sistemik Lupus Eritematozus, Sj\\u00f6gren Sendromu, Vask\\u00fclitler gibi Ba\\u011f Dokusu Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, Gut Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, Romatoid Artrit, Ankilozan Spondilit, Sedef artriti, gibi iltihapl\\u0131 romatizma hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra, a\\u011fr\\u0131l\\u0131 yumu\\u015fak doku romatizmalar\\u0131n\\u0131n, halk aras\\u0131nda kire\\u00e7lenme diye bilinen osteoartrit ve benzeri hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n da te\\u015fhis ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tedavisinde gerekli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc takdirde Fizik Tedavi, Ortopedi, N\\u00f6roloji ve A\\u011fr\\u0131 Poliklini\\u011fi gibi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerden de destek al\\u0131nmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"R\",\"status_1\":\"0\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-20 18:10:21', '2023-12-27 16:01:27'),
