(714, 714, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Kardiyolojisi', 4, 'cocuk-kardiyolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Kalp Damar Cerrahisi\",\"content_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk kardiyolojisi<\\/span>; bebek ve \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n kalp ve damar sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla ilgilenen, dola\\u015f\\u0131m sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n te\\u015fhis ve tedavisini yapan t\\u0131bbi bran\\u015ft\\u0131r. \\u00c7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde, pediyatrik kardiyologlar; 0-18 ya\\u015f aral\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndaki bebek ve \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n anne karn\\u0131ndaki geli\\u015fiminden itibaren kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilenir.<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kalp ve damarlar\\u0131n sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131yla ilgilenen kardiyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnden farkl\\u0131 olarak \\u00e7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, anne karn\\u0131nda organlar\\u0131n olu\\u015ftu\\u011fu zamandan itibaren kardiyovask\\u00fcler sorunlar\\u0131n ve hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tedavisiyle ilgilenir. Kalp ve damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131 do\\u011fumsal ya da kal\\u0131tsal olabildi\\u011finden, bu t\\u00fcr hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n erken tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi olduk\\u00e7a \\u00f6nemlidir. Do\\u011fumsal olmayan, zamanla olu\\u015fan hastal\\u0131klar, kronik kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve akut kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde pediyatrik kardiyologlar taraf\\u0131ndan tedavi edilir.<\\/div>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Kardiyolojisi Hangi Hastal\\u0131klara Bakar?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Bebeklerde ve \\u00e7ocuklarda kalp ve damarlar\\u0131n yap\\u0131sal ya da fonksiyonel hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n ortak bir tak\\u0131m belirtileri bulunmaktad\\u0131r. Bu belirtiler hekim taraf\\u0131ndan de\\u011ferlendirilmeli, belirtiler bir hastal\\u0131\\u011fa aitse bunun te\\u015fhisi yap\\u0131lmal\\u0131 ve tedavisi uygulanmal\\u0131d\\u0131r. \\u00c7ocuklarda kardiyovask\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n belirtileri \\u015fu \\u015fekildedir:<\\/div><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">A\\u011flarken ya da normal zamanlarda morarma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">S\\u0131k ve kesik nefes al\\u0131p verme, solunum g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fckleri<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7abuk yorulma ve halsizlik \\u015fikayetleri, hareket ederken zorlanma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi ve bay\\u0131lma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Tekrarlayan solunum yolu enfeksiyonlar\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kalpte \\u00fcf\\u00fcr\\u00fcm\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7arp\\u0131nt\\u0131 hissi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00c7ocuklarda y\\u00fcksek kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131, hipertansiyon<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kilo alamama, ya\\u015f\\u0131tlar\\u0131ndan fiziksel olarak geri kalma<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Geli\\u015fme bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/li><\\/ul><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuklarda ve bebeklerde kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n belirtisi olan bu durumlar ba\\u015fka hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 da i\\u015faret edebilirler. Bu \\u015fikayetler g\\u00f6r\\u00fcld\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcnde hekime ba\\u015fvurulmal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde te\\u015fhisi ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lan ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca hastal\\u0131klar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/div><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Konjenital kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u00dcf\\u00fcr\\u00fcm<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ritim bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kapak hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">\\u0130nfektif endokardit<\\/li><\\/ul><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Kardiyovask\\u00fcler hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131 do\\u011fumsal yani konjenital olabilir. Bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n baz\\u0131lar\\u0131 anne karn\\u0131ndayken te\\u015fhis edilebilirler. Do\\u011fumsal kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n b\\u00fcy\\u00fck bir k\\u0131sm\\u0131 bebe\\u011fin ilerleyen 1 ya\\u015f\\u0131 i\\u00e7inde hekimler taraf\\u0131ndan te\\u015fhis edilebilirler. \\u00c7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde bu hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n uygun tedavileri ve tedavi sonras\\u0131 kontrolleri sa\\u011flan\\u0131r. Konjenital kalp hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n nedenleri genetik, metabolik ya da teratojenik olabilir.\\u00a0<\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><br style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk kardiyolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde uygulanan ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca tan\\u0131sal y\\u00f6ntemler; kalp kateterizasyonu, kalp elektrokardiyografisi(EKG), holter, telekardiyografi, ekokardiyografi (EKO), renkli doppler kardiyografi, elektrofizyoloji ve efor testidir. Hekim taraf\\u0131ndan \\u00e7ocu\\u011fun \\u015fikayeleri ve ailesinin g\\u00f6zlemleri de\\u011ferlendirilir, hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 i\\u00e7in bu tekniklerden faydalan\\u0131l\\u0131r. Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131n\\u0131n konmas\\u0131ndan itibaren, hastal\\u0131\\u011fa uygun tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri uygulanmaya ba\\u015flan\\u0131r.<\\/div>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-21 10:27:28', '2023-12-27 16:05:54'),
