(726, 726, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Nörolojisi', 4, 'cocuk-norolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p>\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisi, beyin, omurilik, sinir ve kas hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisini yapan ve 0-18 ya\\u015f grubu \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131 kapsayan bir t\\u0131p uzmanl\\u0131k dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Birimimiz \\u201cGeli\\u015fim n\\u00f6rolojisi\\u201d ya da \\u201cPediatrik n\\u00f6roloji\\u201d olarak da literat\\u00fcrde yer al\\u0131r.<\\/p><p>0-18 ya\\u015f grubunda b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme ve geli\\u015fme devam etti\\u011fi i\\u00e7in bu grupta ki bireylerin n\\u00f6rolojik muayeneleri, hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n nedenleri, tan\\u0131 ve tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri yeti\\u015fkinlere g\\u00f6re farkl\\u0131l\\u0131k g\\u00f6sterir ve bu dalda uzmanl\\u0131k gerektirir.<\\/p><p>\\u00c7ocuk n\\u00f6rolojisi, premat\\u00fcre ve risk ta\\u015f\\u0131yan bebeklerin n\\u00f6rolojik s\\u00fcre\\u00e7leri, \\u00e7ocuklarda geli\\u015fim bozukluklar\\u0131, beyin travmalar\\u0131, \\u015fuur kayb\\u0131, y\\u0131llar i\\u00e7erisinde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan y\\u00fcr\\u00fcme bozukluklar\\u0131, ailevi ge\\u00e7i\\u015fli n\\u00f6rolojik hastal\\u0131klar, ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, fel\\u00e7, epilepsi, kas ve sinir yaralanmalar\\u0131, serebral palsi, otistik \\u015fikayetler, davran\\u0131\\u015f bozukluklar\\u0131 da dahil olmak \\u00fczere geni\\u015f bir \\u00e7er\\u00e7eveye yay\\u0131l\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisinin \\u0130lgilendi\\u011fi Hastal\\u0131klar Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(106, 106, 106); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk n\\u00f6rolojisi doktorlar\\u0131 taraf\\u0131ndan takip edilen hastal\\u0131klar beyin ve sinir sistemiyle alakal\\u0131 oldu\\u011fu i\\u00e7in olduk\\u00e7a geni\\u015f yelpazede incelenebilir. Gebelik ve do\\u011fum esnas\\u0131nda geli\\u015fen anormallikler, beyin hasarlanmalar\\u0131, serebral palsi, fel\\u00e7ler gibi perk \\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi \\u00e7ocuk n\\u00f6rolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn sorumlulu\\u011fundad\\u0131r.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisi Tan\\u0131 Y\\u00f6ntemleri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastan\\u0131n rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n ele al\\u0131n\\u0131p, tan\\u0131 yoluna gidilebilmesi i\\u00e7in \\u00f6ncelikle klinik de\\u011ferlendirme yap\\u0131l\\u0131r. Doktorun hasta \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fcn\\u00fc detayl\\u0131 dinlemesinin ard\\u0131ndan\\u00a0 fiziksel muayene yap\\u0131l\\u0131r. Anamnez ad\\u0131 verilen doktorun hastan\\u0131n \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fcn\\u00fc dinledi\\u011fi s\\u00fcre\\u00e7te; genel durum, ya\\u015f, g\\u00fc\\u00e7, g\\u00f6rme i\\u015fitme durumu, konu\\u015fma becerisi gibi konular hakk\\u0131nda fikir sahibi olarak hastal\\u0131k ile ilgili \\u00f6n bilgilere eri\\u015filir.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk muayene s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda hekimlerimizin de\\u011ferlendirdi\\u011fi durumlar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Genel hal, ya\\u015fa uygun olarak tepki ve geli\\u015fim<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">G\\u00f6rme ve i\\u015fitme alanlar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">G\\u00f6z hareketleri<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Konu\\u015fma ve hareket kabiliyeti<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Kafa b\\u00fcy\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px;\\\">Koordinasyon, denge yetene\\u011fi<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; padding-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\\\">Refleks hakimiyeti<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Klinik de\\u011ferlendirme tablosu ve muayene neticesinde edinilen ilk izlenimler, bir\\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 tan\\u0131ya g\\u00f6t\\u00fcren bilgileri g\\u00f6zler \\u00f6n\\u00fcne serer. Ek olarak yap\\u0131lacak testlerin \\u00f6nemi bu a\\u015famadan sonra \\u015fekillenir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisinin Tedavi Y\\u00f6ntemleri Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"Beyin ve sinir sistemi kaynakl\\u0131 \\u00e7o\\u011fu hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuk n\\u00f6rolojisi alan\\u0131nda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcyoruz. Ayr\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 bahsetti\\u011fimiz \\u00fczere, tan\\u0131 ve tedavi i\\u00e7in ayr\\u0131nt\\u0131l\\u0131 \\u00f6yk\\u00fc, hekimin fizik ve n\\u00f6rolojik muayenesi b\\u00fcy\\u00fck \\u00f6nem arz eder. Hekim gerekli g\\u00f6rd\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc takdirde tan\\u0131ya katk\\u0131 sa\\u011flamas\\u0131 i\\u00e7in EEG, MRG, kraniyal ultrasonografi gibi radyolojik metotlar\\u0131, baz\\u0131 metabolik ve geli\\u015fimsel testlerini uygular. Tan\\u0131 netle\\u015fti\\u011finde b\\u00fct\\u00fcn fakt\\u00f6rler, hastan\\u0131n mevcut durumu g\\u00f6z \\u00f6n\\u00fcne koyularak tedavi plan\\u0131 \\u00e7izilir.\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-21 10:33:27', '2023-12-27 16:08:47'),
