(730, 730, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Romatolojisi', 4, 'cocuk-romatolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi\",\"content_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc, romatizma hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 olan \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n ve ergenlerin tan\\u0131 ve tedavisini yapan b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmd\\u00fcr. Romatizma hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 kas-iskelet sistemine ait lokal ve sistematik hastal\\u0131klar ile ilgili olup; kapsam\\u0131 \\u00e7ok geni\\u015ftir. \\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc \\u00e7ocuklardaki kas, eklem ve ba\\u011f dokular\\u0131n\\u0131 tutan yang\\u0131sal hastal\\u0131klar ile ilgili olup bu karma\\u015f\\u0131k hastal\\u0131klar i\\u00e7inde \\u00fclkemizde s\\u0131k g\\u00f6r\\u00fclenler; \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n romatizmas\\u0131 olarak bilinen Juvenil idyopatik  artrit, ailevi Akdeniz ate\\u015fi (FMF), sistemik lupus eritematozus ve damarlar\\u0131n yang\\u0131sal hastal\\u0131klard\\u0131r. Ba\\u015fka hastal\\u0131klar da \\u00e7ocuklarda kemik, eklem, kan ve ba\\u011f dokular\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyebilir ve \\u00e7ocuk romatolojisi bu durumlar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisine de yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur.\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuklar\\u0131n kanlar\\u0131n\\u0131, eklemlerini ve ba\\u011f dokular\\u0131n\\u0131n yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra di\\u011fer t\\u00fcm organlar\\u0131n\\u0131 etkileyebilen bir \\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131k \\u00e7ocuk romatolojisi uzmanlar\\u0131 taraf\\u0131ndan tedavi edilmektedir.<\\/p><p><div class=\\\"clearFix\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0.1px; line-height: 0.1px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/div><div class=\\\"author\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><\\/div><\\/p><ul style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">B\\u00fcy\\u00fcme a\\u011fr\\u0131lar\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Juvenil idiopatik artrit<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sistemik lupus eritematozus<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Juvenil dermatomiyozit<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Sebebi bilinmeyen ate\\u015fler<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Tekrarlayan ate\\u015fler<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Ailevi akdeniz ate\\u015fi<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Skleroderma<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Spondiloartritler<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><font color=\\\"#092c74\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\">Beh\\u00e7et hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/span><\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Henoch-Sch\\u00f6nlein purpuras\\u0131\\u00a0<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Kawasaki hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\">Poliarteritis nodosa ve mikroskopik polianjitis<\\/li><li style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><font color=\\\"#092c74\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-property: all; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\">Ps\\u00f6riatik artrit<\\/span><\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400; fo