(734, 734, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Sağlığı ve Hastalıkları', 4, 'cocuk-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00c7ocuk Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri, t\\u00fcm poliklinik, merkez ve hastanelerimizde 0-16 ya\\u015f aral\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131ndaki \\u00e7ocuk ve gen\\u00e7lerin tetkik, tedavi ve koruyucu sa\\u011fl\\u0131k hizmetlerini vermek \\u00fczere organize olmu\\u015ftur.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde en \\u00f6nemli hedeflerimizden biri anne s\\u00fct\\u00fc ile beslenmenin bebe\\u011fin geli\\u015fimindeki \\u00f6nemini unutturmamakt\\u0131r. Ayr\\u0131ca b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde t\\u00fcm yenido\\u011fan bebeklerimizin topuklar\\u0131ndan kan al\\u0131narak fenilketon\\u00fcri ve hipotiroidi taramas\\u0131 yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastanelerimizde bebeklerin fiziksel, sosyal ve psikolojik geli\\u015fimi de\\u011ferlendirilerek, Sa\\u011fl\\u0131k Bakanl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve D\\u00fcnya Sa\\u011fl\\u0131k \\u00d6rg\\u00fct\\u00fc \\u00f6nerileri g\\u00f6z \\u00f6n\\u00fcne al\\u0131narak a\\u015f\\u0131lar\\u0131 yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Birimimizde ebeveynlerin \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131 kronik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 hakk\\u0131nda bilgilendirilmesine y\\u00f6nelik \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmalar da ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">112Life \\u00c7ocuk Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde, \\u015fu alt dallarda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti verilmektedir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Alerjisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131; kistik fibrozis, t\\u00fcberk\\u00fcloz, do\\u011fumsal anomaliler, premat\\u00fcrenin akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, bron\\u015fiyolit, bron\\u015fit, pn\\u00f6moni, bron\\u015fektazi, sistemik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n akci\\u011fer tutulumu, intersitisiyel akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, pulmoner hemosiderozis, gastro\\u00f6zofagiyel refl\\u00fc ve kist hidatik hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, tetkik tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 i\\u00e7in solunum fonksiyon testleri ve ter testi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131ndaki ki\\u015filerde akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131; kistik fibrozis, t\\u00fcberk\\u00fcloz, do\\u011fumsal anomaliler, premat\\u00fcrenin akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, bron\\u015fiyolit, bron\\u015fit, pn\\u00f6moni, bron\\u015fektazi, sistemik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n akci\\u011fer tutulumu, intersitisiyel akci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, pulmoner hemosiderozis, gastro\\u00f6zofagiyel refl\\u00fc ve kist hidatik hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, tetkik tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131s\\u0131 i\\u00e7in solunum fonksiyon testleri ve ter testi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. Gereksinim duyuldu\\u011funda Grubun di\\u011fer t\\u00fcm b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleriyle \\u00f6zellikle n\\u00fckleer t\\u0131p, biokimya, patoloji, genetik ve di\\u011fer tan\\u0131 laboratuvarlar\\u0131yla i\\u015fbirli\\u011fi i\\u00e7inde faaliyet g\\u00f6sterilmektedir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Endokrinolojisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Endokrinolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde; b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme ve ergenlik sorunlar\\u0131, tiroid hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, diyabet hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, cinsiyet belirsizlikleri, metabolik kemik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, obezite, b\\u00f6brek\\u00fcst\\u00fc bezi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 k\\u0131llanma ve adet d\\u00fczensizli\\u011fi ile ilgili hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131, tedavi ve izlemi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. \\u00d6zellikle diyabet ve b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme hormonu eksikli\\u011fi olan hastalara tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri planlanarak uygulanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Gastroenterolojisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Sindirim sistemi yak\\u0131nmalar\\u0131 ya da hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 olan \\u00e7ocuklara tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmeti verilmektedir.\\u00c7ocuk ya\\u015f grubunda g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen gastrointestinal ve hepatobilier hastal\\u0131klar birimin kapsam\\u0131na girmektedir. Ya\\u015f grubuna uygun \\u015fekilde t\\u00fcm gastrointestinal sistem endoskopisi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir.\\u00a0<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Hematolojisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Hematolojisi birimimizde kan ve kan \\u00fcr\\u00fcnleri kaynakl\\u0131 t\\u00fcm hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve\\u00a0 tedavisi birim hekimlerimizce ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilmektedir. T\\u00fcm anemiler; demir eksikli\\u011fi anemisi, vitamin B12 eksikli\\u011fi anemisi, do\\u011fu\\u015ftan kan hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 Akdeniz anemisi, orak h\\u00fccreli anemi ve di\\u011fer anormal hemoglobinler, kemik ili\\u011fi yetmezlikleri aplastik anemiler, Fanconi aplastik anemisi, Diamand-Blackfan anemisi, idiopatik trombositopenik purpura, n\\u00f6tropeniler, \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131 l\\u00f6semileri, kanama diatezi, tromboz p\\u0131ht\\u0131la\\u015fma bozukluklar\\u0131 birim hekimlerinin ilgilendikleri ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca alanlard\\u0131r.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Kardiyolojisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Kardiyolojisi birimimizin amac\\u0131 do\\u011fumsal ya da sonradan meydana gelen kalp hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 bulunan \\u00e7ocuklara ve anne karn\\u0131ndaki bebeklere uygun sa\\u011fl\\u0131k hizmetini sa\\u011flayabilmektedir. \\u00c7ocuk ya\\u015f grubuna uygun tan\\u0131 ve tetkik ara\\u00e7lar\\u0131 ile tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetleri verilmektedir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Nefrolojisi<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Nefrolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczdeki alan\\u0131nda uzmanla\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015f hekimlerimiz \\u00e7ocuk b\\u00f6brek ve \\u00fcriner sistem hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 konusunda \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmaktad\\u0131r. Birimin ilgi alan\\u0131na giren ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca hastal\\u0131klar; \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131nda b\\u00f6brek ve idrar yollar\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, hipertansiyon ve romatizmal hastal\\u0131klar, ailevi akdeniz ate\\u015fi, sistemik lupus eritematozus ve eklem romatizmas\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisi<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h3><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0\\u00c7ocuk N\\u00f6rolojisi biriminde \\u00e7ocukluk ya\\u015flar\\u0131nda g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen havale gibi n\\u00f6rolojik sorunlar, yenido\\u011fan d\\u00f6neminden itibaren g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen geli\\u015fme gerilikleri, beyin felci (serebral palsy), kas hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, otizm gibi yayg\\u0131n geli\\u015fimsel bozukluklar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi sa\\u011flanmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h3><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Romatolojisi b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fczde \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131 romatizmal hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131na (0-16 ya\\u015f) tan\\u0131 ve tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri uygulanmaktad\\u0131r. Bu b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmde hizmet verilen baz\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar; ailesel akdeniz ate\\u015fi, a\\u011fr\\u0131 sendromlar\\u0131, beh\\u00e7et hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, \\u00e7ocukluk romatizmas\\u0131 (juvenil idiopatik artrit), genetik bir bozuklu\\u011fa ba\\u011fl\\u0131 tekrarlayan ate\\u015fler, Henoch - Sch\\u00f6enlein Purpuras\\u0131, lyme artriti, romatizmal ate\\u015f ve streptokok enfeksiyonu sonras\\u0131 geli\\u015fen artrit ve seyrek g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen \\u00e7ocukluk \\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131 birincil vask\\u00fclilitleri olarak s\\u0131ralanabilir.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; position: relative; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Psikiyatrisi<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h3><h4 style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; color: rgb(37, 170, 225); margin-bottom: 10px;\\\"><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00a0N\\u00fcfusun yar\\u0131dan fazlas\\u0131 \\u00e7ocuk ve gen\\u00e7lerden olu\\u015fan \\u00fclkemizde, sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 bir toplumsal yap\\u0131ya ula\\u015fabilmek ancak ki\\u015filerin \\u00e7o\\u011funlu\\u011funun\\u00a0 \\u00a0ruhsal y\\u00f6nden sa\\u011fl\\u0131kl\\u0131 olmas\\u0131 ile ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015febilece\\u011fi inanc\\u0131na sahiptir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk Psikiyatrisi birimimiz hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n biyolojik y\\u00f6n\\u00fcyle ilgilenmenin yan\\u0131 s\\u0131ra, davran\\u0131\\u015fsal ve toplumsal y\\u00f6n\\u00fcyle de ilgilenen ve bu a\\u00e7\\u0131dan e\\u011fitime ve koruyucu sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011fa y\\u00f6nelik de \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fan bir uzmanl\\u0131k dal\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk psikiyatrisi ilgi alan\\u0131nda bireysel psikoterapi, grup terapisi, oyun terapisi, psikodrama y\\u00f6ntemiyle grup terapisi, aile tedavisinin yan\\u0131nda dikkat eksikli\\u011fi ve hiperaktivite bozuklu\\u011fu gibi hastal\\u0131klar dahil olmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"1\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-kid\"}', '2023-12-21 10:41:27', '2023-12-27 16:13:04'),
