(742, 742, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk Ürolojisi', 4, 'cocuk-urolojisi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk \\u00dcrolojisi\",\"content_1\":\"<p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">\\u00c7ocuk \\u00fcrolojisi, anne karn\\u0131ndan ba\\u015flamak \\u00fczere, yenido\\u011fan ve sonraki d\\u00f6nemlerde g\\u00f6r\\u00fclebilen do\\u011fu\\u015ftan ya da sonradan geli\\u015fen \\u00fcriner ve genital sisteme ait hastal\\u0131klar ve bunlar\\u0131n tedavisi ile ilgilenir. Bu hastal\\u0131klara \\u00f6rnek olarak Hidrosel ve kordon kisti, \\u0130nmemi\\u015f testis, s\\u00fcnnet, testis ve torbalar\\u0131n acil durumlar\\u0131 (Akut skrotum ve testis torsiyonu) ile hipospadias verilebilir.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: none; outline: none; appearance: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hipospadias\\u2019\\u0131n (do\\u011fu\\u015ftan idrar \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f deli\\u011finin normal yerinden daha a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131da olmas\\u0131) cerrahi onar\\u0131m\\u0131 \\u00fcroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn ilgili alanlar\\u0131ndan biridir. Hipospadias\\u2019\\u0131n hem birincil onar\\u0131m\\u0131 hem de daha \\u00f6nce ameliyat edilmi\\u015f ancak sonu\\u00e7 al\\u0131namam\\u0131\\u015f vakalar\\u0131n cerrahi tedavisi yap\\u0131labilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-21 10:50:32', '2023-12-27 16:14:26'),
