(746, 746, 86, 79, 1, 'Çocuk ve Ergen Ruh Sağlığı ve Hastalıkları', 4, 'cocuk-ve-ergen-ruh-sagligi', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"\\u00c7ocuk ve Ergen Ruh Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p>\\u00c7ocuk ve Ergen Ruh Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (\\u00c7ERH) b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc 0 ile 16 ya\\u015f aral\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na poliklinik hizmeti vermektedir. \\u00c7al\\u0131\\u015fma alanlar\\u0131 aras\\u0131nda; otizm spektrum bozukluklar\\u0131, dikkat eksikli\\u011fi, hiperaktivite bozuklu\\u011fu, ergenlik d\\u00f6nemi patolojileri, davran\\u0131m bozukluklar\\u0131, yeme bozukluklar\\u0131, kimlik geli\\u015fimiyle ilgili sorunlar, depresyon, intihar, madde kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, bedensel belirtilerle seyreden ruhsal rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar, anksiyete bozukluklar\\u0131, bipolar duygudurum bozuklu\\u011funu i\\u00e7ermektedir.<\\/p><p>\\u00c7ocuk ve Ergen Ruh Sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 (\\u00c7ERH), sadece psikiyatrik hastal\\u0131klar de\\u011fil bo\\u015fanma, yas, kronik hastal\\u0131klarla ba\\u015fa \\u00e7\\u0131kma, ergenlik d\\u00f6nemi ge\\u00e7i\\u015finde ya\\u015fanan sorunlar, s\\u0131navlara haz\\u0131rl\\u0131k gibi sorunlara y\\u00f6nelik destek ama\\u00e7l\\u0131 terapileri de i\\u00e7ermektedir.<\\/p><p>Ayr\\u0131ca sosyal hizmet uygulamalar\\u0131 ve dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131k hizmetleri, okullara e\\u011fitim dan\\u0131\\u015fmanl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, halk\\u0131 bilin\\u00e7lendirmeye y\\u00f6nelik giri\\u015fimler, psikometrik de\\u011ferlendirmeler ve topluma y\\u00f6nelik koruyucu ruh sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 hizmeti b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcm\\u00fcz\\u00fcn \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fma konular\\u0131 aras\\u0131ndad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"\\u00c7\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-21 10:51:58', '2023-12-27 16:11:51'),
