(754, 754, 86, 79, 1, 'Göz Hastalıkları', 0, 'goz-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"G\\u00f6z Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"G\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, \\u00e7evresel ya da genetik fakt\\u00f6rlere ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak geli\\u015fen ve \\u00e7e\\u015fitli g\\u00f6rme problemlerine yol a\\u00e7abilen fiziksel rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klard\\u0131r. G\\u00f6z kapaklar\\u0131nda, g\\u00f6z\\u00fc d\\u0131\\u015f etkilere kar\\u015f\\u0131 koruyan ve saydam tabaka olarak bilinen g\\u00f6z zar\\u0131nda, g\\u00f6zya\\u015f\\u0131 kanallar\\u0131nda, g\\u00f6z merce\\u011finde ya da g\\u00f6z\\u00fc saran sinir dokular\\u0131nda meydana gelen her t\\u00fcrl\\u00fc hastal\\u0131k g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 olarak adland\\u0131r\\u0131l\\u0131r. \",\"mtitle1_1\":\"G\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n belirtileri nelerdir?\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"<p style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">V\\u00fccudun en \\u00f6nemli duyu organlar\\u0131ndan biri olan g\\u00f6zlerde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan herhangi bir problem\\u00a0g\\u00f6rme duyusunda gerilemeye ya da g\\u00f6z i\\u00e7erisinde batma, yanma ve benzeri \\u015fikayetlere yol a\\u00e7t\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in, g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n belirtileri kolayca fark edilebilir.<\\/p><ul style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6zlerde a\\u011f\\u0131rl\\u0131k ve a\\u011fr\\u0131,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6ze yabanc\\u0131 bir cisim ka\\u00e7m\\u0131\\u015f hissi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6zlerde ya\\u015farma, a\\u011flama \\u015feklinde g\\u00f6zya\\u015f\\u0131 at\\u0131m\\u0131,\\u00a0\\u00e7apaklanma problemleri,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">\\u015eiddetli g\\u00f6z ka\\u015f\\u0131nt\\u0131lar\\u0131,\\u00a0k\\u0131zar\\u0131kl\\u0131k ve yanma hissi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6rme alan\\u0131nda daralma ve g\\u00f6rme azl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6z kapa\\u011f\\u0131 d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fckl\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fc ve g\\u00f6z kapaklar\\u0131nda \\u015fi\\u015flik,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">Ba\\u015f\\u0131 bir yana e\\u011ferek bakma ve g\\u00f6zleri k\\u0131sarak bakma<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">gibi problemlerin bir ya da birka\\u00e7\\u0131n\\u0131n ya\\u015fanmas\\u0131 g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n habercisi olabilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"G\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 tan\\u0131s\\u0131 nas\\u0131l konulur? \",\"mcontent2_1\":\"<h2 style=\\\"font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; line-height: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: -56px 0px 10px; font-size: 28px; padding: 56px 0px 0px; width: 716.656px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><br><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6rme bulan\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, \\u015fiddetli g\\u00f6z a\\u011fr\\u0131lar\\u0131, ba\\u015f a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131, bulant\\u0131, g\\u00f6zlerde k\\u0131zar\\u0131kl\\u0131k ve \\u015fi\\u015fme gibi belirtilerin g\\u00f6zlenmesi bir g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n varl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131na i\\u015faret eder.\\u00a0Belirtilerin do\\u011fru\\u00a0g\\u00f6zlenmesi etkili\\u00a0tan\\u0131 ve tedavi i\\u00e7in olduk\\u00e7a \\u00f6nemlidir. Do\\u011fru tan\\u0131 belirtiler ile birlikte g\\u00f6z doktorlar\\u0131 taraf\\u0131ndan yap\\u0131lan test ya da\\u00a0muayeneler\\u00a0sayesinde belirlenir. G\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n te\\u015fhisi i\\u00e7in en \\u00e7ok kullan\\u0131lan ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca tan\\u0131lama y\\u00f6ntemleri:\\u00a0<\\/p><ul style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6rme kayb\\u0131 testi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">Tonometre ad\\u0131 verilen ve g\\u00f6z i\\u00e7i bas\\u0131nc\\u0131 \\u00f6l\\u00e7en alet ile yap\\u0131lan\\u00a0g\\u00f6z dibi muayenesi,<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: inside; font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6z bebe\\u011fi \\u00fczerine damlat\\u0131lan ve g\\u00f6z\\u00fcn geni\\u015flemesini sa\\u011flayan damla ile\\u00a0g\\u00f6z\\u00fcn \\u0131\\u015f\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 k\\u0131rma de\\u011ferleri, retina muayenesi (g\\u00f6rme zar\\u0131) ve optik sinir (g\\u00f6rme siniri) muayenesinin yap\\u0131lmas\\u0131\\u00a0olarak s\\u0131ralanabilir.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"G\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri nelerdir?\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"<p style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">G\\u00f6rme alan\\u0131nda daralmalara sebep olan g\\u00f6z hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\\u00a0g\\u00fcnl\\u00fck ya\\u015fam\\u00a0kalitesini olumsuz y\\u00f6nde etkiledi\\u011fi i\\u00e7in do\\u011fru tedavi y\\u00f6ntemlerinin tercih edilmesi olduk\\u00e7a \\u00f6nemlidir. Do\\u011fu\\u015ftan gelen g\\u00f6z rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131\\u00a0ve\\u00a0\\u00e7evresel etmenlere ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan g\\u00f6rme\\u00a0problemleri i\\u00e7in\\u00a0birbirinden farkl\\u0131 tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri geli\\u015ftirilmi\\u015ftir. Detayl\\u0131 g\\u00f6z muayenesi ile do\\u011fru \\u015fekilde tan\\u0131lanan g\\u00f6z probleminin tedavisi i\\u00e7in doktorunuz taraf\\u0131ndan g\\u00f6zl\\u00fck kullan\\u0131m\\u0131, ila\\u00e7 tedavisi, ya da cerrahi giri\\u015fim gibi tedavi y\\u00f6ntemleri tercih edilebilir.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \\\"Source Sans Pro\\\", sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 26px !important;\\\">Do\\u011fru te\\u015fhis ile etkili \\u015fekilde tedavi edilmeyen g\\u00f6z problemlerinin h\\u0131zl\\u0131 \\u015fekilde g\\u00f6rme kay\\u0131plar\\u0131na neden olabilece\\u011fi g\\u00f6z \\u00f6n\\u00fcnde bulundurulmal\\u0131, uygun s\\u0131kl\\u0131kta g\\u00f6z muayenesi ve doktor kontrol\\u00fc ihmal edilmemelidi<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"G\",\"status_1\":\"1\",\"icon_class_1\":\"icofont-eye-open\"}', '2023-12-21 17:58:58', '2023-12-27 16:12:59'),
