(760, 758, 86, 79, 3, 'ენდოკრინოლოგია და მეტალობური დავადებები', 0, 'endocrinology-ge', 1, '', '{\"title_3\":\"\\u10d4\\u10dc\\u10d3\\u10dd\\u10d9\\u10e0\\u10d8\\u10dc\\u10dd\\u10da\\u10dd\\u10d2\\u10d8\\u10d0 \\u10d3\\u10d0 \\u10db\\u10d4\\u10e2\\u10d0\\u10da\\u10dd\\u10d1\\u10e3\\u10e0\\u10d8 \\u10d3\\u10d0\\u10d5\\u10d0\\u10d3\\u10d4\\u10d1\\u10d4\\u10d1\\u10d8\",\"content_3\":\"\",\"mtitle1_3\":\"\",\"mcontent1_3\":\"\",\"mtitle2_3\":\"\",\"mcontent2_3\":\"\",\"mtitle3_3\":\"\",\"mcontent3_3\":\"\",\"mtitle4_3\":\"\",\"mcontent4_3\":\"\",\"first_letter_3\":\"\\u10d4\",\"status_3\":\"\",\"icon_class_3\":\"\"}', '2023-12-23 17:17:18', '2023-12-27 16:10:16'),
(761, 758, 86, 79, 4, 'Эндокринология и метаболические заболевания', 0, 'endocrinology-ru', 1, '', '{\"title_4\":\"\\u042d\\u043d\\u0434\\u043e\\u043a\\u0440\\u0438\\u043d\\u043e\\u043b\\u043e\\u0433\\u0438\\u044f \\u0438 \\u043c\\u0435\\u0442\\u0430\\u0431\\u043e\\u043b\\u0438\\u0447\\u0435\\u0441\\u043a\\u0438\\u0435 \\u0437\\u0430\\u0431\\u043e\\u043b\\u0435\\u0432\\u0430\\u043d\\u0438\\u044f\",\"content_4\":\"<p>Endokrinoloji ve Metabolizma Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc endokrin sistem fizyolojisi ve tiroid hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, diyabet, obezite, dislipidemiler, osteoporoz, b\\u00f6brek \\u00fcst\\u00fc bezi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, \\u00fcreme endokrinolojisi, hipofiz hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve hormonal otoimm\\u00fcn hastal\\u0131klar gibi pek \\u00e7ok hormon sistemi ve metabolizma hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131nda tan\\u0131, tedavi ve takip hizmeti sunmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nEndokrinoloji, endokrin sistemin organlar\\u0131 olan salg\\u0131 bezlerini, bunlar\\u0131n salg\\u0131lad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 hormonlar\\u0131 ve bu hormonlar\\u0131n etki etti\\u011fi organlar ile bunlar\\u0131n hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 inceleyen bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Endokrinoloji geli\\u015fime ba\\u011fl\\u0131 b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme sorunlar\\u0131, metabolizma hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, \\u00fcreme hormonlar\\u0131n neden oldu\\u011fu hastal\\u0131klar, \\u015feker hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 gibi pek \\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 inceler.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nEndokrin sistem, v\\u00fccudun farkl\\u0131 b\\u00f6lgelerindeki hormonlar\\u0131 salg\\u0131layan bezlerden sorumludur. V\\u00fccudun salg\\u0131lad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 kimyasallar maddedeler, farkl\\u0131 farkl\\u0131 organlar\\u0131 etkilemektedir. Bunlar aras\\u0131nda ergenlik d\\u00f6neminde b\\u00fcy\\u00fcme hormonlar\\u0131, ins\\u00fclin veya tiroid hormonlar\\u0131 gibi hormonlar bulunur.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"mtitle1_4\":\"Endokrin Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n Tan\\u0131 ve Tedavisi\",\"mcontent1_4\":\"<p>Endokrinoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde bir\\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavi i\\u015flemi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. Endokrin sisteme ba\\u011fl\\u0131 geli\\u015fen hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n \\u00e7e\\u015fidi olduk\\u00e7a geni\\u015f bir yelpazeye sahiptir. Sahip olunan hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n alt\\u0131nda yatan sebeplerin iyi ara\\u015ft\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131 gerekir.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n yap\\u0131s\\u0131na da ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak Endokrinologlar taraf\\u0131ndan hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n te\\u015fhisi i\\u00e7in \\u00e7e\\u015fitli testler istenebilir. Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n te\\u015fhisinden sonra ise hekim taraf\\u0131ndan uygun g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen tedavi y\\u00f6ntemi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nEndokrinolojik hastal\\u0131klar i\\u00e7in tek tip tan\\u0131 ya da tedavi y\\u00f6nteminden bahsedilemez. Farkl\\u0131 tipteki hastal\\u0131klara uygun olarak ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilen testler ve tan\\u0131 y\\u00f6ntemleri mevcuttur. Yine hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n tedavisi i\\u00e7in birden fazla tedavi y\\u00f6ntemi tercih edilebilir.\\r\\nEndokrinoloji hastal\\u0131klar i\\u00e7in genellikle kan testleri, tarama testleri, \\u00e7e\\u015fitli g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcleme y\\u00f6ntemleri ve hekimlerin gerek g\\u00f6rmesi durumunda hastan\\u0131n v\\u00fccudundan al\\u0131nan bir \\u00f6rnek ile biyopsi i\\u015flemi ger\\u00e7ekle\\u015ftirilebilir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle2_4\":\"Endokrinoloji Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 Nelerdir?\",\"mcontent2_4\":\"<p>Tiroid Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tiroid bezinin az veya \\u00e7ok \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131 sonucunda v\\u00fccutta farkl\\u0131 rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar meydana gelebilir. Tiroid hormonar\\u0131n\\u0131n yetersiz salg\\u0131lanmas\\u0131 durumunda; sa\\u00e7 d\\u00f6k\\u00fclmesi, uykusuzluk, kilo alma, halsizlik gibi durumlar meydana gelir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nTiroid hormonlar\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 salg\\u0131lanmas\\u0131 yani hipertiroid durumunda ise; h\\u0131zl\\u0131 kilo kayb\\u0131, \\u00e7arp\\u0131nt\\u0131, a\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131 terleme ve sa\\u00e7 d\\u00f6k\\u00fclmesi g\\u00f6zlemlenebilir. Tiroid hormonlar\\u0131nda meydana gelen bozukluk ciddi sa\\u011fl\\u0131k sorunlar\\u0131na neden olabilir. <\\/p>\",\"mtitle3_4\":\"\\u015eeker Hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131\",\"mcontent3_4\":\"<p>\\u015eeker hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131, di\\u011fer bir ad\\u0131yla diyabet pankreas\\u0131n yeterli miktarda ins\\u00fclin \\u00fcretememesin ya da ins\\u00fclinin v\\u00fccut taraf\\u0131ndan etkin bir \\u015fekilde kullan\\u0131lamamas\\u0131 sonucunda ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\u015eeker hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 (diyabet) en s\\u0131k Tip1 ve Tip2 olarak g\\u00f6zlemlenmektedir. Tip1, v\\u00fccudun ins\\u00fclin \\u00fcretimini b\\u00fcy\\u00fck \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcde azalt\\u0131rken, Tip2 v\\u00fccudun ins\\u00fcline kar\\u015f\\u0131 diren\\u00e7 g\\u00f6stermesine neden olur. \\u00d6te yandan hamilelerde ortaya \\u00e7\\u0131kabilen gestasyonel diyabet de v\\u00fccudun ins\\u00fcline kar\\u015f\\u0131 diren\\u00e7 g\\u00f6sterdi\\u011fi bir diyabet t\\u00fcr\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\u0130ns\\u00fclin yetersizli\\u011fi veya direnci sonucunda y\\u00fcksek seyreden kan \\u015fekeri v\\u00fccutta pek \\u00e7ok farkl\\u0131 sistemi etkileyebilmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle4_4\":\"\",\"mcontent4_4\":\"\",\"first_letter_4\":\"\",\"status_4\":\"\",\"icon_class_4\":\"\"}', '2023-12-23 17:17:18', '2023-12-27 16:10:16'),
(762, 762, 86, 79, 1, 'Enfeksiyon Hastalıkları ve Klinik Mikrobiyoloji', 99, 'enfeksiyon-hastaliklari-ve-klinik-mikrobiyoloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Enfeksiyon Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve Klinik Mikrobiyoloji\",\"content_1\":\"<p>Bug\\u00fcn bir\\u00e7ok hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n nedeni bilinmezken, enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n nedeni bilinmektedir. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Birimlerimizde yap\\u0131lan ara\\u015ft\\u0131rmalar\\u0131n temel amac\\u0131 v\\u00fccutta hastal\\u0131\\u011fa neden olan vir\\u00fcs, bakteri, mantar veya parazitlerin tespit edilmesi ve ilgili tan\\u0131 ve tedavi y\\u00f6ntemlerinin uygulanmas\\u0131d\\u0131r.<\\/p> \\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Normalde bir\\u00e7ok organizma v\\u00fccudumuzda ya\\u015far ve zarars\\u0131zd\\u0131r. Hatta \\u00e7o\\u011fu bakteri v\\u00fccudumuza yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olur. Ancak belirli ko\\u015fullar alt\\u0131nda baz\\u0131 organizmalar hastal\\u0131\\u011fa neden olabilir.<\\/p> \\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Enfeksiyon Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ve Mikrobiyoloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde; bakteriyel, viral, fungal  ve paraziter hastal\\u0131klar olmak \\u00fczere bir\\u00e7ok mikroorganizman\\u0131n neden oldu\\u011fu enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n tan\\u0131 ve tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u00d6zellikle viral enfeksiyonlar, vir\\u00fcs taraf\\u0131ndan meydana gelen enfeksiyonlard\\u0131r. Vir\\u00fcsler, bakteriler gibi her ortamda bulunabilir, yaln\\u0131z bakteriler gibi kendi kendilerine \\u00fcreyemedikleri i\\u00e7in canl\\u0131 bir mikroorganizmaya ihtiya\\u00e7 duyarlar. Bu da genelde baz\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n ki\\u015fiden ki\\u015fiye ya da b\\u00f6cekler veya di\\u011fer hayvanlar taraf\\u0131ndan bula\\u015fmas\\u0131na yol a\\u00e7abilir. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ki\\u015fiden ki\\u015fiye; yiyecek, su, hava veya temas yoluyla bula\\u015fabilece\\u011fi gibi yine ortamdaki organizmalara da maruz kal\\u0131nmas\\u0131 sonucunda ge\\u00e7ebilir.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n belirtileri ve semptomlar\\u0131, enfeksiyona neden olan organizmaya ba\\u011fl\\u0131 olarak de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik g\\u00f6sterebilir. Enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n en s\\u0131k g\\u00f6r\\u00fclen iki belirtisi ate\\u015f ve yorgunluktur. Hafif ge\\u00e7irilen enfeksiyon hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 i\\u00e7in dinlenme ve evde ila\\u00e7 tedavisi verilebilir.  Fakat baz\\u0131 enfeksiyon t\\u00fcrleri hayati tehlikeye neden olabilece\\u011fi i\\u00e7in hastane ortam\\u0131nda m\\u00fcdahale edilmesi gerekmektedir.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"E\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-23 17:41:44', '2023-12-27 16:09:48'),
