(778, 778, 86, 79, 1, 'Kulak Burun Boğaz Hastalıkları', 99, 'kulak-burun-bogaz-hastaliklari', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Kulak Burun Bo\\u011faz Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131\",\"content_1\":\"<p>Kulak, Burun ve Bo\\u011faz Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmleri 112life anla\\u015fmal\\u0131 hastanelerinde  ve t\\u0131p merkezlerinde hizmet vermektedir. Multidisiplinler yakla\\u015f\\u0131m ile kulak, burun, bo\\u011faz ve ilgili ba\\u015f boyun hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n hem medikal hem de cerrahi tedavisi yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Kulak Burun Bo\\u011faz B\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc Tan\\u0131 Tedavi Hizmetleri<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>112life anla\\u015fmal\\u0131 hastaneleri Kulak Burun Bo\\u011faz Hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerinde; i\\u015fitme kay\\u0131plar\\u0131, kulak enfeksiyonlar\\u0131, denge hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, ba\\u015f d\\u00f6nmesi, kulak \\u00e7\\u0131nlamalar\\u0131, kronik sin\\u00fczit, burun alerjileri, koku alma bozukluklar\\u0131, burun kanamalar\\u0131, burun t\\u0131kan\\u0131kl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve burnun d\\u0131\\u015f g\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcm\\u00fc ile ilgili problemler, nazal polipozis gibi burun hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131, g\\u00f6zya\\u015f\\u0131 bezi t\\u0131kan\\u0131kl\\u0131klar\\u0131, ses bozukluklar\\u0131, yutma problemleri, gastro\\u00f6zefajiyal refl\\u00fc gibi bo\\u011faz hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131 ile ba\\u015f ve boyun b\\u00f6lgesi t\\u00fcm\\u00f6rleri alan\\u0131nda tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetleri verilmektedir.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ayr\\u0131ca Odyoloji birimimizde odyolojik testler, orta kulak bas\\u0131n\\u00e7 ve refleks testleri, beyin sap\\u0131 odyometrisi (ERA) ve \\u00f6zellikle yeni do\\u011fan d\\u00f6neminde i\\u015fitmenin de\\u011ferlendirilmesinde en \\u00f6nemli tarama y\\u00f6ntemi olan oto akustik emisyon testleri yap\\u0131lmaktad\\u0131r.<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"K\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-26 12:33:42', '2023-12-27 16:04:32'),
