(786, 786, 86, 79, 1, 'Nefroloji', 99, 'nefroloji', 1, '', '{\"title_1\":\"Nefroloji\",\"content_1\":\"<h4>Nefroloji Nedir?<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Nefroloji, b\\u00f6breklerin sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 ve b\\u00f6brek hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilen bilim dal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Nefroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde b\\u00f6brek hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131yla ilgilenen uzmanlara nefrolog ad\\u0131 verilir. B\\u00f6brekler v\\u00fccutta bo\\u015falt\\u0131m sisteminin par\\u00e7as\\u0131 olarak g\\u00f6rev al\\u0131rlar. Kanda bulunan at\\u0131k maddelerin s\\u00fcz\\u00fcl\\u00fcp temizlenmesini ve v\\u00fccutta bulunan s\\u0131v\\u0131 fazlas\\u0131n\\u0131n idrar bi\\u00e7iminde at\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131 sa\\u011flarlar. B\\u00f6breklerin i\\u015flevlerini yerine getiremedi\\u011fi durumlarda meydana gelebilecek baz\\u0131 durumlar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li>\\u00c7abuk yorulma ve halsizlik ve \\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcme hissi<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Uyku bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130drar miktar\\u0131nda de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130drar renginde de\\u011fi\\u015fiklik<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Y\\u00fcksek kan bas\\u0131nc\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Y\\u00fczde, el ve ayak bileklerinde \\u015fi\\u015flikler, dizlerde \\u00f6dem sonucu a\\u011fr\\u0131l\\u0131 \\u015fi\\u015flik<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130\\u015ftah kayb\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Bulant\\u0131 ve kusma <\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Tat almada bozukluk, k\\u00f6t\\u00fc kokulu nefes<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>G\\u00f6\\u011f\\u00fcs a\\u011fr\\u0131s\\u0131 ve nefes darl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Nefroloji Hangi Hastal\\u0131klara Bakar?<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\nNefroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmlerimizde b\\u00f6brek rahats\\u0131zl\\u0131klar\\u0131 olan hastalara tan\\u0131 ve tedavi hizmetleri verilmektedir. \\r\\n\\r\\n<p>B\\u00f6brek sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in risk olarak tan\\u0131mlanabilecek hastal\\u0131klar ve durumlar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li>Diyabet hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Hipertansiyon<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Kalp ve damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Do\\u011fumsal ya da sonradan b\\u00f6breklerde meydana gelmi\\u015f yap\\u0131sal ya da fonksiyonel hasarlar<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>B\\u00f6brek ta\\u015f\\u0131 olu\\u015fumu<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Obezite<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Gut hastal\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Genetik yatk\\u0131nl\\u0131k ve hastan\\u0131n aile \\u00f6yk\\u00fcs\\u00fc<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130lerlemi\\u015f ya\\u015f<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Nefroloji kapsam\\u0131na giren ve nefroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde uzmanlarca de\\u011ferlendirilen ba\\u015fl\\u0131ca hastal\\u0131klar \\u015funlard\\u0131r:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li>B\\u00f6brek enfeksiyonlar\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>B\\u00f6breklerdeki filtreleme sistemlerini etkileyen glomer\\u00fcler bozukluklar<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>B\\u00f6brek damarlar\\u0131ndaki yap\\u0131sal ve fonskiyonel hasarlar<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Akut ya da kronik b\\u00f6brek yetmezli\\u011fi<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130lerlemi\\u015f b\\u00f6brek yetmezli\\u011finde diyaliz s\\u00fcre\\u00e7lerinin plan\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Tubulointerstisyel hastal\\u0131klar<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Nefrit<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Polikistik b\\u00f6brekler<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Hipertansiyon ve diyabetin b\\u00f6breklerdeki etkisinin tedavisi<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Romatolojik hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n b\\u00f6brekler \\u00fczerindeki etkisinin tedavisi<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130drarda protein ka\\u00e7a\\u011f\\u0131, kanama<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Su ve elektorlit bozukluklar\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Asit-baz dengesizlikleri<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Hidronefroz<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>\\u0130la\\u00e7 ve di\\u011fer maddelerin b\\u00f6brekler \\u00fczerindeki yan etkilerinin tedavisi<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Otoimm\\u00fcn vask\\u00fclit, lupus gibi ba\\u011f\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131kl\\u0131k sistemi hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131n b\\u00f6brek tutulumlar\\u0131<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n  \\r\\n<p>Nefroloji b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fcnde de di\\u011fer t\\u0131bbi birimlerde oldu\\u011fu gibi, ilgili t\\u0131bbi birimlerle i\\u015f birli\\u011fi halinde \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131l\\u0131r. B\\u00f6breklerin \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131 t\\u00fcm v\\u00fccut sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 etkiler. Benzer bi\\u00e7imde v\\u00fccutta bulunan baz\\u0131 hastal\\u0131klar da b\\u00f6breklerin sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 etkiler. Nefrologlar bir\\u00e7ok semptomu, b\\u00f6brekler ve t\\u00fcm v\\u00fccut sa\\u011fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 a\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131ndan birlikte de\\u011ferlendirirler. \\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Uzun s\\u00fcreli ila\\u00e7 kullan\\u0131m\\u0131 b\\u00f6breklerde sorunlara neden olabilir. Baz\\u0131 kronik hastal\\u0131klarda, kalp ve damar hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131nda, karaci\\u011fer hastal\\u0131klar\\u0131nda kullan\\u0131lan tedaviler b\\u00f6breklerde fonksiyon bozuklu\\u011funa sebebiyet verebilirler. Benzer bi\\u00e7imde onkoloji hastalar\\u0131n\\u0131n tedavisinde kullan\\u0131lan ila\\u00e7lar\\u0131n b\\u00f6brekler \\u00fczerinde zararl\\u0131 yan etkileri olabilmektedir. B\\u00f6yle durumlarda nefroloji<\\/p>\",\"mtitle1_1\":\"\",\"mcontent1_1\":\"\",\"mtitle2_1\":\"\",\"mcontent2_1\":\"\",\"mtitle3_1\":\"\",\"mcontent3_1\":\"\",\"mtitle4_1\":\"\",\"mcontent4_1\":\"\",\"first_letter_1\":\"N\",\"status_1\":\"\",\"icon_class_1\":\"\"}', '2023-12-27 16:33:03', '2023-12-27 16:39:19'),
